#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ASH.REMAINS_EYE_BONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ASH.REMAINS_EYE_BONE"
