#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ASH.REMAINS_GLOMMERFLOWER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ASH.REMAINS_GLOMMERFLOWER"
