#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.BEEBOX_HERMIT.FULLHONEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.BEEBOX_HERMIT.FULLHONEY"
