msgstr "Bir yığın bozuk satranç taşı daha."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK3"
