msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_BULBIN"
msgid "You'd never do anything rotten, would you?"
msgstr "Hiç çürük bir şey yapmazdın, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_DRAGONLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_DRAGONLING"
msgid "It's wyrmed its way into my heart."
msgstr "Solucan-vari bir biçimde kalbime girmiş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_EYEOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_EYEOFTERROR"
msgid "Always good to have another set of eyes! Er... eye."
msgstr "Bir çift göz daha her zaman iyi! Şey... bir göz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_GLOMLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_GLOMLING"
msgid "What an aerodynamical creature!"
msgstr "Ne aerodinamiksel bir yaratık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_KITTEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_KITTEN"
msgid "You'd make a good lab assistant."
msgstr "İyi bir laboratuvar asistanı olurdun."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LAMB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LAMB"
msgid "Much less mucusy than its momma."
msgstr "Annesinden çok daha az balgamlı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LUNARMOTHLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LUNARMOTHLING"
msgid "I keep her around because she's good at mothematics."
msgstr "Onu yanımda tutuyorum çünkü güve-matikte iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PERDLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PERDLING"
msgid "My feathered friend."
msgstr "Tüylü dostum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PUPPY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PUPPY"
msgid "Pretty cute for a lil monster!"
msgstr "Küçük bir canavar için epey şirin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CROW.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CROW.GENERIC"
msgid "Creepy!"
msgstr "Tüyler ürpertici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CROW.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CROW.HELD"
msgid "He's not very happy in there."
msgstr "Orada pek mutlu değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRUMBS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CRUMBS"
msgid "A crummy way to hide yourself."
msgstr "Kendini saklamanın kırıntılı bir yolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CURSED_MONKEY_TOKEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CURSED_MONKEY_TOKEN"
msgid "It seems harmless."
msgstr "Zararsız görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTGRASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTGRASS"
msgid "Cut grass, ready for arts and crafts."
msgstr "Kesilmiş çim, sanat ve zanaate hazır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTLESS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTLESS"
msgid "What it lacks in slicing it makes up for in splinters."
msgstr "Dilimlemede eksik kaldığını kıymıklarla telafi ediyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTLICHEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTLICHEN"
msgid "Nutritious, but it won't last long."
msgstr "Besleyici, ama uzun sürmeyecek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTREEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTREEDS"
msgid "Cut reeds, ready for crafting and hobbying."
msgstr "Kesilmiş kamışlar, zanaata ve hobiye hazır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CUTSTONE"
msgid "Seductively smooth."
msgstr "Baştan çıkarıcı kadar pürüzsüz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.GENERIC"
msgid "Freeing him might not have been my best idea."
msgstr "Onu serbest bırakmak en iyi fikrim olmayabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.IMPRISONED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.IMPRISONED"
msgid "I feel almost sorry for him."
msgstr "Onun için neredeyse üzülüyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.BURIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.BURIED"
msgid "He's trapped under all that junk."
msgstr "Tüm o hurdanın altına sıkışmış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.GENERIC"
msgid "Let's not upset him."
msgstr "Onu kızdırmayalım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.HOSTILE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.HOSTILE"
msgid "He seems upset."
msgstr "Kızgın görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.EXPOSED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.EXPOSED"
msgid "A pillar of impossibly hard stone."
msgstr "İmkansız kadar sert taştan bir sütun."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.GENERIC"
msgid "There's something glinting inside the marble."
msgstr "Mermerin içinde parıldayan bir şey var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEADLYFEAST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEADLYFEAST"
msgid "A most potent dish."
msgstr "Çok güçlü bir yemek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEAD_SEA_BONES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEAD_SEA_BONES"
msgid "That's what they get for coming up on land."
msgstr "Karaya çıkmaktan elde ettikleri bu işte."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNING"
msgid "What a waste of wood."
msgstr "Ne odun israfı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNT"
msgid "I feel like I could have prevented that."
msgstr "Bunu önleyebilirdim gibi geliyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.CHOPPED"
msgid "Take that, nature!"
msgstr "Al sana, doğa!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.GENERIC"
msgid "It's all leafy. Most of the time."
msgstr "Hep yapraklı. Çoğu zaman."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.POISON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.POISON"
msgid "It looks unhappy about me stealing those birchnuts!"
msgstr "O kozakları çaldığım için mutsuz görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECK_OF_CARDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECK_OF_CARDS"
msgid "Are we playing with a full deck?"
msgstr "Tam desteyle mi oynuyoruz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_CENTERPIECE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_CENTERPIECE"
msgid "How sophisticated."
msgstr "Ne sofistike."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.EMPTY"
msgid "A nice vase without any flowers."
msgstr "Hiç çiçeği olmayan güzel bir vazo."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.FRESHLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.FRESHLIGHT"
msgid "It's nice to have a little light."
msgstr "Biraz ışık olması güzel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.GENERIC"
msgid "A nice vase of flowers."
msgstr "Hoş bir çiçek vazosu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.OLDLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.OLDLIGHT"
msgid "I know I told Maxwell to replace the bulb."
msgstr "Maxwell'e ampulü değiştirmesini söylediğimi biliyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.WILTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.WILTED"
msgid "Not looking very fresh."
msgstr "Pek taze görünmüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_LAMP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_LAMP"
msgid "A welcoming light."
msgstr "Davetkâr bir ışık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.GENERIC"
msgid "It's beautiful."
msgstr "Güzel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.UNDRAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.UNDRAWN"
msgid "I should draw something in this."
msgstr "Buna bir şey çizmeliyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PORTRAITFRAME
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PORTRAITFRAME"
msgid "Looking good!"
msgstr "Güzel görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER.ANTLER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER.ANTLER"
msgid "What an impressive antler!"
msgstr "Ne etkileyici bir boynuz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER.GENERIC"
msgid "Is it staring at me? ...No, I guess not."
msgstr "Bana mı bakıyor? ...Hayır, sanırım değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS"
msgid "It's enormous!!"
msgstr "Devasa!!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.BURNING"
msgid "Can't be too careful."
msgstr "Aşırı dikkatli olunmaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.GENERIC"
msgid "It's over... right?"
msgstr "Bitti... değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.REVIVING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.REVIVING"
msgid "I don't want to believe what my eyes are seeing!"
msgstr "Gözlerimin gördüğüne inanmak istemiyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.GENERIC"
msgid "How's that for an icy gaze?"
msgstr "Buz gibi bir bakış için ne dersin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.NOEYEBALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.NOEYEBALL"
msgid "Someone lose an eye?"
msgstr "Birisi gözünü mü kaybetti?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD_KIT"
msgid "Stand back everyone, I am a trained scientist!"
msgstr "Geri çekilin millet, ben eğitimli bir bilim adamıyım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS_EYEBALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS_EYEBALL"
msgid "This is really gross."
msgstr "Bu gerçekten iğrenç."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER_ANTLER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER_ANTLER"
msgid "Was that supposed to come off?"
msgstr "Onun çıkması mı gerekiyordu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER_GEMMED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEER_GEMMED"
msgid "It's being controlled by that beast!"
msgstr "O canavar tarafından kontrol ediliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEPLETED_GRASS.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEPLETED_GRASS.GENERIC"
msgid "It's probably a tuft of grass."
msgstr "Muhtemelen bir tutam çim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DESERTHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DESERTHAT"
msgid "Quality eye protection."
msgstr "Kaliteli göz koruması."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DESICCANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DESICCANT"
msgid "Just dry and dry again!"
msgstr "Sadece kuru ve yeniden kuru!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DESICCANTBOOSTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DESICCANTBOOSTED"
msgid "It leaves me high and dry!"
msgstr "Beni yüksek ve kuru bırakıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL"
msgid "It smells of bacon!"
msgstr "Pastırma gibi kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL_NODEV
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL_NODEV"
msgid "I'm not strong enough to wield it."
msgstr "Onu kullanacak kadar güçlü değilim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIRTPILE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIRTPILE"
msgid "It's a pile of dirt... or IS it?"
msgstr "Bu bir kir yığını... yoksa DEĞİL mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.COLD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.COLD"
msgid "The signal is very faint."
msgstr "Sinyal çok zayıf."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.GENERIC"
msgid "It's some kind of homing device."
msgstr "Bir tür yön bulma aleti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.HOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.HOT"
msgid "This thing's going crazy!"
msgstr "Bu şey çıldırıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARM"
msgid "I'm headed in the right direction."
msgstr "Doğru yöne gidiyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARMER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARMER"
msgid "Must be getting pretty close."
msgstr "Epey yaklaşıyor olmalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.GENERIC"
msgid "I wonder what it does."
msgstr "Acaba ne yapar?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.READY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.READY"
msgid "It looks like it needs a large key."
msgstr "Büyük bir anahtara ihtiyacı var gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.UNLOCKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.UNLOCKED"
msgid "Now the machine can work!"
msgstr "Şimdi makine çalışabilir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODSTART
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODSTART"
msgid "That rod looks useful!"
msgstr "Bu çubuk faydalı görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DOCK_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DOCK_KIT"
msgid "Everything I need to build a dock for my boat."
msgstr "Tekneme iskele yapmak için gereken her şey."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DOCK_WOODPOSTS_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DOCK_WOODPOSTS_ITEM"
msgid "Aha! I thought the dock was missing something."
msgstr "Aha! İskelede bir şeyin eksik olduğunu düşünmüştüm."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DOLL_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DOLL_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "My beefalo will look as cute as a button!"
msgstr "Bızonsığırım düğme kadar tatlı görünecek!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_KIT"
msgid "I'd better stop dragon my feet and build it."
msgstr "Ejder-ayaklarımı sürmeyi bırakıp yapsam iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_PACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_PACK"
msgid "Boat building made easy!"
msgstr "Tekne yapımı kolaylaştırıldı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBODYHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBODYHAT"
msgid "I'm middling on this middle piece."
msgstr "Bu orta parçada vasat-orta hissediyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONCHILISALAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONCHILISALAD"
msgid "I hope I can handle the spice level."
msgstr "Umarım acılık seviyesini kaldırabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLY"
msgid "That's one fly dragon!"
msgstr "İşte havalı bir ejder!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.GENERIC"
msgid "Next best thing to a lockbox!"
msgstr "Kilitli kasaya en yakın şey!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.UPGRADED_STACKSIZE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.UPGRADED_STACKSIZE"
msgid "The amount of storage is off the scale!"
msgstr "Depolama miktarı pul-üstü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.GENERIC"
msgid "Produces a lot of heat, but not much light."
msgstr "Çok ısı üretir, ama çok ışık değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HAMMERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HAMMERED"
msgid "I don't think it's supposed to look like that."
msgstr "Böyle görünmesi gerektiğini sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HIGH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HIGH"
msgid "It's scalding!"
msgstr "Kaynar sıcak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.NORMAL"
msgid "Is it winking at me?"
msgstr "Bana göz mü kırpıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT"
msgid "What a weird fruit."
msgstr "Ne tuhaf bir meyve."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_COOKED"
msgid "The fruit's still weird."
msgstr "Meyve hâlâ tuhaf."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_OVERSIZED"
msgid "I half expect it to sprout wings."
msgstr "Yarı yarıya kanat çıkaracağını bekliyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_SEEDS"
msgid "It's a seed."
msgstr "Bir tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONHEADHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONHEADHAT"
msgid "So who gets to be the head?"
msgstr "Peki kim baş olacak?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONPIE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONPIE"
msgid "The dragonfruit is very filling."
msgstr "Ejdermeyvesi çok doyurucu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONTAILHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGONTAILHAT"
msgid "Someone has to bring up the rear."
msgstr "Birinin arkayı toplaması gerek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGON_SCALES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRAGON_SCALES"
msgid "They're still warm."
msgstr "Hâlâ sıcaklar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE"
msgid "It seems to reflect shadows instead of light."
msgstr "Işık yerine gölgeleri yansıtıyor gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONEHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONEHAT"
msgid "To keep my brilliant brain safe and sound."
msgstr "Parlak beynimi sağ salim tutmak için."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE_STACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE_STACK"
msgid "It's coming from deep down in those chasms..."
msgstr "O uçurumların derinliklerinden geliyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_LOG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_LOG"
msgid "It floats on water."
msgstr "Suda yüzüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNING"
msgid "That driftwood's burning!"
msgstr "O sürüklenmiş odun yanıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNT"
msgid "Doesn't look very useful anymore."
msgstr "Artık çok yararlı görünmüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.CHOPPED"
msgid "There might still be something worth digging up."
msgstr "Hâlâ kazılmaya değer bir şey olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.GENERIC"
msgid "A dead tree that washed up on shore."
msgstr "Kıyıya vurmuş ölü bir ağaç."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK"
msgid "Ready for gobbling."
msgstr "Yutmaya hazır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK_COOKED"
msgid "Even better for gobbling!"
msgstr "Yutmaya daha da hazır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_BANANABUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_BANANABUSH"
msgid "That bush is bananas!"
msgstr "Bu çalı muz-gibi çılgın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH"
msgid "Now it can be taken anywhere."
msgstr "Şimdi her yere götürülebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH_JUICY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH_JUICY"
msgid "This could be replanted closer to home."
msgstr "Bu eve daha yakın yere yeniden ekilebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_GRASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_GRASS"
msgid "It can be planted anywhere now."
msgstr "Artık her yere ekilebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_MARSH_BUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_MARSH_BUSH"
msgid "This needs to be planted."
msgstr "Bunun ekilmesi gerek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_MONKEYTAIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_MONKEYTAIL"
msgid "I wonder if they're edible? Maybe an experiment is in order."
msgstr "Yenilebilir mi acaba? Belki bir deney sırada."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_SAPLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_SAPLING"
msgid "This needs to be planted."
msgstr "Bunun ekilmesi gerek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_TRAP_STARFISH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUG_TRAP_STARFISH"
msgid "It's not fooling anyone now."
msgstr "Şimdi kimseyi kandırmıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL"
msgid "I usually let my mind do all the heavy lifting."
msgstr "Genelde tüm ağır işi zihnime yaptırırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_BLUEGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_BLUEGEM"
msgid "You can't get much cooler than that."
msgstr "Bundan daha havalı/serin olamazsın."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GEM"
msgid "I'll conquer this weight with the power of-- ACK! My spine!!"
msgstr "Bu ağırlığı şu güçle fethedeceğim-- AYK! Belim!!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GOLDEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GOLDEN"
msgid "It's worth its weight in gold."
msgstr "Ağırlığı kadar altın değerinde."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_HEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_HEAT"
msgid "It's good for a warm-up."
msgstr "Isınma için iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_MARBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_MARBLE"
msgid "I've trained my brain to be the strongest muscle in my body."
msgstr "Beynimi vücudumun en güçlü kası olacak şekilde eğittim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_REDGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_REDGEM"
msgid "It'll really make you feel the burn."
msgstr "Yanma hissini gerçekten yaşatacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN"
msgid "Oh, it smells!"
msgstr "Off, kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_COOKED"
msgid "Now it smells even worse!"
msgstr "Şimdi daha kötü kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_OVERSIZED"
msgid "I'm sure it'll make an even bigger stink."
msgstr "Eminim daha büyük bir koku çıkaracak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_SEEDS"
msgid "It's a seed."
msgstr "Bir tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUSTMERINGUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUSTMERINGUE"
msgid "Who or what would eat this?"
msgstr "Bunu kim ya da ne yer?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTH"
msgid "Tidy little guys, aren't they?"
msgstr "Düzenli küçükler, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTHDEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTHDEN"
msgid "They're snug as bugs in there."
msgstr "İçeride böcek gibi rahatlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EARMUFFSHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EARMUFFSHAT"
msgid "Makes you warm and fuzzy inside. Outside, too."
msgstr "İçini sıcak ve yumuşak hissettiriyor. Dışını da."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EEL"
msgid "This will make a delicious meal."
msgstr "Bu lezzetli bir yemek olacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EEL_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EEL_COOKED"
msgid "Smells great!"
msgstr "Harika kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT"
msgid "It doesn't look like an egg."
msgstr "Yumurtaya benzemiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_COOKED"
msgid "It's even less eggy."
msgstr "Daha da az yumurta gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_OVERSIZED"
msgid "I still don't see any resemblance to an egg."
msgstr "Hâlâ yumurtaya hiç benzerlik göremiyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_SEEDS"
msgid "It's a seed."
msgstr "Bir tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ELIXIR_CONTAINER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ELIXIR_CONTAINER"
msgid "That's more of a mortician's bag than a basket."
msgstr "Bu sepetten çok cenazecinin çantasına benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EMBERLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EMBERLIGHT"
msgid "A fire without fuel? No matter."
msgstr "Yakıtsız ateş? Önemli değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.BURNT"
msgid "A burnt vase on a burnt table."
msgstr "Yanık bir masada yanık bir vazo."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.EMPTY"
msgid "I should put something in there."
msgstr "İçine bir şey koymalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.FRESHLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.FRESHLIGHT"
msgid "It's nice to have a little light."
msgstr "Biraz ışık olması güzel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.GENERIC"
msgid "A flower in a vase on a table."
msgstr "Masada vazoda bir çiçek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.OLDLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.OLDLIGHT"
msgid "Did we remember to pick up new bulbs?"
msgstr "Yeni ampul almayı hatırladık mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.WILTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.WILTED"
msgid "Not looking too fresh."
msgstr "Pek taze görünmüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNING"
msgid "What a waste of wood."
msgstr "Ne odun israfı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNT"
msgid "I feel like I could have prevented that."
msgstr "Bunu önleyebilirdim gibi geliyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.CHOPPED"
msgid "Take that, nature!"
msgstr "Al sana, doğa!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.GENERIC"
msgid "It's all piney."
msgstr "Hep çam gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNING"
msgid "What a waste of wood."
msgstr "Ne odun israfı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNT"
msgid "I feel like I could have prevented that."
msgstr "Bunu önleyebilirdim gibi geliyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.CHOPPED"
msgid "Take that, nature!"
msgstr "Al sana, doğa!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.GENERIC"
msgid "This sad tree has no cones."
msgstr "Bu üzgün ağacın kozalağı yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEBRELLAHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEBRELLAHAT"
msgid "It watches over the wearer."
msgstr "Takanı gözetler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEMASKHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEMASKHAT"
msgid "You could say I have an eye for style."
msgstr "Tarz için bir gözüm olduğu söylenebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR"
msgid "Go for the eye!"
msgstr "Göze saldır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI"
msgid "I'm starting to feel self-conscious."
msgstr "Kendi kendime utanmaya başlıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI_GROUNDED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI_GROUNDED"
msgid "I think it's about to hatch..."
msgstr "Sanırım yumurtadan çıkmak üzere..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYEPLANT"
msgid "I think I'm being watched."
msgstr "İzlendiğimi düşünüyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET"
msgid "I hope it doesn't turn on me."
msgstr "Umarım bana karşı dönmez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET_ITEM"
msgid "I think it's sleeping."
msgstr "Uyuyor sanırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.BURNT"
msgid "I don't think anything will grow in a pile of ash."
msgstr "Bir kül yığınında hiçbir şeyin büyüyeceğini sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GENERIC"
msgid "I should try planting some crops."
msgstr "Biraz ekin ekmeyi denemeliyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GROWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GROWING"
msgid "Go plants go!"
msgstr "Hadi bitkiler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.NEEDSFERTILIZER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.NEEDSFERTILIZER"
msgid "I think it needs to be fertilized."
msgstr "Sanırım gübrelenmesi gerekiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_HOE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_HOE"
msgid "I have to make the ground more comfortable for the seeds."
msgstr "Toprağı tohumlar için daha rahat hale getirmeliyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.BURNING"
msgid "That can't be good for the plants..."
msgstr "Bu bitkiler için iyi olamaz..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL"
msgid "Time to reap science's rewards."
msgstr "Bilimin ödüllerini toplama vakti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_OVERSIZED"
msgid "With the power of science, I've produced monstrous produce!"
msgstr "Bilimin gücüyle, devasa ürünler ürettim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_WEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_WEED"
msgid "I knew I'd weed out the imposter eventually!"
msgstr "Sahtekarı sonunda eleyip ayıklayacağımı biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GENERIC"
msgid "That's a plant!"
msgstr "Bu bir bitki!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GROWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GROWING"
msgid "Grow my beautiful creation, grow!"
msgstr "Büyü güzel yaratımım, büyü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN"
msgid "Drat! If only I'd picked it while I had the chance!"
msgstr "Aman! Keşke fırsatım varken toplamış olsaydım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN_OVERSIZED"
msgid "What rotten luck."
msgstr "Ne çürük bir şans."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.SEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.SEED"
msgid "And now, we wait."
msgstr "Ve şimdi, bekleriz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW"
msgid "A convenient plot device."
msgstr "Uygun bir tarla-aygıtı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW_ITEM"
msgid "I'd better find a good spot for my garden before I use it."
msgstr "Kullanmadan önce bahçem için iyi bir yer bulsam iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_SOIL_DEBRIS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FARM_SOIL_DEBRIS"
msgid "It's making a mess of my garden."
msgstr "Bahçemi karıştırıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHERFAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHERFAN"
msgid "Down, to bring the temperature down."
msgstr "Tüy, sıcaklığı tüy gibi aşağıya çekmek için."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHERHAT"
msgid "BECOME THE BIRD!"
msgstr "KUŞ OL!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHERPENCIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHERPENCIL"
msgid "The feather increases the scientific properties of the writing."
msgstr "Tüy yazının bilimsel özelliklerini artırır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CANARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CANARY"
msgid "A canary feather."
msgstr "Bir kanarya tüyü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CROW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CROW"
msgid "A feather from a black bird."
msgstr "Bir kara kuştan tüy."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN"
msgid "A redbird feather."
msgstr "Bir kızılkuş tüyü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN_WINTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN_WINTER"
msgid "A snowbird feather."
msgstr "Bir karkuşu tüyü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEM_PUPPET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FEM_PUPPET"
msgid "She's trapped!"
msgstr "Kapana kısılmış!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE"
msgid "It's just a wood fence."
msgstr "Sadece tahta bir çit."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.GENERIC"
msgid "It is not functional as a standalone unit."
msgstr "Tek başına işlev görmez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.LINKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.LINKED"
msgid "Aw, it found a connection."
msgstr "Aw, bağlantı bulmuş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC_ITEM"
msgid "It's not a tree, but it must be planted."
msgstr "Ağaç değil, ama dikilmesi gerek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE"
msgid "It opens. And closes sometimes, too."
msgstr "Açılıyor. Bazen kapanıyor da."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE_ITEM"
msgid "All we need to build a nice, sturdy gate."
msgstr "Güzel, sağlam bir kapı yapmak için ihtiyacımız olan tek şey."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ITEM"
msgid "All we need to build a nice, sturdy fence."
msgstr "Güzel, sağlam bir çit yapmak için ihtiyacımız olan tek şey."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_JUNK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_JUNK"
msgid "Tell me it's ugly, I won't take a fence."
msgstr "Çirkin de, gücenmem — çit gibi sağlam mizacım var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ROTATOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ROTATOR"
msgid "Enguard! Re-post!"
msgstr "En garde! Yeniden direk!"

