#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.LEIF_IDOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.LEIF_IDOL"
msgid "Carving a tree out of wood seems a bit redundant."
