#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.BURNT"
