msgstr "Bu şey çılgınca!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREGROWTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREGROWTH"
