msgstr "O kristaller endişe konusu olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARELIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARELIGHT"
