#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.CALM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.CALM"
