msgstr "Serap mı bu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHABLEFLOTSAM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHABLEFLOTSAM"
