#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VICTORIAN_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VICTORIAN_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "I think my grandmother wore something similar."
msgstr "Sanırım büyükannem benzer bir şey giyerdi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH"
msgid "Those shadows are all cut from the same cloth."
msgstr "O gölgeler hepsi aynı kumaştan kesilmiş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTHHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTHHAT"
msgid "It makes me feel dark and mysterious."
msgstr "Beni karanlık ve gizemli hissettiriyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_BOOMERANG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_BOOMERANG"
msgid "What's the return policy?"
msgstr "İade politikası ne?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_KIT"
msgid "My knowledge of sewing with shadows is patchy at best."
msgstr "Gölgelerle dikiş bilgim en iyi ihtimalle yamalı-bohça."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_SCYTHE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_SCYTHE"
msgid "It makes harvesting so easy, it's scary!"
msgstr "Hasadı o kadar kolaylaştırıyor ki, ürkütücü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_UMBRELLA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOIDCLOTH_UMBRELLA"
msgid "I always hate when my hair gets melted by acid."
msgstr "Saçımın asit tarafından eritilmesinden hep nefret ederim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOLTGOATJELLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.VOLTGOATJELLY"
msgid "It's shockingly delicious."
msgstr "Şok edecek kadar lezzetli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAFFLES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAFFLES"
msgid "I'm waffling on whether it needs more syrup."
msgstr "Daha fazla şurup gerekip gerekmediği konusunda gaf-rette kalıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT"
msgid "Fascinating!"
msgstr "Büyüleyici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_CONSTRUCTIONSITE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_CONSTRUCTIONSITE"
msgid "Keeping it under wraps for now."
msgstr "Şimdilik örtülü tutulacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_CONSTRUCTIONSITE_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_CONSTRUCTIONSITE_KIT"
msgid "Big automatons really do come in small packages."
msgstr "Büyük otomatonlar gerçekten küçük paketlerde gelir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_CREATION_PARTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_CREATION_PARTS"
msgid "It comes in pieces!"
msgstr "Parçalar halinde geliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_LEG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_LEG"
msgid "It withstood for a while!"
msgstr "Bir süre dayandı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_POSSESSED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_POSSESSED"
msgid "Has anyone tried resetting it?"
msgstr "Sıfırlamayı deneyen oldu mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_SECRET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGBOSS_ROBOT_SECRET"
msgid "How intriguing!"
msgstr "Ne ilgi çekici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_BEACON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_BEACON"
msgid "This will help keep things contained."
msgstr "Bu, şeyleri kontrol altında tutmaya yardımcı olacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_FLYING.DAMAGED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_FLYING.DAMAGED"
msgid "It's too damaged to fix but I can salvage the parts."
msgstr "Tamir için çok hasarlı ama parçalarını kurtarabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_FLYING.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_FLYING.GENERIC"
msgid "Like a bot out of hell."
msgstr "Tıpkı cehennemden çıkmış bir bot gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_FLYING.INACTIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_FLYING.INACTIVE"
msgid "We should take it for a whirl."
msgstr "Bir tur atalım onunla."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_PARTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_PARTS"
msgid "Now I can put a positive spin on things."
msgstr "Artık şeylere olumlu bir dönüş katabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.DAMAGED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.DAMAGED"
msgid "I could repair it or harvest for parts."
msgstr "Onu tamir edebilir ya da parçaları için sökebilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.FRIENDLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.FRIENDLY"
msgid "Spin it to win it!"
msgstr "Çevir kazan!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.GENERIC"
msgid "They just drone on and on."
msgstr "Sürekli vız-vızıltı yapıp duruyorlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.INACTIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGDRONE_ROLLING.INACTIVE"
msgid "We should take it for a whirl."
msgstr "Bir tur atalım onunla."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNKBITS_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNKBITS_KIT"
msgid "Machines that fix other machines! What will science think of next?"
msgstr "Diğer makineleri tamir eden makineler! Bilim sırada ne düşünecek?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNKHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNKHAT"
msgid "It really gets my gears turning."
msgstr "Bu cidden dişlilerimi döndürüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_BITS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_BITS"
msgid "I bet I could make something incredibly scientific with this."
msgstr "Eminim bununla inanılmaz bilimsel bir şey yapabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_CAGEWALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_CAGEWALL"
msgid "Wall or nothing!"
msgstr "Duvar ya hep ya hiç!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_FLOOR_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_FLOOR_KIT"
msgid "What is this floor?"
msgstr "Bu nasıl bir zemin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_LEVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_LEVER"
msgid "It's a good time to switch things up."
msgstr "Şeyleri değiştirmek için iyi bir zaman."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_WORKSTATION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGPUNK_WORKSTATION"
msgid "Let's get to work!"
msgstr "Hadi işe koyulalım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_ITEM_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_ITEM_1"
msgid "Strange, this glove is not a projection."
msgstr "Tuhaf, bu eldiven bir projeksiyon değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_ITEM_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_ITEM_2"
msgid "This clipboard is... real."
msgstr "Bu yazı tahtası... gerçek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_MACHINERY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_MACHINERY"
msgid "There might be some discoveries to be made in this pile of junk."
msgstr "Bu hurda yığınında yapılacak keşifler olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_MUTATIONS_NOTE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_MUTATIONS_NOTE"
msgid "Fascinating! Illuminating! Brain-embiggening!"
msgstr "Büyüleyici! Aydınlatıcı! Beyin-büyültücü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_NPC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_NPC"
msgid "As a fellow man of science, I'm compelled to help him!"
msgstr "Bir bilim adamı kardeşi olarak, ona yardım etmem gerekiyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_NPC_MUTATIONS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_NPC_MUTATIONS"
msgid "Science never rests!"
msgstr "Bilim asla dinlenmez!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_NPC_WAGPUNK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_NPC_WAGPUNK"
msgid "I wonder where he's off to..."
msgstr "Acaba nereye gidiyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_1"
msgid "That has to be the tool I'm looking for!"
msgstr "Aradığım alet bu olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_2"
msgid "Of course I know what it is! It's just, er... too complicated to explain."
msgstr "Tabii ki ne olduğunu biliyorum! Sadece, ee... açıklaması çok karmaşık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_3"
msgid "Clearly a very scientific tool!"
msgstr "Açıkça çok bilimsel bir alet!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_4"
msgid "My scientific instincts tell me that this is the tool I'm looking for!"
msgstr "Bilimsel içgüdülerim bana aradığım aletin bu olduğunu söylüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WAGSTAFF_TOOL_5"
msgid "I know exactly what it does! Science!"
msgstr "Tam olarak ne yaptığını biliyorum! Bilim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK"
msgid "Couldn't we have just made a lifeboat?"
msgstr "Sadece bir cankurtaran sandalı yapamaz mıydık?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK_ANCIENT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK_ANCIENT"
msgid "Couldn't we have just made a lifeboat?"
msgstr "Sadece bir cankurtaran sandalı yapamaz mıydık?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK_GRASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK_GRASS"
msgid "Couldn't we have just made a lifeboat?"
msgstr "Sadece bir cankurtaran sandalı yapamaz mıydık?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK_YOTD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKINGPLANK_YOTD"
msgid "Dressing it up doesn't make me feel better about using it."
msgstr "Onu süslemek, kullanma konusunda kendimi daha iyi hissettirmiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKING_STICK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALKING_STICK"
msgid "It's a very nice stick."
msgstr "Çok güzel bir baston."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_DREADSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_DREADSTONE"
msgid "I feel so... safe?"
msgstr "Kendimi çok... güvende mi hissediyorum?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_DREADSTONE_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_DREADSTONE_ITEM"
msgid "What could go wrong?"
msgstr "Ne kötü gidebilir ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_HAY.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_HAY.BURNT"
msgid "That won't do at all."
msgstr "Bu hiç yaramaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_HAY.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_HAY.GENERIC"
msgid "Hmmmm. I guess that'll have to do."
msgstr "Hımmm. Sanırım idare edecek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_HAY_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_HAY_ITEM"
msgid "This seems like a bad idea."
msgstr "Bu kötü bir fikir gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_MOONROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_MOONROCK"
msgid "Spacey and smooth!"
msgstr "Uzayvari ve düzgün!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_MOONROCK_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_MOONROCK_ITEM"
msgid "Very light, but surprisingly tough."
msgstr "Çok hafif ama şaşırtıcı şekilde sağlam."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_RUINS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_RUINS"
msgid "An ancient piece of wall."
msgstr "Kadim bir duvar parçası."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_RUINS_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_RUINS_2"
msgid "An ancient piece of wall."
msgstr "Kadim bir duvar parçası."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_RUINS_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_RUINS_ITEM"
msgid "A solid piece of history."
msgstr "Tarihin sağlam bir parçası."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_SCRAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_SCRAP"
msgid "It's made of garbage."
msgstr "Çöpten yapılmış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_SCRAP_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_SCRAP_ITEM"
msgid "It's like a bundle wrap, of scrap."
msgstr "Hurda-cak bir paket-çek gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_STONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_STONE"
msgid "That's a nice wall."
msgstr "Hoş bir duvar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_STONE_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_STONE_2"
msgid "That's a nice wall."
msgstr "Hoş bir duvar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_STONE_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_STONE_ITEM"
msgid "They make me feel so safe."
msgstr "Beni çok güvende hissettiriyorlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_WOOD.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_WOOD.BURNT"
msgid "Burnt!"
msgstr "Yanmış!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_WOOD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_WOOD.GENERIC"
msgid "Pointy!"
msgstr "Sivri!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_WOOD_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALL_WOOD_ITEM"
msgid "Pickets!"
msgstr "Kazıklar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS"
msgid "Walruses are natural predators."
msgstr "Morslar doğuştan avcıdır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUSHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUSHAT"
msgid "It's covered with walrus hairs."
msgstr "Mors kıllarıyla kaplı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS_CAMP.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS_CAMP.EMPTY"
msgid "Looks like somebody was camping here."
msgstr "Birisi burada kamp yapmış gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS_CAMP.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS_CAMP.GENERIC"
msgid "It looks warm and cozy inside."
msgstr "İçerisi sıcak ve rahat görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS_TUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALRUS_TUSK"
msgid "I'm sure I'll find a use for it eventually."
msgstr "Eninde sonunda bir yararını bulacağıma eminim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.ATTACKER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.ATTACKER"
msgid "Is that how a Pinetree Pioneer is meant to behave?"
msgstr "Bir Çamağacı Öncüsü böyle mi davranmalı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.FIRESTARTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.FIRESTARTER"
msgid "That doesn't look like a campfire, %s."
msgstr "Bu kamp ateşine benzemiyor, %s."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.GENERIC"
msgid "Good day, %s!"
msgstr "İyi günler, %s!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.GHOST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.GHOST"
msgid "I know you're having fun, but we'd best find a heart."
msgstr "Eğlendiğini biliyorum ama bir kalp bulsak iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.MURDERER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.MURDERER"
msgid "Did you run out of material for your stories, %s?"
msgstr "Hikâyelerine malzemen mi tükendi, %s?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.REVIVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTER.REVIVER"
msgid "I can always count on %s."
msgstr "%s'a her zaman güvenebilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WALTERHAT"
msgid "I was never exactly \"outdoorsy\" in my youth."
msgstr "Gençliğimde tam olarak \"doğa adamı\" sayılmazdım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.ATTACKER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.ATTACKER"
msgid "This really isn't the time or place for that, %s!"
msgstr "Bunun ne zamanı ne de yeri, %s!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.FIRESTARTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.FIRESTARTER"
msgid "Let me guess, this has something to do with \"preserving the timeline\"?"
msgstr "Tahmin edeyim, bunun \"zaman çizgisini korumakla\" bir alakası mı var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.GENERIC"
msgid "Good day, %s!"
msgstr "İyi günler, %s!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.GHOST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.GHOST"
msgid "I'd better hurry up and find a heart."
msgstr "Acele edip bir kalp bulsam iyi olacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.MURDERER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.MURDERER"
msgid "Murderer! You won't get any second chances from me!"
msgstr "Katil! Benden ikinci bir şans alamayacaksın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.REVIVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDA.REVIVER"
msgid "If it wasn't for %s, I'd be history!"
msgstr "%s olmasaydı, tarih olmuştum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDERINGTRADER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDERINGTRADER.GENERIC"
msgid "What a strange looking beefalo."
msgstr "Ne tuhaf görünümlü bir bızonsığır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDERINGTRADER.REVEALED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WANDERINGTRADER.REVEALED"
msgid "If we trade, will we beef friends?"
msgstr "Takas edersek, sığ-arkadaş olur muyuz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARDROBE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARDROBE.BURNING"
msgid "That's burning fast!"
msgstr "Hızla yanıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARDROBE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARDROBE.BURNT"
msgid "It's out of style now."
msgstr "Artık modası geçti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARDROBE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARDROBE.GENERIC"
msgid "It holds dark, forbidden secrets..."
msgstr "Karanlık, yasak sırlar barındırıyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WARG"
msgid "You might be something to reckon with, big dog."
