msgstr "Acaba dinozorlar da böyle mi hissetti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WONKEY.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.WONKEY.GENERIC"
