msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.STORE.NOTMASTERCHEF"
msgid "I'd rather cook over a campfire, honestly..."
msgstr "Açıkçası kamp ateşinde yemek pişirmeyi tercih ederim..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.STORE.NOTSOULJARHANDLER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.STORE.NOTSOULJARHANDLER"
msgid "They're souls Woby, not treats."
msgstr "Onlar ruh, Woby, ikram değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.STORE.RESTRICTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.STORE.RESTRICTED"
msgid "Aww, I can't use that."
msgstr "Ay, onu kullanamam."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.CANTLEARN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.CANTLEARN"
msgid "Sorry, I kind of lost interest."
msgstr "Üzgünüm, ilgimi kaybettim biraz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.KNOWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.KNOWN"
msgid "Heh. I already knew that."
msgstr "Heh. Onu zaten biliyordum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.MESSAGEBOTTLEMANAGER_NOT_FOUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.MESSAGEBOTTLEMANAGER_NOT_FOUND"
msgid "Come on Walter, gotta focus! Don't get distracted!"
msgstr "Hadi Walter, odaklanman lazım! Dikkatin dağılmasın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.STASH_MAP_NOT_FOUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.STASH_MAP_NOT_FOUND"
msgid "Um... those monkeys aren't very good at making maps."
msgstr "Eee... o maymunlar harita yapmakta pek iyi değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.WRONGWORLD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TEACH.WRONGWORLD"
msgid "Wait... this map looks all wrong."
msgstr "Dur... bu harita tamamen yanlış görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TELLSTORY.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TELLSTORY.GENERIC"
msgid "This isn't really the place for a scary story..."
msgstr "Burası korkunç bir hikâye için pek uygun değil..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TELLSTORY.NOT_NIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TELLSTORY.NOT_NIGHT"
msgid "I should wait until it's dark, for maximum spookiness."
msgstr "Maksimum ürperti için karanlık olana kadar beklemeliyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TELLSTORY.NO_FIRE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.TELLSTORY.NO_FIRE"
msgid "I need a fire, it adds to the atmosphere!"
msgstr "Bir ateşe ihtiyacım var, atmosfere katkı yapıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.UNLOCK.WRONGKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.UNLOCK.WRONGKEY"
msgid "That's not right."
msgstr "Bu doğru değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.BEEF_BELL_ALREADY_USED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.BEEF_BELL_ALREADY_USED"
msgid "I already rang it!"
msgstr "Onu zaten çaldım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.BEEF_BELL_HAS_BEEF_ALREADY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.BEEF_BELL_HAS_BEEF_ALREADY"
msgid "I've already got as many big fuzzy friends as I can manage."
msgstr "Zaten idare edebileceğim kadar tüylü dostum var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.BEEF_BELL_INVALID_TARGET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.BEEF_BELL_INVALID_TARGET"
msgid "I don't think that's going to work."
msgstr "Bunun işe yarayacağını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.CANNOT_FIX_DRONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.CANNOT_FIX_DRONE"
msgid "Aww, it can't be fixed."
msgstr "Ay, tamir edilemez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.NOT_MINE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEITEMON.NOT_MINE"
msgid "That's not ours, Woby."
msgstr "O bizim değil, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEKLAUSSACKKEY.KLAUS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEKLAUSSACKKEY.KLAUS"
msgid "Wait, I want to get a closer look at that monster!"
msgstr "Dur, o canavara daha yakından bakmak istiyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEKLAUSSACKKEY.QUAGMIRE_WRONGKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEKLAUSSACKKEY.QUAGMIRE_WRONGKEY"
msgid "I guess I need another key."
msgstr "Sanırım başka bir anahtara ihtiyacım var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEKLAUSSACKKEY.WRONGKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.USEKLAUSSACKKEY.WRONGKEY"
msgid "I don't think that's what I'm supposed to use in this situation."
msgstr "Bu durumda kullanmam gereken şeyin bu olduğunu sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.WRAPBUNDLE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.WRAPBUNDLE.EMPTY"
msgid "Darnit, I forgot to get something to wrap."
msgstr "Lanet olsun, sarmak için bir şey almayı unuttum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.WRITE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ACTIONFAIL.WRITE.GENERIC"
