#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_CANNOT_BUILD.NO_INGREDIENTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_CANNOT_BUILD.NO_INGREDIENTS"
msgid "It looks like I need to find more supplies first."
msgstr "Önce daha fazla erzak bulmam gerekiyor gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_CANNOT_BUILD.NO_STATION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_CANNOT_BUILD.NO_STATION"
msgid "I could probably do it if I had a station with the right tools."
msgstr "Doğru aletleri olan bir istasyonum olsa muhtemelen yapabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_CANNOT_BUILD.NO_TECH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_CANNOT_BUILD.NO_TECH"
