msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DAMP"
msgid "It's just a little water!"
msgstr "Sadece biraz su!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DEERCLOPS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DEERCLOPS"
msgid "That has to be a Deerclops! I need to get a closer look!"
msgstr "Bu kesin Geyikgöz olmalı! Daha yakından bakmam lazım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DESPAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DESPAWN"
msgid "I don't feel so good..."
msgstr "Pek iyi hissetmiyorum..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_ATTACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_ATTACK"
msgid "Huh? My punches feel wimpier... not that I was wimpy before!"
msgstr "Ha? Yumruklarım daha zayıf hissediyor... daha önce de zayıftım demek değil bu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_ELECTRICATTACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_ELECTRICATTACK"
msgid "Darnit... guess the show's over."
msgstr "Lanet olsun... galiba gösteri bitti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_MOISTUREIMMUNITY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_MOISTUREIMMUNITY"
msgid "Oh well. It's good to stay hydrated anyway."
msgstr "Eh boş ver. Susuz kalmamak zaten iyidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_PLAYERABSORPTION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_PLAYERABSORPTION"
msgid "Back to regular Walter."
msgstr "Normal Walter'a geri döndüm."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_SLEEPRESISTANCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_SLEEPRESISTANCE"
msgid "I'm starting to get a bit tired..."
msgstr "Biraz yorulmaya başladım..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_WORKEFFECTIVENESS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DETACH_BUFF_WORKEFFECTIVENESS"
msgid "Alright, time for a break."
msgstr "Pekâlâ, mola zamanı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DIG_DISEASE_WARNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DIG_DISEASE_WARNING"
msgid "That should help... I think."
msgstr "Bu yardımcı olmalı... sanırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_DUSK"
msgid "It's getting late, better set up camp soon."
msgstr "Geç oluyor, en kısa zamanda kamp kurmamız iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.GENERIC"
msgid "Being outdoors makes everything taste better!"
msgstr "Doğada olmak her şeye daha iyi tat veriyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.INVALID
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.INVALID"
msgid "I don't think that's safe to eat."
msgstr "Bunu yemenin güvenli olduğunu sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.PAINFUL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.PAINFUL"
msgid "Oooh... my stomach hurts..."
msgstr "Aaah... midem ağrıyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.SPOILED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.SPOILED"
msgid "Ugh, what did I just eat?"
msgstr "Iyy, ne yedim ben?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.STALE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.STALE"
msgid "I think that was old..."
msgstr "Sanırım bu eskiymiş..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.YUCKY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EAT.YUCKY"
msgid "Even Woby wouldn't eat that."
msgstr "Woby bile onu yemezdi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EATING_NOT_FEASTING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EATING_NOT_FEASTING"
msgid "Hey everybody! Time to eat!"
msgstr "Hey millet! Yemek vakti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_BOOSTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_BOOSTED"
msgid "Refreshing!"
msgstr "Ferahlatıcı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_GHOSTVISION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_GHOSTVISION"
msgid "It's the best of both worlds!"
msgstr "İki dünyanın da en iyisi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_PLAYER_SPEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_PLAYER_SPEED"
msgid "I bet I could carry you, Woby!"
msgstr "Bahse girerim seni taşıyabilirim, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_TOO_SUPER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ELIXIR_TOO_SUPER"
msgid "I don't think my tummy can handle that."
msgstr "Karınımın bunu kaldırabileceğini sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.1"
msgid "A Pinetree Pioneer... never gives up...!"
msgstr "Bir Çamağacı Öncüsü... asla pes etmez...!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.2"
msgid "This is... ergh... a little heavy..."
msgstr "Bu... ühm... biraz ağır..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.3"
msgid "Woby... could you... help... at all...?"
msgstr "Woby... biraz... yardım... eder misin...?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.4"
msgid "I'll get it...! I just... need a minute...!"
msgstr "Yapabilirim...! Sadece... bir dakika lazım...!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.5"
msgid "This can't... be good... for my spine..."
msgstr "Bu... omurgam için... iyi olamaz..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.6"
msgid "Come on Wobyyyy... help me... out!"
msgstr "Hadi Wobyyyy... bana... yardım et!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.7
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.7"
msgid "I can... do it...!"
msgstr "Yapabilirim...!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.8
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.8"
msgid "Errgh... just... give me a minute..."
msgstr "Üühm... bana... bir dakika ver..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.9
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENCUMBERED.9"
msgid "Why am I... doing this... again...?"
msgstr "Bunu... neden... yapıyorum ki...?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENGINEERING_CAN_DOWNGRADE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENGINEERING_CAN_DOWNGRADE"
msgid "only_used_by_winona"
msgstr "only_used_by_winona"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENGINEERING_CAN_SIDEGRADE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENGINEERING_CAN_SIDEGRADE"
msgid "only_used_by_winona"
msgstr "only_used_by_winona"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENGINEERING_CAN_UPGRADE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENGINEERING_CAN_UPGRADE"
msgid "only_used_by_winona"
msgstr "only_used_by_winona"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENTER_DARK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENTER_DARK"
msgid "Ohh, verrry spooooky!"
msgstr "Aaah, çoook ürküüütücü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENTER_LIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_ENTER_LIGHT"
msgid "Oh, hey! I can see again!"
msgstr "Ah, hey! Yine görebiliyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EXIT_GELBLOB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EXIT_GELBLOB"
msgid "That was not fun."
msgstr "Bu eğlenceli değildi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EYEOFTERROR_ARRIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EYEOFTERROR_ARRIVE"
msgid "I'm pretty sure that's supposed to be attached to something!"
msgstr "Bunun bir şeye bağlı olması gerektiğine epey eminim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EYEOFTERROR_FLYAWAY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EYEOFTERROR_FLYAWAY"
msgid "Aww wait, come back!"
msgstr "Ay dur, geri gel!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EYEOFTERROR_FLYBACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_EYEOFTERROR_FLYBACK"
msgid "Oh good, they came back!"
msgstr "Ah ne güzel, geri geldiler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FAN_OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FAN_OUT"
msgid "Guess it's time for a new fan."
msgstr "Sanırım yeni bir yelpaze zamanı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FERTILIZER_RESEARCHED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FERTILIZER_RESEARCHED"
msgid "I didn't know there was so much to learn about this stuff."
msgstr "Bu şey hakkında öğrenilecek bu kadar çok şey olduğunu bilmiyordum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FIRENETTLE_TOXIN.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FIRENETTLE_TOXIN.1"
msgid "Ah! Ow! It burns!!"
msgstr "Ah! Of! Yanıyor!!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FIRENETTLE_TOXIN.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FIRENETTLE_TOXIN.2"
msgid "Aaaah, it got me! It got me!"
msgstr "Aaaah, beni yakaladı! Beni yakaladı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FIRENETTLE_TOXIN_DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FIRENETTLE_TOXIN_DONE"
msgid "Whew... I-I think I'm okay now."
msgstr "Of... s-sanırım şimdi iyiyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLARE_SEEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLARE_SEEN"
msgid "A signal! We should follow it!"
msgstr "Bir işaret! Onu takip etmeliyiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLOATER_HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLOATER_HELD"
msgid "I knew I'd come out on top!"
msgstr "Yukarı çıkacağımı biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLOATER_LETGO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLOATER_LETGO"
msgid "Submerging!"
msgstr "Dalıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLOAT_SWIM_TIRED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FLOAT_SWIM_TIRED"
msgid "I gotta paws. Get it, Wobes?"
msgstr "Mola-pati vermem lazım. Anladın mı, Wobes?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FOODMEMORY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FOODMEMORY"
msgid "only_used_by_warly"
msgstr "only_used_by_warly"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FREEDOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_FREEDOM"
msgid "That wasn't nearly as fun as I thought it'd be..."
msgstr "Bu sandığım kadar eğlenceli değildi..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_GATHER_MERM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_GATHER_MERM"
msgid "only_used_by_wurt"
msgstr "only_used_by_wurt"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_GHOSTDRAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_GHOSTDRAIN"
msgid "My head... I thought having ghosts around would be more fun."
msgstr "Kafam... etrafta hayaletlerin olmasının daha eğlenceli olacağını sanmıştım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HEALINGSALVE_ACIDBUFF_DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HEALINGSALVE_ACIDBUFF_DONE"
msgid "Hold on Woby, I think my Acid Repellent is wearing off."
msgstr "Bekle Woby, sanırım Asit Kovucum etkisini yitiriyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HERMITCRAB_SHELL_ARRIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HERMITCRAB_SHELL_ARRIVE"
msgid "We're here, Wobes!"
msgstr "Geldik, Wobes!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HERMITCRAB_SHELL_BADTELEPORTPOINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HERMITCRAB_SHELL_BADTELEPORTPOINT"
msgid "Aw, it didn't work!"
msgstr "Ay, işe yaramadı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HIGHRESEARCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HIGHRESEARCH"
msgid "I know everything now! Mostly everything, at least."
msgstr "Şimdi her şeyi biliyorum! En azından çoğunu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HOT"
msgid "Whew... come on Woby, we'd better find some shade."
msgstr "Of... hadi Woby, biraz gölge bulsak iyi olacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HOUNDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HOUNDS"
msgid "Woby? Do you hear something?"
msgstr "Woby? Bir şey duyuyor musun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNGRY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNGRY"
msgid "Can we stop for a snack break?"
msgstr "Atıştırma molası için durabilir miyiz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_AVOID_FORK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_AVOID_FORK"
msgid "Aww, but the other trail looks so much more exciting..."
msgstr "Ay ama diğer iz çok daha heyecanlı görünüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_BEAST_NEARBY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_BEAST_NEARBY"
msgid "I learned all about tracking in the Pioneers! It went thataway!"
msgstr "Öncülerde iz sürmenin her şeyini öğrendim! O tarafa gitti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_LOST_TRAIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_LOST_TRAIL"
msgid "I uh... think I lost the trail..."
msgstr "Eee... sanırım izi kaybettim..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_LOST_TRAIL_SPRING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_LOST_TRAIL_SPRING"
msgid "There's too many footprints in this wet ground!"
msgstr "Bu ıslak zeminde çok fazla ayak izi var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_START_FORK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_START_FORK"
msgid "This trail could be dangerous, but a Pinetree Pioneer has no fear!"
msgstr "Bu iz tehlikeli olabilir ama bir Çamağacı Öncüsü korkmaz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_SUCCESSFUL_FORK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_SUCCESSFUL_FORK"
msgid "Don't worry Woby, we're gonna catch them by surprise!"
msgstr "Merak etme Woby, onları sürpriz yakalayacağız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_WRONG_FORK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_HUNT_WRONG_FORK"
msgid "Huh... I have the weirdest feeling something's watching me."
msgstr "Hmm... bir şeyin beni izlediğine dair garip bir his var bende."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_INSUFFICIENTFERTILIZER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_INSUFFICIENTFERTILIZER"
msgid "I think it needs more nutrients."
msgstr "Sanırım daha fazla besine ihtiyacı var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_INV_FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_INV_FULL"
msgid "I already have too many supplies to carry."
msgstr "Zaten taşıyabileceğimden fazla erzağım var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_IS_FEASTING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_IS_FEASTING"
msgid "Don't worry Woby, I'll save some for you!"
msgstr "Merak etme Woby, sana da biraz ayıracağım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_FOUND_IN_THE_WILD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_FOUND_IN_THE_WILD"
msgid "Woby! Look what I found!"
msgstr "Woby! Bak ne buldum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.1"
msgid "I knew I'd find you!"
msgstr "Seni bulacağımı biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.2"
msgid "There you are!"
msgstr "İşte buradasın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.3"
msgid "Gotcha!"
msgstr "Yakaladım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND.4"
msgid "That was too easy."
msgstr "Çok kolaydı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND_LAST_ONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND_LAST_ONE"
msgid "I think that's all of them!"
msgstr "Sanırım hepsi bu kadar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND_LAST_ONE_TEAM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND_LAST_ONE_TEAM"
msgid "Good job {name}, I think that's the last one!"
msgstr "Aferin {name}, sanırım sonuncusu bu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND_ONE_MORE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_FOUND_ONE_MORE"
msgid "There should be one more hiding somewhere..."
msgstr "Bir tane daha bir yerde saklanıyor olmalı..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_LOSEGAME
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_LOSEGAME"
msgid "Darnit, they're too good at hiding!"
msgstr "Lanet olsun, saklanmakta çok iyiler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_TIME_ALMOST_UP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_TIME_ALMOST_UP"
msgid "Uh oh, I think we're almost out of time."
msgstr "Eyvah, sanırım vaktimiz neredeyse bitti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_TOOFAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_TOOFAR"
msgid "I don't think they'd be hiding way out here."
msgstr "Bu kadar uzakta saklanacaklarını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_TOOFAR_RETURN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDANDSEEK_TOOFAR_RETURN"
msgid "I think we're getting warmer, Woby!"
msgstr "Sanırım yaklaşıyoruz, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDEANDSEEK_JOIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDEANDSEEK_JOIN"
msgid "Can I play too? Uh... I mean, use my Pioneer tracking expertise?"
msgstr "Ben de oynayabilir miyim? Eee... yani Öncü iz sürme uzmanlığımı kullanayım mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDEANDSEEK_START
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KITCOON_HIDEANDSEEK_START"
msgid "Alright, I'm closing my eyes! Three... two... one...!"
msgstr "Tamam, gözlerimi kapıyorum! Üç... iki... bir...!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KLAUS_CALLFORHELP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KLAUS_CALLFORHELP"
msgid "He's calling more monsters! YES!!"
msgstr "Daha fazla canavar çağırıyor! EVET!!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KLAUS_ENRAGE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KLAUS_ENRAGE"
msgid "I think we made him angry."
msgstr "Sanırım onu kızdırdık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KLAUS_UNCHAINED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KLAUS_UNCHAINED"
msgid "Maybe he'll feel better with that chain gone."
msgstr "Belki o zincir gidince daha iyi hisseder."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KNOCKEDOUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_KNOCKEDOUT"
msgid "W-Woby...? Oooh... what happened?"
msgstr "W-Woby...? Aaah... ne oldu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_LIGHTNING_DAMAGE_AVOIDED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_LIGHTNING_DAMAGE_AVOIDED"
msgid "Woah! I almost got zapped!"
msgstr "Vay! Az kalsın çarpılıyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_LIGHTSOUT_SHADOWHAND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.ANNOUNCE_LIGHTSOUT_SHADOWHAND"
