msgid "I get kind of disappointed when it doesn't turn out to be a rat."
msgstr "Sıçan çıkmayınca biraz hayal kırıklığına uğruyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_COOKED"
msgid "Yup. It's a cooked carrot."
msgstr "Aha. Pişmiş havuç."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_OVERSIZED"
msgid "I was hoping it would sprout ears and whiskers too... oh well."
msgstr "Kulak ve bıyık da çıkarır diye umuyordum... eh, neyse."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_PLANTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_PLANTED"
msgid "Now we'll have more carrots. Yay."
msgstr "Artık daha çok havucumuz olacak. Yaşasın."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARROT_SEEDS"
msgid "Yep, those are seeds!"
msgstr "Aha, bunlar tohum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARTOGRAPHYDESK.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARTOGRAPHYDESK.BURNING"
msgid "That's not a proper campfire!"
msgstr "Bu düzgün bir kamp ateşi değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARTOGRAPHYDESK.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARTOGRAPHYDESK.BURNT"
msgid "Someone wasn't practicing fire safety."
msgstr "Birisi yangın güvenliğini uygulamıyormuş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARTOGRAPHYDESK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CARTOGRAPHYDESK.GENERIC"
msgid "We're mapping out the wilderness!"
msgstr "Vahşi doğanın haritasını çıkarıyoruz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOON"
msgid "You're a weird looking raccoon."
msgstr "Garip görünüşlü bir rakunsun."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOONDEN.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOONDEN.EMPTY"
msgid "Nobody's home."
msgstr "Evde kimse yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOONDEN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOONDEN.GENERIC"
msgid "I think something lives in there!"
msgstr "Sanırım içinde bir şey yaşıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOONHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATCOONHAT"
msgid "Now this is a hat made for the wilderness!"
msgstr "İşte bu vahşi doğa için yapılmış bir şapka!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATTOY_MOUSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CATTOY_MOUSE"
msgid "Sorry Woby, that's for the kits to play with."
msgstr "Üzgünüm Woby, bu yavruların oyuncağı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVEIN_BOULDER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVEIN_BOULDER.GENERIC"
msgid "Come on Woby, give me a hand moving this!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby, bunu taşımakta bana pati ver!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVEIN_BOULDER.RAISED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVEIN_BOULDER.RAISED"
msgid "I can't get to it!"
msgstr "Ona ulaşamıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA"
msgid "I wouldn't mind stopping for a snack."
msgstr "Atıştırmak için durmaktan rahatsız olmam."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA_BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA_BURNT"
msgid "Whoops..."
msgstr "Eyvah..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA_COOKED"
msgid "Well... it's a hot banana."
msgstr "Şey... bu sıcak bir muz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA_TREE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_BANANA_TREE"
msgid "I didn't know bananas could grow in caves."
msgstr "Mağaralarda muz yetiştiğini bilmiyordum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE"
msgid "That rock's blocking the entrance!"
msgstr "O kaya girişi tıkıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_OPEN.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_OPEN.FULL"
msgid "There's too many people in there... I'll just wait."
msgstr "İçeride çok fazla insan var... Ben beklerim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_OPEN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_OPEN.GENERIC"
msgid "Why can't we go in?"
msgstr "Neden içeri giremiyoruz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_OPEN.OPEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_OPEN.OPEN"
msgid "Come on Woby! Let's take a look around!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby! Etrafa bir göz atalım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_RUINS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_ENTRANCE_RUINS"
msgid "There's probably tons of good stuff in there."
msgstr "Muhtemelen içeride bir sürü güzel şey var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_EXIT.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_EXIT.FULL"
msgid "There's too many people outside... let's just wait here."
msgstr "Dışarıda çok fazla insan var... burada bekleyelim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_EXIT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_EXIT.GENERIC"
msgid "Guess we're stuck here Woby."
msgstr "Galiba burada mahsur kaldık Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_EXIT.OPEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_EXIT.OPEN"
msgid "Alright, let's go!"
msgstr "Tamam, gidelim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_FERN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_FERN"
msgid "There's some weird plants growing down here."
msgstr "Burada garip bitkiler yetişiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_FERN_WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_FERN_WITHERED"
msgid "These weird plants don't do well down here."
msgstr "Bu garip bitkiler burada pek tutmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.DEAD"
msgid "Yup. It's dead."
msgstr "Aha. Ölmüş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.GENERIC"
msgid "Careful Woby! It's gassy."
msgstr "Dikkat Woby! Gazlı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.SLEEPING"
msgid "Shh... don't wake it, Woby."
msgstr "Şşşt... uyandırma onu Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.VENTING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_MITE.VENTING"
msgid "It's blowing off steam! Get it, Woby?"
msgstr "Buhar üflüyor! Anladın mı Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.GAS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.GAS"
msgid "Yuck! Stay back, Woby girl!"
msgstr "Iyy! Geri dur Woby kızım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.GENERIC"
msgid "Not too close, Wobes."
msgstr "Fazla yaklaşma Wobes."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.HOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.HOT"
msgid "It's just blowing off steam! Get it, Woby?"
msgstr "Sadece buhar üflüyor! Anladın mı Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.MIASMA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CAVE_VENT_ROCK.MIASMA"
msgid "Steer clear, Wobers!"
msgstr "Uzak dur Wobers!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CEVICHE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CEVICHE"
msgid "Mushy, but tasty."
msgstr "Yumuşacık ama lezzetli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARCOAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARCOAL"
msgid "You find a lot of these in fire pits."
msgstr "Ateş çukurlarında bunlardan çokça bulunur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIERESIDUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIERESIDUE"
msgid "only_used_by_winona"
msgstr "only_used_by_winona"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIEROSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIEROSE"
msgid "only_used_by_winona"
msgstr "only_used_by_winona"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_HAND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_HAND"
msgid "We should give it a hand! Heh. Good one, Walter."
msgstr "Buna pati uzatmalıyız! Hehe. İyiydi Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_HECKLER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_HECKLER"
msgid "What mean birds! At least I think they're birds."
msgstr "Ne kötü kuşlar! En azından kuş olduklarını sanıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_LECTURN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_LECTURN"
msgid "I wonder who'll be playing the characters?"
msgstr "Acaba karakterleri kim oynayacak?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_NPC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_NPC"
msgid "Excuse me, ma'am! It's dangerous here, do you need any assistance?"
msgstr "Affedersiniz hanımefendi! Burası tehlikeli, yardıma ihtiyacınız var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_STAGE_POST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHARLIE_STAGE_POST"
msgid "Are we doing a talent show?"
msgstr "Yetenek gösterisi mi yapıyoruz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK1"
msgid "I don't think they're going to get up anytime soon."
msgstr "Yakın zamanda kalkacaklarını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK2"
msgid "I don't think they're going to get up anytime soon."
msgstr "Yakın zamanda kalkacaklarını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK3"
msgid "I don't think they're going to get up anytime soon."
msgstr "Yakın zamanda kalkacaklarını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ANCHOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ANCHOR"
msgid "Technically this could still work as a real anchor."
msgstr "Teknik olarak hâlâ gerçek bir çapa olarak iş görebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ANTLION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ANTLION"
msgid "She really shook you up, didn't she Woby?"
msgstr "Seni iyice sarstı, değil mi Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEARGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEARGER"
msgid "It looks just like him!"
msgstr "Tam ona benziyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEARGER_MUTATED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEARGER_MUTATED"
msgid "We bearly escaped! Get it?"
msgstr "Ayı-zı kalsın kurtulduk! Anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEEFALO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEEFALO"
msgid "Aw don't be jealous Woby, you deserve a statue too!"
msgstr "Aaa kıskanma Woby, sen de bir heykeli hak ediyorsun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEEQUEEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BEEQUEEN"
msgid "At least I'm not allergic to bees made out of stone."
msgstr "En azından taştan yapılmış arılara alerjim yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BISHOP.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BISHOP.GENERIC"
msgid "Woby doesn't seem to like it."
msgstr "Woby pek hoşlanmamış gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BISHOP.STRUGGLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BISHOP.STRUGGLE"
msgid "It's coming to life!"
msgstr "Canlanıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BUTTERFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_BUTTERFLY"
msgid "It's not quite as good as a real bug collection, but close!"
msgstr "Gerçek bir böcek koleksiyonu kadar iyi değil ama yakın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CARRAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CARRAT"
msgid "I usually prefer badges to trophies, but I might make an exception."
msgstr "Genelde rozetleri kupalara tercih ederim ama bir istisna yapabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CATCOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CATCOON"
msgid "It's not quite as exciting as a monster statue, is it?"
msgstr "Bir canavar heykeli kadar heyecanlı değil, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CLAYHOUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CLAYHOUND"
msgid "He wasn't a very good dog."
msgstr "Pek iyi bir köpek değildi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CLAYWARG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CLAYWARG"
msgid "Poor Woby. She never seems to get along with the other dogs."
msgstr "Zavallı Woby. Diğer köpeklerle hiç anlaşamıyor gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CRABKING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_CRABKING"
msgid "The crabbiest sea monster I've ever met!"
msgstr "Tanıştığım en huysuz deniz canavarı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DAYWALKER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DAYWALKER"
msgid "I sure hope we get to see him again!"
msgstr "Umarım onu tekrar görürüz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DAYWALKER2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DAYWALKER2"
msgid "We did see him again!"
msgstr "Onu tekrar gördük!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DEERCLOPS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DEERCLOPS"
msgid "I like this one!"
msgstr "Bunu sevdim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DEERCLOPS_MUTATED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DEERCLOPS_MUTATED"
msgid "I still feel kind of bad for her."
msgstr "Hâlâ ona biraz üzülüyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DEPTHWORM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DEPTHWORM"
msgid "The carving somehow still feels slithery!"
msgstr "Heykel hâlâ kıvrak hissettiriyor nedense!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DRAGONFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_DRAGONFLY"
msgid "If only we could've gotten along."
msgstr "Keşke anlaşabilseydik."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_EYEOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_EYEOFTERROR"
msgid "Nothing to see here, folks! Ha ha, get it Woby?"
msgstr "Burada görecek bir şey yok millet! Ha ha, anladın mı Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_FORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_FORMAL"
msgid "Ugh. Who would want to be stuck wearing a suit forever?"
msgstr "Off. Kim sonsuza kadar takım elbiseyle kalmak ister ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_GUARDIANPHASE3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_GUARDIANPHASE3"
msgid "It's so lifelike, I feel like they're staring right at me!"
msgstr "Çok canlı görünüyor, sanki tam bana bakıyormuş gibi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_HORNUCOPIA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_HORNUCOPIA"
msgid "I'm starting to get hungry just looking at it..."
msgstr "Sırf bakarken acıkmaya başladım..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KITCOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KITCOON"
msgid "They're pretty cute, but not as cute as you Woby."
msgstr "Bayağı tatlılar ama senin kadar değil Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KLAUS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KLAUS"
msgid "Aw, it reminds me of the holidays."
msgstr "Aaa, bana bayramları hatırlatıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KNIGHT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KNIGHT.GENERIC"
msgid "What are you so worried about Woby? It's just a statue."
msgstr "Neden bu kadar endişelisin Woby? Sadece bir heykel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KNIGHT.STRUGGLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_KNIGHT.STRUGGLE"
msgid "Alright Woby, I stand corrected."
msgstr "Tamam Woby, yanılmışım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MALBATROSS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MALBATROSS"
msgid "She was pretty angry at us, wasn't she Woby?"
msgstr "Bize bayağı kızgındı, değil mi Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MANRABBIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MANRABBIT"
msgid "He looks so happy! And hoppy!"
msgstr "Çok mutlu görünüyor! Hem de hopla-mutlu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MINOTAUR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MINOTAUR"
msgid "This statue is... a-maze-ing! Get it?"
msgstr "Bu heykel... lab-iharika! Anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MOON"
msgid "It tells folks to be-were! Get it?"
msgstr "İnsanlara kurt-larlı olun diyor! Anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MOOSEGOOSE.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MOOSEGOOSE.1"
msgid "It's a shame things had to end the way they did."
msgstr "Olayların öyle bitmesi yazık oldu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MUSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_MUSE"
msgid "It's just a statue."
msgstr "Sadece bir heykel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_PAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_PAWN"
msgid "Pawns don't seem like statue material."
msgstr "Piyonlar heykel malzemesi gibi durmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_PIPE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_PIPE"
msgid "It looks like one of those joke pipes you can mail in for."
msgstr "Şu posta yoluyla sipariş edebileceğin şaka pipolarından birine benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ROOK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ROOK.GENERIC"
msgid "It's so lifelike!"
msgstr "Çok canlı görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ROOK.STRUGGLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_ROOK.STRUGGLE"
msgid "Hey, I think it's moving!"
msgstr "Hey, sanırım hareket ediyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_SHARKBOI
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_SHARKBOI"
msgid "Your bark was worse than their bite, Woby!"
msgstr "Senin havlaman onların ısırığından daha kötüydü Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_STALKER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_STALKER"
msgid "Definitely on my top five list of skeletons."
msgstr "Kesinlikle en sevdiğim beş iskeletten biri."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_TOADSTOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_TOADSTOOL"
msgid "At least this version doesn't smell like old mushrooms."
msgstr "En azından bu versiyon eski mantar gibi kokmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_TWINSOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_TWINSOFTERROR"
msgid "Is this one of those sculptures where the eyes follow you around the room?"
msgstr "Bu, gözleri seni odanın her yerinde takip eden o heykellerden biri mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WAGBOSS_LUNAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WAGBOSS_LUNAR"
msgid "Like a robot possessed!"
msgstr "Sanki cinli bir robot!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WAGBOSS_ROBOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WAGBOSS_ROBOT"
msgid "My very own model robot!"
msgstr "Kendi maket robotum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WARG_MUTATED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WARG_MUTATED"
msgid "They weren't nearly as nice as you, Woby."
msgstr "Senin kadar kibar değillerdi Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WORMBOSS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_WORMBOSS"
msgid "It was gross inside and out!"
msgstr "İçi de dışı da iğrençti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_YOTD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_YOTD"
msgid "Racing was fun, even if I didn't get a badge for it..."
msgstr "Yarış eğlenceliydi, bunun için rozet almasam bile..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_YOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_YOTH"
msgid "It's a chess piece of a chess piece!"
msgstr "Bu bir satranç taşının satranç taşı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_YOTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESSPIECE_YOTS"
msgid "The carving still looks slithery!"
msgstr "Heykel hâlâ kıvrak görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTER"
msgid "Who's a good little monster? You are!"
msgstr "Kim iyi bir küçük canavar? Sensin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTER_EYEBONE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTER_EYEBONE.GENERIC"
msgid "No chewing on this bone, okay Woby?"
msgstr "Bu kemiği çiğnemek yok, tamam mı Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTER_EYEBONE.WAITING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTER_EYEBONE.WAITING"
msgid "Getting some well deserved shut-eye."
msgstr "Hak ettiği bir şekerleme yapıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTUPGRADE_STACKSIZE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHESTUPGRADE_STACKSIZE"
msgid "I can make more room for supplies!"
msgstr "Erzaklara daha fazla yer açabilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHEST_MIMIC_REVEALED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHEST_MIMIC_REVEALED"
msgid "And I was right! It's a box monster, Woby!"
msgstr "Haklıymışım! Bu bir kutu canavarı Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHUM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CHUM"
msgid "You use it to lure the fish in."
msgstr "Balıkları çekmek için kullanılıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYHOUND.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYHOUND.GENERIC"
msgid "Who's a good boy?"
msgstr "Kim iyi bir oğlan?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYHOUND.STATUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYHOUND.STATUE"
msgid "I wonder who made these statues? They look so real!"
msgstr "Acaba bu heykelleri kim yaptı? Çok gerçekçi görünüyorlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYWARG.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYWARG.GENERIC"
msgid "Don't worry, I'm good with dogs!"
msgstr "Merak etme, köpeklerle aram iyidir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYWARG.STATUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CLAYWARG.STATUE"
msgid "Woby's sure sniffing around this statue a lot."
msgstr "Woby bu heykelin etrafını fena koklayıp duruyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.EMBERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.EMBERS"
msgid "We need more fuel for the fire!"
msgstr "Ateşe daha fazla yakıt lazım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.GENERIC"
msgid "Anyone want to hear a scary story?"
msgstr "Korkunç bir hikâye dinlemek isteyen var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.HIGH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.HIGH"
msgid "Woah! I don't think that's safe..."
msgstr "Vay! Bu hiç güvenli görünmüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.LOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.LOW"
msgid "It might need some more fuel."
msgstr "Biraz daha yakıt gerekebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.NORMAL"
msgid "It's the perfect temperature for... cold marshmallows?"
msgstr "Tam... soğuk lokum için mükemmel sıcaklık?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIRE.OUT"
msgid "Over already?"
msgstr "Bitti mi şimdiden?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.EMBERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.EMBERS"
msgid "We need more fuel for the fire!"
msgstr "Ateşe daha fazla yakıt lazım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.GENERIC"
msgid "Anyone want to hear a scary story?"
msgstr "Korkunç bir hikâye dinlemek isteyen var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.HIGH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.HIGH"
msgid "Woah! I don't think that's safe..."
msgstr "Vay! Bu hiç güvenli görünmüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.LOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.LOW"
msgid "I might need to feed the fire a bit."
msgstr "Ateşi biraz beslemem gerekebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.NORMAL"
msgid "It's the perfect temperature for... cold marshmallows?"
msgstr "Tam... soğuk lokum için mükemmel sıcaklık?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLDFIREPIT.OUT"
msgid "The fire pit's already built, all we need is more wood!"
msgstr "Ateş çukuru zaten kurulu, tek gereken daha çok odun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLLAPSEDCHEST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COLLAPSEDCHEST"
msgid "It looks pretty messed-up... but I think I could fix it!"
msgstr "Bayağı dağılmış görünüyor... ama bence tamir edebilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.E
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.E"
msgid "East."
msgstr "Doğu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.GENERIC"
msgid "The Pinetree Pioneer handbook says to always bring a compass!"
msgstr "Çamağacı Öncüsü el kitabı her zaman bir pusula getirmeyi söyler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.N
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.N"
msgid "North."
msgstr "Kuzey."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.NE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.NE"
msgid "Northeast."
msgstr "Kuzeydoğu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.NW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.NW"
msgid "Northwest."
msgstr "Kuzeybatı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.S
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.S"
msgid "South."
msgstr "Güney."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.SE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.SE"
msgid "Southeast."
msgstr "Güneydoğu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.SW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.SW"
msgid "Southwest."
msgstr "Güneybatı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.W
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPASS.W"
msgid "West."
msgstr "Batı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOST"
msgid "Nothing goes to waste!"
msgstr "Hiçbir şey çöpe gitmiyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.BALANCED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.BALANCED"
msgid "That looks pretty good!"
msgstr "Bayağı iyi görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.BURNT"
msgid "We should all really be more careful with fire!"
msgstr "Hepimiz ateş konusunda daha dikkatli olmalıyız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.DRY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.DRY"
msgid "Hm... does that look a bit too dry, Woby?"
msgstr "Hmm... biraz fazla kuru görünmüyor mu Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.GENERIC"
msgid "Oooh, compost bins usually have all kinds of interesting bugs in them!"
msgstr "Oooh, kompost kutularında genelde her türden ilginç böcek olur!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.WET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTINGBIN.WET"
msgid "This might be a bit too wet."
msgstr "Bu biraz fazla ıslak olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTWRAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COMPOSTWRAP"
msgid "Oh, uh... that's alright, I'm not hungry."
msgstr "Şey, ee... bir şey değil, aç değilim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CONSTRUCTION_PLANS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CONSTRUCTION_PLANS"
msgid "I'm good at following instructions! I have a badge for it!"
msgstr "Talimat izlemede iyiyim! Bunun için rozetim var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKBOOK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKBOOK"
msgid "Looks like I've got a new guide to memorize!"
msgstr "Görünüşe göre ezberlemem gereken yeni bir kılavuzum var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDMANDRAKE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDMANDRAKE"
msgid "Sorry little buddy."
msgstr "Üzgünüm küçük dostum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDMEAT"
msgid "You can't beat cooking outdoors!"
msgstr "Açık havada pişirmenin yerini hiçbir şey tutmaz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDMONSTERMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDMONSTERMEAT"
msgid "Is it supposed to have that weird aftertaste?"
msgstr "O garip ağız tadı olması gerekiyor mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDSMALLMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKEDSMALLMEAT"
msgid "A little meat is better than none."
msgstr "Az et, hiç yoktan iyidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKIECUTTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKIECUTTER"
msgid "They're smiling! Wait, I think I was looking at them upside-down."
msgstr "Gülümsüyorlar! Dur, sanırım onlara ters bakıyordum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKIECUTTERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKIECUTTERHAT"
msgid "It's a shellmet! Because it's a helmet, but a shell-- you get it."
msgstr "Bir kabukfer! Çünkü bir miğfer, ama kabuk-- anladın işte."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKIECUTTERSHELL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKIECUTTERSHELL"
msgid "These guys have tough armor!"
msgstr "Bu adamların zırhı sert!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKINGRECIPECARD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKINGRECIPECARD.GENERIC"
msgid "Woby, I can't read the recipe if you chew on the cards!"
msgstr "Woby, kartları çiğnersen tarifi okuyamam!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.BURNT"
msgid "It's uh... extra done!"
msgstr "Eee... fazladan pişmiş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.COOKING_LONG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.COOKING_LONG"
msgid "This might take a while. Wanna see this cool bug I found in the meantime?"
msgstr "Bu biraz sürebilir. Bu arada bulduğum süper böceği görmek ister misin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.COOKING_SHORT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.COOKING_SHORT"
msgid "Almost time to eat!"
msgstr "Yemek vakti yaklaştı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.DONE"
msgid "Come and get it!"
msgstr "Gelin ve alın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOKPOT.EMPTY"
msgid "Sure wish there was food in it."
msgstr "Keşke içinde yemek olsaydı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COOLANT"
msgid "I don't know what that stuff is, but I love it."
msgstr "O şeyin ne olduğunu bilmiyorum ama bayılıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COONTAIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COONTAIL"
msgid "It's a tall tail! Or, I guess more of a bushy one... never mind."
msgstr "Bu uzunca bir kuyruk-luk hikâye! Aslında daha çok kabarık bir tane... boş ver."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN"
msgid "Some corn on the cob sounds pretty good right about now."
msgstr "Şimdi koçanlı mısır iyi giderdi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN_COOKED"
msgid "I don't have anything to fund-raise for out here..."
msgstr "Burada bağış toplayacak bir şeyim yok..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Imagine all the popcorn we could make with that!"
msgstr "Bununla yapabileceğimiz tüm patlamış mısırı düşün!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CORN_SEEDS"
msgid "We should plant these."
msgstr "Bunları ekmeliyiz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_BLACKSMITH_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_BLACKSMITH_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_DOLL_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_DOLL_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_FOOL_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_FOOL_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_KING_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_KING_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_MIRROR_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_MIRROR_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_PRINCESS_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_PRINCESS_BODY"
msgid "Someone ponied up for this outfit."
msgstr "Birisi bu kıyafet için cebini açmış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_QUEEN_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_QUEEN_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_TREE_BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COSTUME_TREE_BODY"
msgid "Who would leave such a nice costume out in the wilderness?"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada böyle güzel bir kostümü kim bırakır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL1.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL1.GENERIC"
msgid "Come on Woby, we need to find some kindling!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby, biraz çıra bulmalıyız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL1.LIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL1.LIT"
msgid "That's one neat way to have a campfire!"
msgstr "İşte kamp ateşi yakmanın hoş bir yolu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL2.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL2.GENERIC"
msgid "Come on Woby, we need to find some kindling!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby, biraz çıra bulmalıyız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL2.LIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL2.LIT"
msgid "Wow, it looks so nice it's kind of hard to leave!"
msgstr "Vay, o kadar güzel görünüyor ki ayrılmak zor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL3.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL3.GENERIC"
msgid "Come on Woby, we need to find some kindling!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby, biraz çıra bulmalıyız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL3.LIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TABERNACLE_LEVEL3.LIT"
msgid "I think I'll stay here and watch it... just a bit longer."
msgstr "Sanırım burada kalıp izleyeceğim... biraz daha."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TRINKET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COTL_TRINKET"
msgid "I hope whoever lost it isn't missing it too much."
msgstr "Umarım kaybeden kişi onu çok özlemiyordur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COZY_BUNNYMAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.COZY_BUNNYMAN"
msgid "They seem friendly!"
msgstr "Dostça görünüyorlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING.GENERIC"
msgid "YES!! Now that's a proper sea monster!"
msgstr "EVET!! İşte düzgün bir deniz canavarı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING.INERT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING.INERT"
msgid "Who built this giant sand castle in the middle of the ocean?"
msgstr "Okyanusun ortasında bu dev kum kalesini kim yaptı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_CANNONTOWER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_CANNONTOWER"
msgid "Incoming!"
msgstr "Geliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_CLAW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_CLAW"
msgid "Woah! Look at the size of those claws!"
msgstr "Vay! Şu kıskaçların boyutuna bak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_ICEWALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_ICEWALL"
msgid "Just have to chip away at it."
msgstr "Yontmaya devam etmek lazım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_MOB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_MOB"
msgid "Watch out for those pinchers, Woby!"
msgstr "O kıskaçlara dikkat et Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_MOB_KNIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRABKING_MOB_KNIGHT"
msgid "Whoa! Cool crab!"
msgstr "Vay! Süper yengeç!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTERLAB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTERLAB"
msgid "What's wrong Woby? Is something in there?"
msgstr "Ne oldu Woby? İçeride bir şey mi var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_BULBIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_BULBIN"
msgid "I didn't know vegetables could be monsters too!"
msgstr "Sebzelerin de canavar olabileceğini bilmiyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_DRAGONLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_DRAGONLING"
msgid "Play nice with Woby, okay?"
msgstr "Woby ile nazik oyna, tamam mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_EYEOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_EYEOFTERROR"
msgid "What is it, boy? Do you see something?"
msgstr "Ne oldu oğlum? Bir şey mi görüyorsun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_GLOMLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_GLOMLING"
msgid "It's small for a monster, but big for a bug."
msgstr "Bir canavar için küçük ama bir böcek için büyük."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_KITTEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_KITTEN"
msgid "I'm usually more of a dog person, but you're so cute!"
msgstr "Genelde köpek seven biriyim ama sen çok tatlısın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LAMB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LAMB"
msgid "Aww, you're like a dust bunny that came to life!"
msgstr "Aaaa, canlanmış bir toz tüyüne benziyorsun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LUNARMOTHLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_LUNARMOTHLING"
msgid "Mom would never let me keep a pet bug this big!"
msgstr "Annem asla bu kadar büyük bir evcil böceği tutmama izin vermez!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PERDLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PERDLING"
msgid "What a funny little turkey."
msgstr "Ne komik küçük bir hindi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PUPPY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRITTER_PUPPY"
msgid "You and Woby will get along great!"
msgstr "Sen ve Woby çok iyi anlaşacaksınız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CROW.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CROW.GENERIC"
msgid "Finally, something I recognize from my bird guide!"
msgstr "Sonunda kuş kılavuzumdan tanıdığım bir şey!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CROW.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CROW.HELD"
msgid "A pocket isn't really the best place for a bird."
msgstr "Cep, bir kuş için pek de en iyi yer değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRUMBS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CRUMBS"
msgid "Maybe they dropped them to find their way home?"
msgstr "Belki eve dönüş yolunu bulmak için bırakmışlardır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CURSED_MONKEY_TOKEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CURSED_MONKEY_TOKEN"
msgid "This is definitely going in my collection."
msgstr "Bu kesinlikle koleksiyonuma giriyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTGRASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTGRASS"
msgid "Look, I can make a whistle with it! PHHWEEEE!"
msgstr "Bak, bununla düdük yapabilirim! FİİİYÜÜÜ!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTLESS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTLESS"
msgid "Toy swords are for little kids."
msgstr "Oyuncak kılıçlar küçük çocuklar içindir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTLICHEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTLICHEN"
msgid "This won't keep for long."
msgstr "Bu uzun süre dayanmaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTREEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTREEDS"
msgid "Ms. Wickerbottom might need some more... reed-ing material."
msgstr "Bayan Wickerbottom'a biraz daha... saz-ana malzeme lazım olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.CUTSTONE"
msgid "It wasn't too hard!"
msgstr "Pek zor değildi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.GENERIC"
msgid "I thought he'd be a bit happier to be free..."
msgstr "Özgür olduğu için biraz daha mutlu olur sanmıştım..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.IMPRISONED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER.IMPRISONED"
msgid "We can't just leave him like that, Woby! We've gotta help him!"
msgstr "Onu öyle bırakamayız Woby! Ona yardım etmeliyiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.BURIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.BURIED"
msgid "Should we help him, Woby?"
msgstr "Ona yardım edelim mi Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.GENERIC"
msgid "Don't worry, Woby. I think I can gain his trust."
msgstr "Merak etme Woby. Sanırım güvenini kazanabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.HOSTILE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER2.HOSTILE"
msgid "I still think we can be friends."
msgstr "Hâlâ arkadaş olabileceğimizi düşünüyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.EXPOSED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.EXPOSED"
msgid "Oh, it's just a different kind of rock."
msgstr "Aa, sadece farklı türde bir kaya."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DAYWALKER_PILLAR.GENERIC"
msgid "Hey, what's that stuff inside?"
msgstr "Hey, içindeki o şey ne?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEADLYFEAST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEADLYFEAST"
msgid "Someone could get sick from eating that!"
msgstr "Birisi bunu yiyince hasta olabilir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEAD_SEA_BONES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEAD_SEA_BONES"
msgid "These are definitely sea monster bones!"
msgstr "Bunlar kesinlikle deniz canavarı kemikleri!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNING"
msgid "You're supposed to chop the tree first, THEN build the fire!"
msgstr "Önce ağacı kesmen, SONRA ateşi yakman gerekirdi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.BURNT"
msgid "That tree just couldn't wait to be a campfire..."
msgstr "O ağaç kamp ateşi olmak için sabredememiş..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.CHOPPED"
msgid "This tree looks stumped. Heh, nice one Walter."
msgstr "Bu ağaç kütüğe oturdu. Hehe, iyiydi Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.GENERIC"
msgid "Did you know the word deciduous means to \"fall off\"?"
msgstr "Yaprak döken kelimesinin \"düşmek\" anlamına geldiğini biliyor muydun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.POISON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECIDUOUSTREE.POISON"
msgid "Woah! I've never seen a tree with teeth before!"
msgstr "Vay! Daha önce dişi olan bir ağaç görmemiştim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECK_OF_CARDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECK_OF_CARDS"
msgid "Woby! Pick a card, any card!"
msgstr "Woby! Bir kart seç, herhangi bir kart!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_CENTERPIECE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_CENTERPIECE"
msgid "It's cool. I guess."
msgstr "Hoşmuş. Sanırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.EMPTY"
msgid "Woby, did you eat the flower?"
msgstr "Woby, çiçeği sen mi yedin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.FRESHLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.FRESHLIGHT"
msgid "Oooh, useful."
msgstr "Oooh, faydalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.GENERIC"
msgid "Careful with that, Woby."
msgstr "Ona dikkat et Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.OLDLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.OLDLIGHT"
msgid "We should find a fresh one, Woby!"
msgstr "Taze bir tane bulmalıyız Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.WILTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_FLOWERVASE.WILTED"
msgid "It looks sad."
msgstr "Üzgün görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_LAMP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_LAMP"
msgid "Turn it off when we tell ghost stories."
msgstr "Hayalet hikâyeleri anlatırken kapat."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.GENERIC"
msgid "Is it upside down?"
msgstr "Ters mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.UNDRAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PICTUREFRAME.UNDRAWN"
msgid "Woby, wanna do a pawprint painting?"
msgstr "Woby, pati izi resmi yapmak ister misin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PORTRAITFRAME
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DECOR_PORTRAITFRAME"
msgid "It really looks like them! Right, Woby?"
msgstr "Tam onlara benziyor! Değil mi Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER.ANTLER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER.ANTLER"
msgid "You could poke an eye out with those! Maybe he already did?"
msgstr "Onlarla bir göz çıkarabilirsin! Belki zaten çıkarmıştır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER.GENERIC"
msgid "Hey Woby, do you guys go to the same barber?"
msgstr "Hey Woby, aynı berbere mi gidiyorsunuz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS"
msgid "Woah! It's you!"
msgstr "Vay! Sensin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.BURNING"
msgid "I'm going to miss her."
msgstr "Onu özleyeceğim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.GENERIC"
msgid "Poor Deerclops..."
msgstr "Zavallı Geyikgöz..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.REVIVING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSCORPSE.REVIVING"
msgid "Look Woby, she's okay!"
msgstr "Bak Woby, iyi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.GENERIC"
msgid "The way it just stares at me is so creepy. I love it."
msgstr "Bana öyle dik dik bakması çok ürkütücü. Bayıldım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.NOEYEBALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD.NOEYEBALL"
msgid "Something is missing. Woby, that eyeball is not a toy!"
msgstr "Bir şey eksik. Woby, o göz bir oyuncak değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPSEYEBALL_SENTRYWARD_KIT"
msgid "Woby, wanna help me put this together?"
msgstr "Woby, bunu birleştirmeme yardım eder misin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS_EYEBALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEERCLOPS_EYEBALL"
msgid "At least we got this souvenir."
msgstr "En azından bu hatırayı aldık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER_ANTLER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER_ANTLER"
msgid "Hey, you dropped this!"
msgstr "Hey, bunu düşürdün!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER_GEMMED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEER_GEMMED"
msgid "It can't be comfortable having a gem stuck in your forehead."
msgstr "Alnında bir mücevher takılı olması rahat olmasa gerek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEPLETED_GRASS.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEPLETED_GRASS.GENERIC"
msgid "It hasn't grown back yet."
msgstr "Henüz yeniden uzamamış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DESERTHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DESERTHAT"
msgid "It's important to dress appropriately for the environment."
msgstr "Ortama uygun giyinmek önemlidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DESICCANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DESICCANT"
msgid "No more wet dog smell for you, Woby!"
msgstr "Sana artık ıslak köpek kokusu yok Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DESICCANTBOOSTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DESICCANTBOOSTED"
msgid "It sure keeps me nice and dry."
msgstr "Beni güzelce kuru tutuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL"
msgid "Weird! It looks like an axe, but..."
msgstr "Garip! Bir baltaya benziyor ama..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL_NODEV
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DEVTOOL_NODEV"
msgid "Guess I haven't earned that badge yet."
msgstr "Galiba o rozeti henüz kazanmadım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIRTPILE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIRTPILE"
msgid "Woby, did you dig something up?"
msgstr "Woby, bir şey mi kazıp çıkardın?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.COLD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.COLD"
msgid "Getting colder... must've taken a wrong turn."
msgstr "Soğuyor... yanlış dönüş yapmış olmalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.GENERIC"
msgid "Hey! This looks a lot like that radio!"
msgstr "Hey! Bu radyoya çok benziyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.HOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.HOT"
msgid "We're hot on the trail, Woby!"
msgstr "İz sürüyoruz Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARM"
msgid "Getting warm..."
msgstr "Isınıyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARMER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGROD.WARMER"
msgid "Warmer..."
msgstr "Daha sıcak..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.GENERIC"
msgid "This looks important."
msgstr "Bu önemli görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.READY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.READY"
msgid "Maybe I can unlock it with something..."
msgstr "Belki bir şeyle açabilirim..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.UNLOCKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODBASE.UNLOCKED"
msgid "It worked!"
msgstr "İşe yaradı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODSTART
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DIVININGRODSTART"
msgid "Hey! This looks a lot like that radio!"
msgstr "Hey! Bu radyoya çok benziyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DOCK_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DOCK_KIT"
msgid "Neat, I can build a dock for my boat!"
msgstr "Süper, teknem için bir iskele yapabilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DOCK_WOODPOSTS_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DOCK_WOODPOSTS_ITEM"
msgid "Some posts will make the dock look even more... dock-y."
msgstr "Birkaç direk iskeleyi daha da... iskele-msi yapar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DOLL_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DOLL_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "Aww, it's cute!"
msgstr "Aaaa, çok tatlı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_KIT"
msgid "Stand back everyone, this looks like a job for a Pinetree Pioneer."
msgstr "Geri çekilin millet, bu bir Çamağacı Öncüsü işi gibi duruyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_PACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBOAT_PACK"
msgid "Wow, how did they pack this all up so tightly?"
msgstr "Vay, bunu nasıl bu kadar sıkı paketlemişler?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBODYHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONBODYHAT"
msgid "I think I'd be better in the lead."
msgstr "Bence başta daha iyi olurum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONCHILISALAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONCHILISALAD"
msgid "Is it made from real dragons?"
msgstr "Gerçek ejderhalardan mı yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLY"
msgid "Woah! It's a giant bug!"
msgstr "Vay! Bu dev bir böcek!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.GENERIC"
msgid "We'll have to find something worthy of going in there."
msgstr "İçine girmeye değer bir şey bulmamız gerekecek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.UPGRADED_STACKSIZE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYCHEST.UPGRADED_STACKSIZE"
msgid "The more supplies we can keep safe from fire, the better!"
msgstr "Ne kadar çok erzağı yangından koruyabilirsek o kadar iyi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.GENERIC"
msgid "Can I cook marshmallows over it though?"
msgstr "Ama üstünde lokum kızartabilir miyim?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HAMMERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HAMMERED"
msgid "...That didn't fix it."
msgstr "...O düzeltmedi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HIGH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.HIGH"
msgid "Roasty!"
msgstr "Kavurucu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFLYFURNACE.NORMAL"
msgid "Toasty!"
msgstr "Sıcacık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT"
msgid "Looks tasty."
msgstr "Lezzetli görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_COOKED"
msgid "It makes sense that Dragon Fruit tastes better with fire."
msgstr "Ejder Meyvesinin ateşle daha iyi tat vermesi mantıklı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Unfortunately, not a real dragon."
msgstr "Maalesef gerçek bir ejderha değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONFRUIT_SEEDS"
msgid "Let's find some place to plant these."
msgstr "Bunları ekecek bir yer bulalım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONHEADHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONHEADHAT"
msgid "I'll be the leader!"
msgstr "Ben lider olacağım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONPIE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONPIE"
msgid "Is it made from actual dragons?"
msgstr "Gerçek ejderhalardan mı yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONTAILHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGONTAILHAT"
msgid "I don't want the back end..."
msgstr "Arka kısmını istemiyorum..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGON_SCALES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRAGON_SCALES"
msgid "Was she a bug or a lizard?"
msgstr "O bir böcek miydi yoksa kertenkele miydi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE"
msgid "It's just a rock, what's so scary about a rock?"
msgstr "Sadece bir kaya, bir kayanın korkutucu nesi var ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONEHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONEHAT"
msgid "Never forget to wear your dark helmet."
msgstr "Karanlık miğferini takmayı asla unutma."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE_STACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DREADSTONE_STACK"
msgid "I bet there's more buried deep underground!"
msgstr "Bahse girerim yer altında daha derinde gömülü olanlar var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_LOG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_LOG"
msgid "You'll float too, if you hold onto it!"
msgstr "Buna tutunursan sen de yüzersin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNING"
msgid "You're supposed to make a pit, gather the firewood and THEN make a fire!"
msgstr "Önce çukur açman, odunu toplaman ve SONRA ateş yakman gerekirdi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.BURNT"
msgid "That could've been bad."
msgstr "Bu kötü olabilirdi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.CHOPPED"
msgid "Thanks for the firewood, tree!"
msgstr "Odun için sağ ol ağaç!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRIFTWOOD_TREE.GENERIC"
msgid "Looks kind of eerie, doesn't it?"
msgstr "Biraz tekinsiz görünüyor, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK"
msgid "Is it a good idea to eat raw meat...?"
msgstr "Çiğ et yemek iyi bir fikir mi...?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DRUMSTICK_COOKED"
msgid "That's better!"
msgstr "Bu daha iyi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_BANANABUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_BANANABUSH"
msgid "Wait, I thought bananas grew on trees around here?"
msgstr "Dur, buralarda muzun ağaçta yetiştiğini sanıyordum?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH"
msgid "Come on berry bush, we're going on an adventure!"
msgstr "Hadi yemiş çalısı, maceraya çıkıyoruz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH_JUICY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_BERRYBUSH_JUICY"
msgid "Come on berry bush, we're going on an adventure!"
msgstr "Hadi yemiş çalısı, maceraya çıkıyoruz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_GRASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_GRASS"
msgid "Now I can plant it closer to camp."
msgstr "Artık kampa daha yakın ekebilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_MARSH_BUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_MARSH_BUSH"
msgid "Hey Woby, do you see a good spot to plant this?"
msgstr "Hey Woby, bunu ekecek iyi bir yer görüyor musun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_MONKEYTAIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_MONKEYTAIL"
msgid "I wonder if there's any real monkeys hiding in there?"
msgstr "Acaba içinde gerçek maymun saklanıyor mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_SAPLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_SAPLING"
msgid "Hey Woby, do you see a good spot to plant this?"
msgstr "Hey Woby, bunu ekecek iyi bir yer görüyor musun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_TRAP_STARFISH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUG_TRAP_STARFISH"
msgid "I'm putting them in time out."
msgstr "Onları ceza köşesine koyuyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL"
msgid "I can do it! I just... need to get a good grip on it!"
msgstr "Yapabilirim! Sadece... iyi bir şekilde kavramam gerekiyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_BLUEGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_BLUEGEM"
msgid "You'll get a really n-ice workout with that! Heh. Good one, Walter."
msgstr "Bununla buz-meyiş bir antrenman yapacaksın! Hehe. İyiydi Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GEM"
msgid "Time to hit the gem! Get it? Because gem sounds like gym?"
msgstr "Mücevhere koyulma vakti! Anladın mı? Çünkü mücevher spor salonu gibi geliyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GOLDEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_GOLDEN"
msgid "Uh, m-maybe I should start with something a bit lighter."
msgstr "Şey, b-belki biraz daha hafifle başlamalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_HEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_HEAT"
msgid "I can warm up without lifting anything! N-not that I can't!"
msgstr "Bir şey kaldırmadan ısınabilirim! Y-yapamıyorum demiyorum tabii!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_MARBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_MARBLE"
msgid "Oh... when he said it was made of marble, I kind of hoped he meant the tiny ones."
msgstr "Aaa... mermerden yapıldığını söylediğinde, küçüklerini kastediyor sanmıştım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_REDGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUMBBELL_REDGEM"
msgid "I don't think your muscles should be burning THAT much..."
msgstr "Kaslarının O kadar yanması gerekmemeli..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN"
msgid "Yuck! What is that?"
msgstr "Iyy! Bu da ne?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_COOKED"
msgid "No thank you."
msgstr "Hayır teşekkürler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Why did this one have to grow so big?"
msgstr "Bu neden bu kadar büyümek zorundaydı ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DURIAN_SEEDS"
msgid "Yep, those are seeds!"
msgstr "Aha, bunlar tohum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUSTMERINGUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUSTMERINGUE"
msgid "Uh... no thanks. Maybe the moths will like it?"
msgstr "Şey... hayır teşekkürler. Belki güveler beğenir?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTH"
msgid "Can I keep them? Pleeeaaaase?"
msgstr "Onları besleyebilir miyim? Lüüütfeeen?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTHDEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.DUSTMOTHDEN"
msgid "Woah, so that's where that weird material comes from!"
msgstr "Vay, demek o garip malzeme buradan geliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EARMUFFSHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EARMUFFSHAT"
msgid "Some of us don't have ear fluff of our own, Woby."
msgstr "Bazılarımızın kulak tüyü yok Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EEL"
msgid "Look at the teeth it has!"
msgstr "Şu dişlerine bak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EEL_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EEL_COOKED"
msgid "That actually smells pretty good!"
msgstr "Aslında epey güzel kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT"
msgid "Even in the wilderness you have to eat your vegetables."
msgstr "Vahşi doğada bile sebzelerini yemen gerekiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_COOKED"
msgid "Oh, it's much better cooked!"
msgstr "Aa, pişince çok daha iyi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Oh... great! I guess we're eating eggplant for the next week..."
msgstr "Aaa... harika! Galiba önümüzdeki bir hafta patlıcan yiyeceğiz..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EGGPLANT_SEEDS"
msgid "We should find a place to plant these."
msgstr "Bunları ekecek bir yer bulmalıyız."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ELIXIR_CONTAINER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ELIXIR_CONTAINER"
msgid "Contents not safe for human consumption!"
msgstr "İçindekiler insan tüketimi için güvenli değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EMBERLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EMBERLIGHT"
msgid "There's no wood in this campfire. Oh well."
msgstr "Bu kamp ateşinde odun yok. Eh, neyse."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.BURNT"
msgid "That's how forest fires get started!"
msgstr "Orman yangınları işte böyle başlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.EMPTY"
msgid "Hey... I think I saw something move under there."
msgstr "Hey... Sanırım altında bir şeyin hareket ettiğini gördüm."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.FRESHLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.FRESHLIGHT"
msgid "Ta-da! Light!"
msgstr "Tada! Işık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.GENERIC"
msgid "Is somebody decorating out here?"
msgstr "Burada birisi süsleme mi yapıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.OLDLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.OLDLIGHT"
msgid "Looks like we need to replace a bulb."
msgstr "Galiba bir ampul değiştirmemiz lazım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.WILTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ENDTABLE.WILTED"
msgid "Those flowers are looking pretty sad."
msgstr "O çiçekler bayağı üzgün görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNING"
msgid "You're supposed to chop the tree first, THEN build the fire!"
msgstr "Önce ağacı kesmen, SONRA ateşi yakman gerekirdi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.BURNT"
msgid "That tree just couldn't wait to be a campfire..."
msgstr "O ağaç kamp ateşi olmak için sabredememiş..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.CHOPPED"
msgid "This tree looks stumped. Heh, nice one Walter."
msgstr "Bu ağaç kütüğe oturdu. Hehe, iyiydi Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN.GENERIC"
msgid "They're called \"evergreen\" because... well you get the idea."
msgstr "Adına \"hep yeşil\" deniyor çünkü... şey anladın işte."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNING"
msgid "You're supposed to chop the tree first, THEN build the fire!"
msgstr "Önce ağacı kesmen, SONRA ateşi yakman gerekirdi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.BURNT"
msgid "That tree just couldn't wait to be a campfire..."
msgstr "O ağaç kamp ateşi olmak için sabredememiş..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.CHOPPED"
msgid "This tree looks stumped. Heh, nice one Walter."
msgstr "Bu ağaç kütüğe oturdu. Hehe, iyiydi Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EVERGREEN_SPARSE.GENERIC"
msgid "What a scraggly tree."
msgstr "Ne çelimsiz bir ağaç."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEBRELLAHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEBRELLAHAT"
msgid "It keeps an eye on me. Get it? Because it's a giant eyeball?"
msgstr "Üstüme göz kulak oluyor. Anladın mı? Çünkü dev bir göz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEMASKHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEMASKHAT"
msgid "Don't worry Woby. It's just a hat, see?"
msgstr "Merak etme Woby. Sadece bir şapka, gördün mü?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR"
msgid "Wow! Do you think it escaped from a giant head?"
msgstr "Vay! Sence dev bir kafadan mı kaçtı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI"
msgid "Would you say they're... multipl-eying? Heh. Good one, Walter."
msgstr "Onlara... göz-alıcı çoğaldılar mı dersin? Hehe. İyiydi Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI_GROUNDED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEOFTERROR_MINI_GROUNDED"
msgid "Ohh, so that's how baby eyeballs are made."
msgstr "Aa, demek bebek göz küreleri böyle yapılıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYEPLANT"
msgid "Eye bet it's friendly!"
msgstr "Gözüm üstünde, dostça!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET"
msgid "It's keeping an eye on me! Get it? Because it's... you know..."
msgstr "Üstüme göz kulak oluyor! Anladın mı? Çünkü o... bilirsin..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.EYETURRET_ITEM"
msgid "Come on Woby, let's find a good place to put this!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby, bunu koyacak iyi bir yer bulalım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.BURNT"
msgid "Darnit, now I have to start all over!"
msgstr "Of be, şimdi her şeye baştan başlamam lazım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GENERIC"
msgid "Mom never let me in her garden... not since the Slug Incident."
msgstr "Annem beni bahçesine asla sokmadı... Sümüklüböcek Vakası'ndan beri."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GROWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.GROWING"
msgid "Hey! I'm pretty good at this!"
msgstr "Hey! Bu işte epey iyiyim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.NEEDSFERTILIZER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARMPLOT.NEEDSFERTILIZER"
msgid "It needs something to help it grow..."
msgstr "Büyümesine yardım edecek bir şeye ihtiyacı var..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_HOE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_HOE"
msgid "We'll need that to plant seeds."
msgstr "Tohum ekmek için buna ihtiyacımız olacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.BURNING"
msgid "They uh... might need some water."
msgstr "Onlara şey... biraz su lazım olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL"
msgid "I think it's ready to pick!"
msgstr "Sanırım toplanmaya hazır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Woah, what a monster!"
msgstr "Vay, ne canavarmış!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_WEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.FULL_WEED"
msgid "Hey, you're not a vegetable!"
msgstr "Hey, sen sebze değilsin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GENERIC"
msgid "That's one of our plants."
msgstr "Bu bizim bitkilerimizden biri."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GROWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.GROWING"
msgid "I'll take good care of you, don't you worry."
msgstr "Sana iyi bakacağım, merak etme."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN"
msgid "Whoops... I probably should've picked that sooner."
msgstr "Eyvah... Onu muhtemelen daha önce toplamalıydım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.ROTTEN_OVERSIZED"
msgid "It's all rotten!"
msgstr "Hepsi çürümüş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.SEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLANT.SEED"
msgid "Look Woby, it's growing!"
msgstr "Bak Woby, büyüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW"
msgid "Hey, farming doesn't seem too hard!"
msgstr "Hey, çiftçilik pek zor görünmüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_PLOW_ITEM"
msgid "Want to help me find a good place for the garden, Woby?"
msgstr "Bahçe için iyi bir yer bulmamda yardım eder misin Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_SOIL_DEBRIS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FARM_SOIL_DEBRIS"
msgid "We'd better clean that up."
msgstr "Onu temizlesek iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHERFAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHERFAN"
msgid "I'm a big fan of staying cool. Get it, because it's a fan?"
msgstr "Serin kalmanın büyük hayranıyım. Anladın mı, çünkü bu bir yelpaze?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHERHAT"
msgid "And I thought my bird watching badge was a feather in my cap!"
msgstr "Bir de kuş gözlemi rozetimi kavuğumun süsü sanmıştım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHERPENCIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHERPENCIL"
msgid "I feel like I should write something poetic with this..."
msgstr "Bununla şiirsel bir şeyler yazmalıyım gibi geliyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CANARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CANARY"
msgid "Looks like a canary feather."
msgstr "Kanarya tüyüne benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CROW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_CROW"
msgid "Looks like a black bird feather."
msgstr "Siyah kuş tüyüne benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN"
msgid "Looks like a redbird feather."
msgstr "Kızıl kuş tüyüne benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN_WINTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEATHER_ROBIN_WINTER"
msgid "Looks like a snowbird feather."
msgstr "Karkuşu tüyüne benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEM_PUPPET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FEM_PUPPET"
msgid "Don't worry, a Pinetree Pioneer always helps those in need!"
msgstr "Merak etme, bir Çamağacı Öncüsü her zaman ihtiyacı olanlara yardım eder!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE"
msgid "Why do we need fences? It's the great outdoors!"
msgstr "Çitlere ne gerek var ki? Burası muhteşem açık hava!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.GENERIC"
msgid "Don't worry, Wobes. It's not connected."
msgstr "Merak etme Wobes. Bağlı değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.LINKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC.LINKED"
msgid "Stay back, Woby!"
msgstr "Geri dur Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ELECTRIC_ITEM"
msgid "We have to plant it first."
msgstr "Önce dikmemiz lazım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE"
msgid "It's open-and-shut."
msgstr "Açılır-kapanır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_GATE_ITEM"
msgid "I guess I should find someplace to put that."
msgstr "Galiba onu koyacak bir yer bulmalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ITEM"
msgid "Why fence in nature?"
msgstr "Doğayı niye çitlemek?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_JUNK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_JUNK"
msgid "I guess it's better than just leaving all that scrap metal lying around."
msgstr "Galiba o kadar hurda metali öylece bırakmaktan iyidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ROTATOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FENCE_ROTATOR"
msgid "Huh. I didn't know people used swords to fix their fences."
msgstr "Vay. İnsanların çitlerini onarmak için kılıç kullandığını bilmiyordum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FERTILIZER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FERTILIZER"
msgid "Plants love poop."
msgstr "Bitkiler kakaya bayılır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FESTIVEFISH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FESTIVEFISH"
msgid "Fish with some special seasonal seasonings."
msgstr "Özel mevsimsel baharatlarla balık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FESTIVE_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FESTIVE_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "I wish I could make one for Woby, but her measurements keep changing..."
msgstr "Keşke Woby'ye de bir tane yapabilseydim ama ölçüleri sürekli değişiyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIG"
msgid "I don't really like figs..."
msgstr "İnciri pek sevmem..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIGATONI
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIGATONI"
msgid "At least the fig's hidden inside."
msgstr "En azından incir içinde gizli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIGKABAB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIGKABAB"
msgid "Aw, did it have to be figs?"
msgstr "Aaa, illa incir mi olmalıydı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIG_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIG_COOKED"
msgid "I don't really like cooked figs any better..."
msgstr "Pişmiş inciri de pek sevmem..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREBALLSTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREBALLSTAFF"
msgid "It calls a meteor from above."
msgstr "Yukarıdan göktaşı çağırıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRECRACKERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRECRACKERS"
msgid "You're not supposed to set those off in the woods."
msgstr "Onları ormanda patlatman gerekmiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREFLIES.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREFLIES.GENERIC"
msgid "I wish I had a jar."
msgstr "Keşke bir kavanozum olsaydı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREFLIES.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREFLIES.HELD"
msgid "Hope they get along with the other bugs in my pockets."
msgstr "Umarım cebimdeki diğer böceklerle anlaşırlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREHOUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREHOUND"
msgid "Who's a good boy?"
msgstr "Kim iyi bir oğlan?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRENETTLES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRENETTLES"
msgid "They're even worse than poison oak!"
msgstr "Zehirli sumaktan bile beterler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRENETTLES_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRENETTLES_DRIED"
msgid "Dried perfectly!"
msgstr "Mükemmel kurumuş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPEN"
msgid "I had no idea writing was so dangerous."
msgstr "Yazmanın bu kadar tehlikeli olduğunu bilmiyordum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.EMBERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.EMBERS"
msgid "We need more fuel for the fire!"
msgstr "Ateşe daha fazla yakıt lazım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.GENERIC"
msgid "Anyone want to hear a scary story?"
msgstr "Korkunç bir hikâye dinlemek isteyen var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.HIGH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.HIGH"
msgid "Woah! I don't think that's safe..."
msgstr "Vay! Bu hiç güvenli görünmüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.LOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.LOW"
msgid "I might need to feed the fire a bit."
msgstr "Ateşi biraz beslemem gerekebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.NORMAL"
msgid "It's the perfect temperature for roasting marshmallows!"
msgstr "Lokum kızartmak için mükemmel sıcaklık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIREPIT.OUT"
msgid "The fire pit's already built, all we need is more wood!"
msgstr "Ateş çukuru zaten kurulu, tek gereken daha çok odun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESTAFF"
msgid "I'd better keep this away from the younger kids... and Willow."
msgstr "Bunu küçüklerden uzak tutsam iyi olur... ve Willow'dan."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESUPPRESSOR.LOWFUEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESUPPRESSOR.LOWFUEL"
msgid "We'd better give it some more fuel."
msgstr "Ona biraz daha yakıt versek iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESUPPRESSOR.OFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESUPPRESSOR.OFF"
msgid "It's conserving its energy."
msgstr "Enerjisini koruyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESUPPRESSOR.ON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FIRESUPPRESSOR.ON"
msgid "That should keep us from setting the camp on fire... hopefully."
msgstr "Bu bizi kampı yakmaktan korumalı... umarım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISH"
msgid "I'm great at catching fish! I got a badge and everything!"
msgstr "Balık tutmada harikayım! Rozetim falan da var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHINGNET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHINGNET"
msgid "Hey Woby, want to go fishing?"
msgstr "Hey Woby, balığa çıkalım mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHINGROD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHINGROD"
msgid "It's a fishing rod, you use it for fishing."
msgstr "Bu bir olta kamışı, balık tutmak için kullanılır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT"
msgid "Is it okay to eat it raw?"
msgstr "Çiğ yemek sorun mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_COOKED"
msgid "Catching your own fish and eating it, real survivor stuff!"
msgstr "Kendi balığını tutup yemek, gerçek hayatta kalma işi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_DRIED"
msgid "That's some good fish jerky!"
msgstr "İşte güzel bir kuru balık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_SMALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_SMALL"
msgid "Maybe I could use it as bait for a bigger fish."
msgstr "Belki daha büyük bir balığa yem olarak kullanabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_SMALL_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_SMALL_COOKED"
msgid "It smells good!"
msgstr "Güzel kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_SMALL_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHMEAT_SMALL_DRIED"
msgid "A little jerky is better than none."
msgstr "Az kuru et, hiç yoktan iyidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHSTICKS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHSTICKS"
msgid "Delicious, nutritious and full of fishes."
msgstr "Lezzetli, besleyici ve balık dolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHTACOS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISHTACOS"
msgid "The s'more of fish dishes!"
msgstr "Balık yemeklerinin lokum şenliği!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISH_BOX
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISH_BOX"
msgid "That'll keep our fish fresh!"
msgstr "Bu balıklarımızı taze tutacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISH_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FISH_COOKED"
msgid "Catching and cooking your own fish is what camping is all about!"
msgstr "Kendi balığını tutup pişirmek, kampçılığın özü budur!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLINT"
msgid "This should come in handy!"
msgstr "Bu işe yarayacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOATINGLANTERN.DEFLATED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOATINGLANTERN.DEFLATED"
msgid "Aw, it was nice while it lasted."
msgstr "Aaa, sürdüğü kadarıyla güzeldi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOATINGLANTERN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOATINGLANTERN.GENERIC"
msgid "Look up, Woby!"
msgstr "Yukarı bak Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOATINGLANTERN.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOATINGLANTERN.HELD"
msgid "Should we brighten the mood, Wobes?"
msgstr "Havayı aydınlatalım mı Wobes?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOTATIONCUSHION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOTATIONCUSHION"
msgid "We love water safety! Don't we, Wobes?"
msgstr "Su güvenliğine bayılıyoruz! Değil mi Wobes?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER.GENERIC"
msgid "Are there any bugs on it?"
msgstr "Üstünde böcek var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER.ROSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER.ROSE"
msgid "Funny, this isn't the type of rose you usually see in the wild."
msgstr "Garip, bu vahşi doğada genelde görülen gül türü değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWERHAT"
msgid "Hey, that looks swell!"
msgstr "Hey, çok güzel görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWERSALAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWERSALAD"
msgid "Even scavenged leaves can be food in the wilderness!"
msgstr "Vahşi doğada toplanmış yapraklar bile yemek olabilir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_CAVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_CAVE"
msgid "Pretty swell of those flowers to light the way for us!"
msgstr "O çiçeklerin bize yolu aydınlatması ne hoş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_CAVE_WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_CAVE_WITHERED"
msgid "I wonder why it's dying."
msgstr "Acaba neden ölüyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_EVIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_EVIL"
msgid "Woby, what's wrong? It's just a flower."
msgstr "Woby, ne oldu? Sadece bir çiçek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FLOWER_WITHERED"
msgid "Should I water it more? Or water it less?!"
msgstr "Daha fazla mı sulamalıyım? Yoksa daha az mı?!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOLIAGE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOLIAGE"
msgid "This would be great for starting a campfire."
msgstr "Bu kamp ateşi yakmak için harika olurdu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOLIAGE_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOLIAGE_DRIED"
msgid "Dried perfectly!"
msgstr "Mükemmel kurumuş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOOTBALLHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOOTBALLHAT"
msgid "Oh, football! Yeah I'm uh... great at football..."
msgstr "Aa, futbol! Evet, ben şey... futbolda harikayım..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FORGETMELOTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FORGETMELOTS"
msgid "I keep forgetting to look them up in my handbook."
msgstr "El kitabımdan bakmayı sürekli unutuyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FORGETMELOTS_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FORGETMELOTS_DRIED"
msgid "Dried perfectly!"
msgstr "Mükemmel kurumuş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FORMAL_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FORMAL_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "This doesn't seem very practical for the outdoors."
msgstr "Bu açık hava için pek pratik durmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_PIECE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_PIECE"
msgid "The bones of an ancient creature!"
msgstr "Kadim bir yaratığın kemikleri!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_STALKER.COMPLETE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_STALKER.COMPLETE"
msgid "I think we figured it out Woby!"
msgstr "Sanırım çözdük Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_STALKER.FUNNY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_STALKER.FUNNY"
msgid "\"The arm bone's connected to the...\" which bone was it..."
msgstr "\"Kol kemiği bağlanır...\" hangi kemikti..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_STALKER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FOSSIL_STALKER.GENERIC"
msgid "It's still missing something."
msgstr "Hâlâ bir şeyi eksik."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRESHFRUITCREPES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRESHFRUITCREPES"
msgid "With fresh-picked wild fruits."
msgstr "Taze toplanmış vahşi meyvelerle."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRIENDLYFRUITFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRIENDLYFRUITFLY"
msgid "I'm going to call you Buzzy!"
msgstr "Sana Vızvız diyeceğim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROG.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROG.DEAD"
msgid "Poor little guy."
msgstr "Zavallı küçük dostum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROG.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROG.GENERIC"
msgid "That doesn't look like the frogs in my handbook..."
msgstr "El kitabımdaki kurbağalara benzemiyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROG.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROG.SLEEPING"
msgid "Have sweet, fly-filled dreams."
msgstr "Tatlı, sinek dolu rüyalar gör."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGFISHBOWL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGFISHBOWL"
msgid "Er... maybe Woby wants some."
msgstr "Şey... belki Woby ister."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGGLEBUNWICH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGGLEBUNWICH"
msgid "You can make anything into a sandwich if you try hard enough."
msgstr "Yeterince uğraşırsan her şeyi sandviç yapabilirsin."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGLEGS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGLEGS"
msgid "I don't think they're ripe yet, they're still green."
msgstr "Sanırım daha olgunlaşmamışlar, hâlâ yeşiller."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGLEGS_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGLEGS_COOKED"
msgid "It doesn't look as fancy as I imagined."
msgstr "Hayal ettiğim kadar şık görünmüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGNEWTON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROGNEWTON"
msgid "Hey, that's pretty good! What's in it?"
msgstr "Hey, bayağı güzel! İçinde ne var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROZENBANANADAIQUIRI
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FROZENBANANADAIQUIRI"
msgid "Don't drink it too fast or you'll get a headache."
msgstr "Çok hızlı içme yoksa başın ağrır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITDRAGON.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITDRAGON.GENERIC"
msgid "It's a little lizard thing!"
msgstr "Küçük bir kertenkele şeyi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITDRAGON.RIPE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITDRAGON.RIPE"
msgid "I could've sworn it was green a second ago."
msgstr "Yemin ederim bir saniye önce yeşildi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITDRAGON.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITDRAGON.SLEEPING"
msgid "They're even cuter when they're sleeping."
msgstr "Uyurken daha da tatlılar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITFLY"
msgid "They're just doing what bugs do! I wish they wouldn't do it to my plants though..."
msgstr "Sadece böceklerin yaptığını yapıyorlar! Keşke bitkilerime yapmasalardı..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITFLYFRUIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITFLYFRUIT"
msgid "The Fruit Flies seem to like following it around."
msgstr "Meyve Sinekleri etrafında takılmaya bayılıyor gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITMEDLEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FRUITMEDLEY"
msgid "It's good for you!"
msgstr "Sana iyi gelir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FURTUFT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FURTUFT"
msgid "It's so soft!"
msgstr "Çok yumuşak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FUSED_SHADELING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FUSED_SHADELING"
msgid "Woby, look! It has a ball on its tail!"
msgstr "Woby, bak! Kuyruğunda bir top var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FUSED_SHADELING_BOMB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.FUSED_SHADELING_BOMB"
msgid "Woah! The ball's alive!"
msgstr "Vay! Top canlı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARGOYLE_HOUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARGOYLE_HOUND"
msgid "Wouldn't it be funny if it came to life?"
msgstr "Canlansa komik olmaz mıydı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARGOYLE_WEREPIG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARGOYLE_WEREPIG"
msgid "Don't worry Woby, it's just a statue."
msgstr "Merak etme Woby, sadece bir heykel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC"
msgid "Wards off the vampires."
msgstr "Vampirleri uzak tutuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC_COOKED"
msgid "Too bad vampires never get to enjoy it."
msgstr "Vampirler keyfine asla varamayacak ne yazık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Well, we'll be safe from giant vampires now."
msgstr "Şey, artık dev vampirlerden güvendeyiz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GARLIC_SEEDS"
msgid "Where should we plant them, Woby?"
msgstr "Onları nereye ekelim Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GAZPACHO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GAZPACHO"
msgid "(Sigh) I know it's probably good for me..."
msgstr "(İç çek) Bana iyi geleceğini biliyorum..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GEARS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GEARS"
msgid "These don't usually occur in nature."
msgstr "Bunlar genelde doğada bulunmaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB.GENERIC"
msgid "Don't get stuck, Woby!"
msgstr "Sıkışma Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB.HAS_CHARACTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB.HAS_CHARACTER"
msgid "Are you in need of assistance?"
msgstr "Yardıma mı ihtiyacınız var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB.HAS_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB.HAS_ITEM"
msgid "Do you see what's inside, Woby?"
msgstr "İçinde ne olduğunu görüyor musun Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_BOTTLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_BOTTLE"
msgid "We really should label that."
msgstr "Onu etiketlemeliyiz cidden."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_STORAGE.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_STORAGE.FULL"
msgid "It's floating in that gloop!"
msgstr "O sümüğün içinde yüzüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_STORAGE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_STORAGE.GENERIC"
msgid "What should we put in there, Woby?"
msgstr "Oraya ne koyalım Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_STORAGE_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GELBLOB_STORAGE_KIT"
msgid "This might be messy to build."
msgstr "Bunu kurması dağınık olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GEMSOCKET.GEMS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GEMSOCKET.GEMS"
msgid "I need to put in the gems first."
msgstr "Önce mücevherleri koymam lazım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GEMSOCKET.VALID
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GEMSOCKET.VALID"
msgid "Ready to go."
msgstr "Gitmeye hazır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GENERIC_CORPSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GENERIC_CORPSE.BURNING"
msgid "We gotta make sure it doesn't rise from the dead!"
msgstr "Ölümden geri dönmediğinden emin olmalıyız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GENERIC_CORPSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GENERIC_CORPSE.GENERIC"
msgid "That's just how things go in the wilderness, sometimes."
msgstr "Vahşi doğada bazen işler böyle yürür."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GENERIC_CORPSE.REVIVING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GENERIC_CORPSE.REVIVING"
msgid "Woby! It's back from the dead!"
msgstr "Woby! Ölümden geri döndü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT"
msgid "Are you a ghost... from the moon?"
msgstr "Sen ay'dan gelen... bir hayalet misin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_CAGE.FILLED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_CAGE.FILLED"
msgid "Yup, we got one, Woby!"
msgstr "Aha, bir tane yakaladık Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_CAGE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_CAGE.GENERIC"
msgid "It's empty, Wobes."
msgstr "Boş Wobes."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_GUARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_GUARD"
msgid "Wow, they reeaally don't like those shadow creatures."
msgstr "Vay, o gölge yaratıklarından gerçeeeekten hoşlanmıyorlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_GUARD_EVOLVED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GESTALT_GUARD_EVOLVED"
msgid "Wobes! I think we're the unfinished business for these ghosts!"
msgstr "Wobes! Sanırım biz bu hayaletlerin yarım kalmış işiyiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOST"
msgid "Ha, and people tried to tell me ghosts aren't real."
msgstr "Ha, bir de insanlar bana hayaletlerin gerçek olmadığını söylemeye çalıştı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTFLOWER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTFLOWER"
msgid "Spooky!"
msgstr "Ürkütücü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTFLOWERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTFLOWERHAT"
msgid "I guess it's kinda haunted."
msgstr "Galiba biraz perili."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_ATTACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_ATTACK"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_FASTREGEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_FASTREGEN"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_LUNAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_LUNAR"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_RETALIATION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_RETALIATION"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_REVIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_REVIVE"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SHADOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SHADOW"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SHIELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SHIELD"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SLOWREGEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SLOWREGEN"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SPEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GHOSTLYELIXIR_SPEED"
msgid "Ghosts can drink potions? Uh, of course I knew that!"
msgstr "Hayaletler iksir içebilir mi? Şey, tabii ki biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GIFT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GIFT"
msgid "A present!"
msgstr "Bir hediye!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GIFTWRAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GIFTWRAP"
msgid "I'm not great at wrapping things... it always ends up a crumpled ball."
msgstr "Paketleme konusunda harika değilim... hep buruşuk bir top oluyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GINGERBREADHOUSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GINGERBREADHOUSE"
msgid "What do they do when it rains?"
msgstr "Yağmur yağdığında ne yapıyorlar?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GINGERBREADPIG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GINGERBREADPIG"
msgid "Is that cookie alive?!"
msgstr "O kurabiye canlı mı?!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GINGERBREADWARG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GINGERBREADWARG"
msgid "Who's a sweet Varg? Yes you are!"
msgstr "Kim tatlı bir Varg? Evet sensin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLASSBLOCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLASSBLOCK"
msgid "It looks nice I guess."
msgstr "Galiba güzel görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLASSCUTTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLASSCUTTER"
msgid "Moon sword!!"
msgstr "Ay kılıcı!!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLASSSPIKE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLASSSPIKE"
msgid "It looks like a giant tooth from a glass monster!"
msgstr "Cam canavarından dev bir dişe benziyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMER.GENERIC"
msgid "Don't be jealous Woby, you'll always be my best friend."
msgstr "Kıskanma Woby, her zaman benim en iyi arkadaşım olacaksın."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMER.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMER.SLEEPING"
msgid "He must be tired from doing... whatever he does all day."
msgstr "Tüm gün... her ne yapıyorsa onu yapmaktan yorulmuş olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERFLOWER.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERFLOWER.DEAD"
msgid "Darnit... what did I do wrong?"
msgstr "Of be... neyi yanlış yaptım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERFLOWER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERFLOWER.GENERIC"
msgid "That flower isn't in my Pinetree Pioneer handbook."
msgstr "O çiçek Çamağacı Öncüsü el kitabımda yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERFUEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERFUEL"
msgid "Don't eat it, Woby!"
msgstr "Yeme onu Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERWINGS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOMMERWINGS"
msgid "How did he fly with these little wings?"
msgstr "Bu küçük kanatlarla nasıl uçabilmiş?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOWBERRYMOUSSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GLOWBERRYMOUSSE"
msgid "Will my insides light up if I eat it?"
msgstr "Bunu yersem içim aydınlanır mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.BROKENHORN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.BROKENHORN"
msgid "Oh no! You lost your horn!"
msgstr "Eyvah! Boynuzunu kaybetmişsin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.BROKENHORN_FOLLOWER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.BROKENHORN_FOLLOWER"
msgid "I sure hope your horn grows back."
msgstr "Umarım boynuzun yeniden çıkar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.FOLLOWER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.FOLLOWER"
msgid "See? We can all get along!"
msgstr "Gördün mü? Hepimiz anlaşabiliriz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL.GENERIC"
msgid "Unicorns of the sea."
msgstr "Denizin tek boynuzlu atları."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL_HORN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GNARWAIL_HORN"
msgid "If they're not using it anymore, might as well keep it."
msgstr "Artık kullanmıyorlarsa pekâlâ saklayabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOATMILK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOATMILK"
msgid "I don't think milk is supposed to crackle..."
msgstr "Sanırım sütün çıtırdaması gerekmiyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOGGLESHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOGGLESHAT"
msgid "I feel more adventurous already!"
msgstr "Şimdiden daha maceraperest hissediyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENAXE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENAXE"
msgid "I feel like you could use gold for better things."
msgstr "Bence altını daha iyi şeyler için kullanabilirsin."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENPICKAXE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENPICKAXE"
msgid "It makes sense if you don't think about it."
msgstr "Üzerinde düşünmezsen mantıklı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENPITCHFORK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENPITCHFORK"
msgid "Now I can be part of a FANCY angry mob."
msgstr "Artık ŞIK bir öfkeli kalabalığın parçası olabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENSHOVEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDENSHOVEL"
msgid "Instead of digging up gold, I can dig with gold!"
msgstr "Altın kazmak yerine altınla kazabilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDEN_FARM_HOE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDEN_FARM_HOE"
msgid "My tilling skills deserve a gold metal! Get it?"
msgstr "Çapalama becerilerim altın madalyayı hak ediyor! Anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDNUGGET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOLDNUGGET"
msgid "Ow... I bit it, isn't that a thing people do?"
msgstr "Off... Isırdım, insanlar böyle yapmıyor mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOOSE_FEATHER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GOOSE_FEATHER"
msgid "Goosey."
msgstr "Kazlı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.BARREN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.BARREN"
msgid "This grass needs something to help it grow."
msgstr "Bu ota büyümesi için bir şey lazım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.BURNING"
msgid "Hey! Brush fires destroy forests!"
msgstr "Hey! Çalı yangınları ormanları yok eder!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.DISEASED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.DISEASED"
msgid "That's... not how it's supposed to look, is it?"
msgstr "Bu... böyle görünmemeli, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.DISEASING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.DISEASING"
msgid "Something seems off."
msgstr "Bir şey ters gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.GENERIC"
msgid "A patch of grass. With bugs in it, if we're lucky."
msgstr "Bir parça ot. Şanslıysak içinde böcek olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.PICKED"
msgid "Can't take anymore from it."
msgstr "Ondan daha fazla alamam."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS.WITHERED"
msgid "It's too hot out for anything to grow."
msgstr "Dışarısı her şeyin büyümesi için fazla sıcak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASSGATOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASSGATOR"
msgid "He seems pretty shy."
msgstr "Bayağı utangaç görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASSGEKKO.DISEASED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASSGEKKO.DISEASED"
msgid "Oh no... I think it's sick."
msgstr "Eyvah... Sanırım hasta."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASSGEKKO.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASSGEKKO.GENERIC"
msgid "That patch of grass is alive!"
msgstr "O ot kümesi canlı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS_UMBRELLA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRASS_UMBRELLA"
msgid "Flowers actually have lots of practical uses."
msgstr "Çiçeklerin aslında bir sürü pratik kullanımı vardır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRAVEURN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRAVEURN.GENERIC"
msgid "Soulless! Aww, that's mean."
msgstr "Ruhsuz! Aaa, bu kötü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRAVEURN.HAS_SPIRIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRAVEURN.HAS_SPIRIT"
msgid "Where do you think it wants to go, Woby?"
msgstr "Sence nereye gitmek istiyor Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRAVY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GRAVY"
msgid "Pass it over here!"
msgstr "Buraya uzat!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENAMULET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENAMULET"
msgid "Great for when you're low on supplies!"
msgstr "Erzakların azaldığında harika!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENGEM"
msgid "It's a great green gem!"
msgstr "Bu harika yeşil bir mücevher!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENMOONEYE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENMOONEYE"
msgid "They never taught us how to use these in the Pinetree Pioneers."
msgstr "Çamağacı Öncüleri'nde bize bunları nasıl kullanacağımızı öğretmediler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENSTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREENSTAFF"
msgid "I wish I had this when I had to break camp in the Pinetree Pioneers..."
msgstr "Çamağacı Öncüleri'nde kamp toplamak zorunda kaldığımda keşke bu olsaydı..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_CAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_CAP"
msgid "It's not usually smart to eat unfamiliar mushrooms."
msgstr "Tanımadığın mantarları yemek genellikle akıllıca değildir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_CAP_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_CAP_COOKED"
msgid "It's probably safe now that it's cooked, right?"
msgstr "Pişince muhtemelen güvenlidir, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_MUSHROOM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_MUSHROOM.GENERIC"
msgid "It doesn't look like any of the mushrooms in my handbook."
msgstr "El kitabımdaki mantarlardan hiçbirine benzemiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_MUSHROOM.INGROUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_MUSHROOM.INGROUND"
msgid "There's a mushroom hiding in there!"
msgstr "İçinde saklanan bir mantar var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_MUSHROOM.PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GREEN_MUSHROOM.PICKED"
msgid "Maybe it will grow back."
msgstr "Belki yeniden çıkar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GROTTO_POOL_BIG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GROTTO_POOL_BIG"
msgid "Sorry Woby, I don't think it'll be any good for swimming."
msgstr "Üzgünüm Woby, sanırım yüzmek için iyi olmayacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GROTTO_POOL_SMALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GROTTO_POOL_SMALL"
msgid "Sorry Woby, I don't think it'll be any good for swimming."
msgstr "Üzgünüm Woby, sanırım yüzmek için iyi olmayacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GUACAMOLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GUACAMOLE"
msgid "Now all we need are some chips!"
msgstr "Şimdi tek gereken biraz cips!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GUANO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GUANO"
msgid "My Pinetree Pioneer training is telling me there's bats nearby!"
msgstr "Çamağacı Öncüsü eğitimim bana yakınlarda yarasa olduğunu söylüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GUNPOWDER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.GUNPOWDER"
msgid "I better make sure none of the younger kids play with this."
msgstr "Küçüklerden hiçbirinin bununla oynamadığından emin olsam iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_1"
msgid "Even candy's better when it's on a stick."
msgstr "Şeker bile çubuğa takılınca daha iyi oluyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_10
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_10"
msgid "Is it made with real tentacles?"
msgstr "Gerçek dokunaçlardan mı yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_11
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_11"
msgid "I'm far too mature for trick or treating."
msgstr "Şeker mi şaka mı oynamak için fazla olgunum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_12
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_12"
msgid "I think these might be real bugs!"
msgstr "Sanırım bunlar gerçek böcek olabilir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_13
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_13"
msgid "Huh. It's sour."
msgstr "Vay. Ekşi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_14
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_14"
msgid "Oh! I wasn't expecting it to actually be spicy!"
msgstr "Aa! Gerçekten acı olmasını beklemiyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_2"
msgid "A handful of candy kernels."
msgstr "Bir avuç şeker tanesi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_3"
msgid "Not very spooky, but it is tasty."
msgstr "Pek ürkütücü değil ama lezzetli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_4"
msgid "Maybe that spider kid would like this. Or maybe not..."
msgstr "Belki o örümcek çocuğu bunu sever. Ya da belki sevmez..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_5"
msgid "It's wearing a little mask!"
msgstr "Küçük bir maske takmış!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_6"
msgid "Those look suspicious."
msgstr "Onlar şüpheli görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_7
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_7"
msgid "I don't know what some people's problem is, raisins are good!"
msgstr "Bazı insanların sorunu ne bilmiyorum, kuru üzüm iyidir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_8
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_8"
msgid "Maybe I'll give it to the twins."
msgstr "Belki ikizlere veririm."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_9
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENCANDY_9"
msgid "Gummy."
msgstr "Yumuşak şeker."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_BRAVERY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_BRAVERY"
msgid "So that's what \"liquid courage\" is!"
msgstr "Demek \"sıvı cesaret\" buymuş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_DRINKS_POTENT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_DRINKS_POTENT"
msgid "Dabbling in witchcraft is fun!"
msgstr "Cadılık denemek eğlenceliymiş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_DRINKS_WEAK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_DRINKS_WEAK"
msgid "It didn't turn out quite as well as I thought it would."
msgstr "Düşündüğüm kadar iyi olmadı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_FIRE_FX
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_FIRE_FX"
msgid "It should only be handled by someone who knows fire safety. Like me!"
msgstr "Yangın güvenliğini bilen biri tarafından kullanılmalı. Benim gibi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_MOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEENPOTION_MOON"
msgid "What should we mutate first?"
msgstr "Önce neyi mutasyona uğratalım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_1"
msgid "Spooooky!"
msgstr "Ürküütücüü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_2"
msgid "This is my favourite time of year."
msgstr "Bu yılın en sevdiğim zamanı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_3"
msgid "It's pretty good, I thought it was a real spider!"
msgstr "Bayağı iyi, gerçek bir örümcek sanmıştım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_4"
msgid "This looks really authentic!"
msgstr "Bu gerçekten otantik görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_5"
msgid "Weird how the spiders around here only have six legs."
msgstr "Buralardaki örümceklerin sadece altı bacağının olması garip."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HALLOWEEN_ORNAMENT_6"
msgid "This decoration needs a tree to perch in."
msgstr "Bu süslemenin tüneyecek bir ağaca ihtiyacı var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAMBAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAMBAT"
msgid "Don't get any ideas, Woby."
msgstr "Sakın aklına bir şey getirme Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAMMER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAMMER"
msgid "Sometimes you need to break stuff to make stuff."
msgstr "Bazen bir şey yapmak için bir şey kırman gerekir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAMMER_MJOLNIR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAMMER_MJOLNIR"
msgid "It's a heavy hammer for hitting things."
msgstr "Bu, bir şeylere vurmak için ağır bir çekiç."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_BEEFALOWOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_BEEFALOWOOL"
msgid "It's almost as good of a pillow as Woby!"
msgstr "Neredeyse Woby kadar iyi bir yastık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_KELP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_KELP"
msgid "Well, um... I guess there are worse things to use for a pillow?"
msgstr "Şey, ee... Galiba yastık olarak kullanılacak daha kötü şeyler vardır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_PETALS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_PETALS"
msgid "Don't worry, I already checked it for bees."
msgstr "Merak etme, arı var mı diye baktım bile."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_STEELWOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HANDPILLOW_STEELWOOL"
msgid "It's not so bad, I once made a bed out of pine needles."
msgstr "O kadar kötü değil, bir keresinde çam iğnelerinden yatak yapmıştım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAREBALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAREBALL"
msgid "That looks like something Woby spit up."
msgstr "Bu Woby'nin tükürdüğü bir şeye benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAWAIIANSHIRT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HAWAIIANSHIRT"
msgid "This DEFINITELY wouldn't pass uniform inspection."
msgstr "Bu KESİNLİKLE üniforma denetiminden geçmez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEALINGSALVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEALINGSALVE"
msgid "Never hurts to be prepared!"
msgstr "Hazırlıklı olmak hiç zarar vermez!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEALINGSALVE_ACID
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEALINGSALVE_ACID"
msgid "We're prepared for anything, Woby!"
msgstr "Her şeye hazırız Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEALINGSTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEALINGSTAFF"
msgid "It conducts regenerative energy."
msgstr "Yenileyici enerjiyi iletiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.COLD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.COLD"
msgid "Ahh... nice and cold."
msgstr "Ahh... güzel ve soğuk."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.FROZEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.FROZEN"
msgid "Almost as chilling as one of my campfire stories. Right?"
msgstr "Neredeyse kamp ateşi hikâyelerimden biri kadar tüyler ürpertici. Değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.GENERIC"
msgid "That's a nice rock."
msgstr "Güzel bir kaya."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.HOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.HOT"
msgid "Hot! Hot rock!"
msgstr "Sıcak! Sıcak kaya!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.WARM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEATROCK.WARM"
msgid "Almost as good as cuddling up with Woby."
msgstr "Neredeyse Woby'ye sarılmak kadar iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEDGEHOUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEDGEHOUND"
msgid "Maybe he just has a thorn stuck in his paw?"
msgstr "Belki sadece patisine bir diken batmıştır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEDGEHOUND_BUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HEDGEHOUND_BUSH"
msgid "Woby, what's wrong? It's just a rose bush!"
msgstr "Woby, ne oldu? Sadece bir gül çalısı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB"
msgid "Hello ma'am! Can I help you with anything?"
msgstr "Merhaba hanımefendi! Bir şeyde yardım edebilir miyim?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_FIRENETTLES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_FIRENETTLES"
msgid "A toasty blend!"
msgstr "Sıcacık bir karışım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_FOLIAGE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_FOLIAGE"
msgid "Let's save this for the others! Right, Woby girl?"
msgstr "Bunu diğerleri için saklayalım! Değil mi Woby kızım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_FORGETMELOTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_FORGETMELOTS"
msgid "Remind me to take this when I'm feeling really funny. Okay, Woby?"
msgstr "Çok komik hissettiğimde bunu almamı hatırlat. Tamam mı Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_MOON_TREE_BLOSSOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_MOON_TREE_BLOSSOM"
msgid "The tea from outer space!"
msgstr "Uzaydan gelen çay!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_PETALS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_PETALS"
msgid "It even smells calming!"
msgstr "Kokusu bile sakinleştirici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_PETALS_EVIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_PETALS_EVIL"
msgid "We better be careful with this one, Woby!"
msgstr "Bunda dikkatli olsak iyi olur Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_SUCCULENT_PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_SUCCULENT_PICKED"
msgid "Perfect for a hot day!"
msgstr "Sıcak bir gün için mükemmel!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_TILLWEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRABTEA_TILLWEED"
msgid "This one is chock full of vitamins!"
msgstr "Bu vitamin dolu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_LIGHTPOST.ABANDONED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_LIGHTPOST.ABANDONED"
msgid "Aw, I don't think we can fix that."
msgstr "Aaa, sanırım bunu tamir edemeyiz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_LIGHTPOST.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_LIGHTPOST.GENERIC"
msgid "I hope Ms. Pearl likes it!"
msgstr "Umarım Bayan Pearl beğenir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_LIGHTPOST_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_LIGHTPOST_ITEM"
msgid "C'mon, Woby! Let's lighten this place up a bit!"
msgstr "Hadi Woby! Burayı biraz aydınlatalım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_RELOCATION_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_RELOCATION_KIT"
msgid "I think there's a badge for helping the elderly move. But we'll do it just 'cuz, right Wobers?"
msgstr "Sanırım yaşlılara taşınmada yardım etmenin bir rozeti var. Ama biz öylesine yapacağız, değil mi Wobers?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_SHELL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_SHELL"
msgid "Aw, we can visit Ms. Pearl instantly!"
msgstr "Aaa, Bayan Pearl'i anında ziyaret edebiliriz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.ACTIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.ACTIVE"
msgid "Ms. Pearl makes the best tea!"
msgstr "Bayan Pearl en iyi çayı yapar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.BREWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.BREWING"
msgid "I can't wait for my tea!"
msgstr "Çayım için sabırsızlanıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.BURNT"
msgid "I hope Ms. Pearl is okay."
msgstr "Umarım Bayan Pearl iyidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITCRAB_TEASHOP.GENERIC"
msgid "That's right, Woby. She's not in yet."
msgstr "Doğru Woby. Henüz gelmedi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITHOTSPRING.BOMBED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITHOTSPRING.BOMBED"
msgid "Nothing like a soak at the end of a long day!"
msgstr "Uzun bir günün sonunda suya dalmak gibisi yok!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITHOTSPRING.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITHOTSPRING.EMPTY"
msgid "It's just a hole in the ground now."
msgstr "Artık sadece yerdeki bir delik."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITHOTSPRING.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.HERMITHOTSPRING.GENERIC"
msgid "This would make a great swimming hole! It's even heated!"
msgstr "Bu harika bir yüzme havuzu olur! Hem de ısıtılmış!"

