msgstr "O silah fırlatmak için."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAARENA_PORTAL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAARENA_PORTAL.GENERIC"
