msgstr "Bu muhteşem!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_COCOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_COCOON"
