msgstr "Aaaa, sanırım gülümsüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_PET.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_PET.GENERIC"
msgid "You're the best grub in the whole wide world!"
msgstr "Sen koca dünyadaki en iyi kurtçuksun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_PET.HUNGRY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_PET.HUNGRY"
msgid "Are you hungry, little guy?"
msgstr "Aç mısın küçük dostum?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_PET.STARVING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_PET.STARVING"
msgid "This little guy needs some food!"
msgstr "Bu küçük dostun yemeğe ihtiyacı var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_TOOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVAE_TOOTH"
msgid "Aw, they lost their first tooth!"
msgstr "Aaaa, ilk dişlerini kaybetmişler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVASPIT.COOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVASPIT.COOL"
msgid "It's cool!"
msgstr "Soğumuş!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVASPIT.HOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVASPIT.HOT"
msgid "It's rude to spit at people!"
msgstr "İnsanlara tükürmek kabalıktır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVA_POND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVA_POND"
msgid "Probably not the best swimming hole."
msgstr "Muhtemelen en iyi yüzme havuzu değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVA_POND_ROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LAVA_POND_ROCK"
msgid "Sedimentary, my dear Woby! Well, igneous actually... never mind."
msgstr "Tortul, sevgili Woby! Şey, aslında volkanik... boş ver."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEAFLOAF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEAFLOAF"
msgid "I guess it's one way to eat your vegetables."
msgstr "Galiba sebzelerini yemenin bir yolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEAFYMEATBURGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEAFYMEATBURGER"
msgid "It's not quite the same."
msgstr "Pek aynı değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEAFYMEATSOUFFLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEAFYMEATSOUFFLE"
msgid "I don't think we needed to get that fancy with it..."
msgstr "Bence onunla bu kadar şıklaşmamıza gerek yoktu..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEIF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEIF"
msgid "They've come to take their revenge!"
msgstr "İntikamlarını almaya geldiler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEIF_IDOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEIF_IDOL"
msgid "What a neat way to start a campfire!"
msgstr "Kamp ateşi yakmak için ne hoş bir yol!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEIF_SPARSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LEIF_SPARSE"
msgid "They've come to take their revenge!"
msgstr "İntikamlarını almaya geldiler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LICHEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LICHEN"
msgid "It grows in most caves."
msgstr "Çoğu mağarada yetişir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIFEINJECTOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIFEINJECTOR"
msgid "This is supposed to make me healthier?"
msgstr "Bu beni daha sağlıklı yapması mı gerekiyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTBULB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTBULB"
msgid "Will I start glowing if I eat it?"
msgstr "Yersem parlamaya başlar mıyım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTCRAB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTCRAB"
msgid "What kind of crab is that?"
msgstr "Bu ne tür bir yengeç?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTER"
msgid "Way easier than rubbing sticks together, but not as fun."
msgstr "Çubukları birbirine sürtmekten çok daha kolay ama o kadar eğlenceli değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTFLIER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LIGHTFLIER"
