msgstr "Kim bu yüzü sevmez ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LOBSTERBISQUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LOBSTERBISQUE"
msgid "It's tasty, I like it!"
msgstr "Lezzetli, sevdim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LOBSTERDINNER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.LOBSTERDINNER"
