msgstr "Cidden büyük bir kafası var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLLIGHT"
msgid "That's a pretty neat trick."
msgstr "Bu epey havalı bir numara."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLLOCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLLOCK"
msgid "It looks like something should go in there."
msgstr "Oraya bir şey girmeli gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLPHONOGRAPH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLPHONOGRAPH"
msgid "It's like a radio, but not as good."
msgstr "Radyo gibi ama o kadar iyi değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLTHRONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MAXWELLTHRONE"
msgid "That chair is just screaming \"cursed\"."
msgstr "O sandalye resmen \"lanetli\" diye bağırıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEAT"
msgid "I hope I don't get sick from eating this..."
msgstr "Umarım bunu yiyince hasta olmam..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATBALLS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATBALLS"
msgid "They're the best part of spaghetti anyway."
msgstr "Zaten spagettinin en güzel kısmı bunlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.BURNT"
msgid "Nooo the jerky!"
msgstr "Hayııır pastırma!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DONE"
msgid "Yes! The jerky's ready!"
msgstr "Evet! Pastırma hazır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DONE_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DONE_NOTMEAT"
msgid "I think it's done!"
msgstr "Sanırım bitti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYING"
msgid "You have to be patient, Woby."
msgstr "Sabırlı olman gerek, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYINGINRAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYINGINRAIN"
msgid "I don't think that's going to work."
msgstr "Bunun işe yarayacağını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYINGINRAIN_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYINGINRAIN_NOTMEAT"
msgid "I probably should've planned ahead for this."
msgstr "Bunun için önceden plan yapmalıydım galiba."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYING_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.DRYING_NOTMEAT"
msgid "While we're waiting, does anyone want to see this bug I found?"
msgstr "Beklerken, bulduğum böceği görmek isteyen var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK.GENERIC"
msgid "We should make some jerky!"
msgstr "Pastırma yapmalıyız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.BURNT"
msgid "It burned up!"
msgstr "Yanıp kül oldu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DONE"
msgid "Your jerky's ready, ma'am!"
msgstr "Pastırmanız hazır, hanımefendi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DONE_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DONE_NOTMEAT"
msgid "Your jerky's ready, ma'am!"
msgstr "Pastırmanız hazır, hanımefendi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYING"
msgid "It should be ready soon."
msgstr "Yakında hazır olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYINGINRAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYINGINRAIN"
msgid "Oh no, it's never going to dry in this rain!"
msgstr "Ah hayır, bu yağmurda asla kurumayacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYINGINRAIN_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYINGINRAIN_NOTMEAT"
msgid "Oh no, it's never going to dry in this rain!"
msgstr "Ah hayır, bu yağmurda asla kurumayacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYING_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.DRYING_NOTMEAT"
msgid "It should be ready soon."
msgstr "Yakında hazır olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT.GENERIC"
msgid "Those are some pretty swell looking drying racks."
msgstr "Bunlar epey havalı görünen kurutma rafları."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.ABANDONED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.ABANDONED"
msgid "I don't know if we can fix this, Woby..."
msgstr "Bunu tamir edebilir miyiz bilmiyorum, Woby..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.BURNT"
msgid "It burned up!"
msgstr "Yanıp kül oldu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DONE"
msgid "Your dried goods are ready, ma'am!"
msgstr "Kuru ürünleriniz hazır, hanımefendi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DONE_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DONE_NOTMEAT"
msgid "Your dried goods are ready, ma'am!"
msgstr "Kuru ürünleriniz hazır, hanımefendi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DONE_SALT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DONE_SALT"
msgid "Look at all that salt, Woby!"
msgstr "Şu kadar tuza bak, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYING"
msgid "It should be ready soon."
msgstr "Yakında hazır olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYINGINRAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYINGINRAIN"
msgid "Oh no, it's never going to dry in this rain!"
msgstr "Ah hayır, bu yağmurda asla kurumayacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYINGINRAIN_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYINGINRAIN_NOTMEAT"
msgid "Oh no, it's never going to dry in this rain!"
msgstr "Ah hayır, bu yağmurda asla kurumayacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYING_NOTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.DRYING_NOTMEAT"
msgid "It should be ready soon."
msgstr "Yakında hazır olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATRACK_HERMIT_MULTI.GENERIC"
msgid "Oooh, we can dry so many things, Woby!"
msgstr "Oooo, bir sürü şey kurutabiliriz, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATYSALAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEATYSALAD"
msgid "What are those chunks in it?"
msgstr "İçindeki o iri parçalar ne?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEAT_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEAT_DRIED"
msgid "That's some tasty jerky!"
msgstr "Bu bayağı lezzetli bir pastırma!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEGAFLARE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MEGAFLARE"
msgid "We don't want anyone feeling left out, right Woby?"
msgstr "Kimsenin dışlanmış hissetmesini istemeyiz, değil mi Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM"
msgid "A bog monster! I knew they were real!"
msgstr "Bir bataklık canavarı! Gerçek olduklarını biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMARMORHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMARMORHAT"
msgid "Aww, merms get all the good stuff."
msgstr "Aaa, mermlere bütün havalı şeyler kalıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMARMORUPGRADEDHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMARMORUPGRADEDHAT"
msgid "Aww, merms get all the good stuff."
msgstr "Aaa, mermlere bütün havalı şeyler kalıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMCORPSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMCORPSE.BURNING"
msgid "It reminds me of barbequed fish."
msgstr "Bana ızgara balığı hatırlatıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMCORPSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMCORPSE.GENERIC"
msgid "Yikes, that smells fishy."
msgstr "Vay canına, balık balık kokuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMCORPSE.REVIVING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMCORPSE.REVIVING"
msgid "It smells extra fishy!"
msgstr "Daha da fazla balık kokuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMGUARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMGUARD"
msgid "Are they a different type of bog monster?"
msgstr "Bunlar farklı bir bataklık canavarı türü mü?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMGUARD_LUNAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMGUARD_LUNAR"
msgid "Bog monsters from the moon!"
msgstr "Aydan gelen bataklık canavarları!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMGUARD_SHADOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMGUARD_SHADOW"
msgid "Neat! It's a bog monster and shadow monster at the same time!"
msgstr "Havalı! Aynı anda hem bataklık canavarı hem gölge canavarı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHAT"
msgid "Now I can disguise myself as a bog monster! The tables have turned!"
msgstr "Artık bataklık canavarı kılığına girebilirim! Tas tarak değişti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHEAD.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHEAD.BURNT"
msgid "Darnit, there goes my evidence."
msgstr "Hay aksi, kanıtım uçtu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHEAD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHEAD.GENERIC"
msgid "Woah, it's not made of rubber! I think it's real!"
msgstr "Vaay, lastikten yapılmamış! Sanırım gerçek!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE.BURNT"
msgid "Hopefully all the termites made it out safely."
msgstr "Umarım bütün termitler sağ salim kaçabilmiştir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE.GENERIC"
msgid "I bet that wood is full of termites."
msgstr "İddiaya girerim o tahta termit kaynıyordur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE_CRAFTED.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE_CRAFTED.BURNT"
msgid "That's horrible!"
msgstr "Bu korkunç!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE_CRAFTED.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMHOUSE_CRAFTED.GENERIC"
msgid "Bog monsters live in houses?"
msgstr "Bataklık canavarları evde mi yaşıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMKING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMKING"
msgid "The king of the bog monsters!"
msgstr "Bataklık canavarlarının kralı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE.BURNT"
msgid "I'm so sorry about that!"
msgstr "Bunun için çok özür dilerim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE.GENERIC"
msgid "Wow, there's a whole bog monster civilization!"
msgstr "Vay, koskoca bir bataklık canavarı medeniyeti var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE_CONSTRUCTION.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE_CONSTRUCTION.BURNT"
msgid "Darnit! Now I'll never know what it was!"
msgstr "Hay aksi! Artık ne olduğunu asla bilemeyeceğim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE_CONSTRUCTION.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMTHRONE_CONSTRUCTION.GENERIC"
msgid "It looks like they're building something, but what?"
msgstr "Bir şey inşa ediyor gibiler ama ne?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMWATCHTOWER_NOKING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMWATCHTOWER_NOKING"
msgid "Wow, it's like a tree fort!"
msgstr "Vay, ağaç sığınağı gibi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMWATCHTOWER_REGULAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERMWATCHTOWER_REGULAR"
msgid "They're friendly!"
msgstr "Dost canlısılar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_ARMORY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_ARMORY"
msgid "Aww, can't I just take a little peek inside?"
msgstr "Aaa, içeriye ufacık göz atamaz mıyım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_ARMORY_UPGRADED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_ARMORY_UPGRADED"
msgid "Aww, can't I just take a little peek inside?"
msgstr "Aaa, içeriye ufacık göz atamaz mıyım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_LUNAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_LUNAR"
msgid "Bog monsters from the moon!"
msgstr "Aydan gelen bataklık canavarları!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_PRINCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_PRINCE"
msgid "I wonder how they pick their king?"
msgstr "Acaba krallarını nasıl seçiyorlar?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_SHADOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_SHADOW"
msgid "Neat! It's a bog monster and shadow monster at the same time!"
msgstr "Havalı! Aynı anda hem bataklık canavarı hem gölge canavarı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOL"
msgid "It must be really hard to make things when you have claws for hands."
msgstr "Ellerin pençe olunca eşya yapmak çok zor olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOLSHED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOLSHED"
msgid "I wonder what kind of bog monster secrets they're hiding in there..."
msgstr "Acaba içeride ne çeşit bataklık canavarı sırları saklıyorlar..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOLSHED_UPGRADED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOLSHED_UPGRADED"
msgid "I wonder what kind of bog monster secrets they're hiding in there..."
msgstr "Acaba içeride ne çeşit bataklık canavarı sırları saklıyorlar..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOL_UPGRADED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MERM_TOOL_UPGRADED"
msgid "It must be really hard to make things when you have claws for hands."
msgstr "Ellerin pençe olunca eşya yapmak çok zor olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MESSAGEBOTTLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MESSAGEBOTTLE"
msgid "There's a note inside."
msgstr "İçinde bir not var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MESSAGEBOTTLEEMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MESSAGEBOTTLEEMPTY"
msgid "Maybe I'll use it for my bug collection, my pockets are getting full."
msgstr "Belki böcek koleksiyonum için kullanırım, ceplerim doluyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MIGHTY_GYM.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MIGHTY_GYM.BURNT"
msgid "Aww, I never even got to try it..."
msgstr "Aaaa, denemeye bile fırsat bulamadım..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MIGHTY_GYM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MIGHTY_GYM.GENERIC"
msgid "Wow! I wonder if I could be as strong as Mr. Wolfgang one day..."
msgstr "Vay! Acaba bir gün Bay Wolfgang kadar güçlü olabilir miyim..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MILKYWHITES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MILKYWHITES"
msgid "Woby, can you find me a stick? I want to poke it."
msgstr "Woby, bana bir çubuk bulur musun? Dürtmek istiyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINERHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINERHAT"
msgid "Being able to see makes exploring a lot easier."
msgstr "Görebilmek keşfetmeyi çok daha kolay kılıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINIBOATLANTERN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINIBOATLANTERN"
msgid "It'll help us find the sea monsters. I know they're out there!"
msgstr "Deniz canavarlarını bulmamıza yardım eder. Orada olduklarını biliyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINIFAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINIFAN"
msgid "Those are for little kids!'"
msgstr "Onlar küçük çocuklar için!'"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINIFLARE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINIFLARE"
msgid "It's a signal, only to be used in an emergency."
msgstr "Bir işaret fişeği, sadece acil durumda kullanılır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINISIGN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINISIGN.GENERIC"
msgid "Who drew this?"
msgstr "Bunu kim çizdi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINISIGN.UNDRAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINISIGN.UNDRAWN"
msgid "Woby, sit still! I'll draw your portrait."
msgstr "Woby, kıpırdama! Portreni çizeceğim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINISIGN_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINISIGN_ITEM"
msgid "Where's the perfect spot to put this..."
msgstr "Bunu koyacak en iyi yer nerede..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINOTAUR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINOTAUR"
msgid "Aw, did someone leave you all alone down here?"
msgstr "Aaa, biri seni burada yapayalnız mı bıraktı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINOTAURCHEST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINOTAURCHEST"
msgid "I have to know what's inside!"
msgstr "İçinde ne olduğunu bilmek zorundayım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINOTAURHORN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MINOTAURHORN"
msgid "This is amazing! A real monster horn!"
msgstr "Bu inanılmaz! Gerçek bir canavar boynuzu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLE.ABOVEGROUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLE.ABOVEGROUND"
msgid "Get it, Woby!"
msgstr "Yakala, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLE.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLE.HELD"
msgid "I got it! Guys, I actually got it!!"
msgstr "Yakaladım! Çocuklar, gerçekten yakaladım!!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLE.UNDERGROUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLE.UNDERGROUND"
msgid "Is something moving underground?"
msgstr "Yer altında bir şey mi hareket ediyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEBAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEBAT"
msgid "They must have terrible allergies."
msgstr "Korkunç alerjileri olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEBATHILL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEBATHILL"
msgid "There might be something interesting in there."
msgstr "İçeride ilginç bir şey olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEHAT"
msgid "These work way better than the X-ray goggles I mailed in for back home!"
msgstr "Bunlar memlekette posta yoluyla aldığım röntgen gözlüklerinden çok daha iyi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEHILL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOLEHILL"
msgid "I wonder what's in there..."
msgstr "İçeride ne var acaba..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEY"
msgid "I've only ever seen them in zoos!"
msgstr "Onları sadece hayvanat bahçesinde görmüştüm!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYBARREL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYBARREL"
msgid "I'm sure it's just an ordinary barrel."
msgstr "Eminim sıradan bir varildir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYHUT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYHUT.BURNT"
msgid "Something tells me they never learned about fire safety."
msgstr "İçimden bir ses ateş güvenliğini hiç öğrenmediklerini söylüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYHUT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYHUT.GENERIC"
msgid "Neat, a tree fort!"
msgstr "Havalı, ağaç sığınağı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYISLAND_PORTAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYISLAND_PORTAL"
msgid "Neat, a portal! Is... it supposed to look like that?"
msgstr "Havalı, bir geçit! Şey... böyle mi görünmesi gerekiyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYISLAND_PORTAL_DEBRIS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYISLAND_PORTAL_DEBRIS"
msgid "People really shouldn't leave their litter lying around."
msgstr "İnsanlar gerçekten çöplerini ortalıkta bırakmamalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYPILLAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYPILLAR"
msgid "I wonder if I could climb all the way to the top..."
msgstr "Acaba en tepeye kadar tırmanabilir miyim..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYQUEEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYQUEEN"
msgid "Hello ma'am! Do you need help getting down from there?"
msgstr "Merhaba hanımefendi! Oradan inmek için yardıma ihtiyacınız var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYTAIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEYTAIL"
msgid "I wonder if there's any real monkeys hiding in there?"
msgstr "Acaba içinde saklanan gerçek maymun var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEY_MEDIUMHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEY_MEDIUMHAT"
msgid "Listen up everybody, I'm the captain!"
msgstr "Dinleyin millet, ben kaptanım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEY_SMALLHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONKEY_SMALLHAT"
msgid "It makes me look like a real pirate!"
msgstr "Beni gerçek bir korsan gibi gösteriyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERLASAGNA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERLASAGNA"
msgid "It looks kind of suspicious... maybe Woby will want it."
msgstr "Şüpheli görünüyor... belki Woby ister."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERMEAT"
msgid "Uhh Woby? Do you want this?"
msgstr "Şey Woby? Bunu ister misin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERMEAT_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERMEAT_DRIED"
msgid "Hey Woby, it's your favourite!"
msgstr "Hey Woby, en sevdiğin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERTARTARE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MONSTERTARTARE"
msgid "Fancy and gross overlaps a lot."
msgstr "Şıklık ve iğrençlik çoğu zaman örtüşüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.BROKEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.BROKEN"
msgid "What a mess."
msgstr "Ne berbat manzara."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.GENERIC"
msgid "It looks like something should go here..."
msgstr "Buraya bir şey girmeli gibi görünüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.MOONSTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.MOONSTAFF"
msgid "Woah! That did something!"
msgstr "Vaay! Bu bir şey yaptı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.STAFFED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.STAFFED"
msgid "Should... should something be happening?"
msgstr "Bir... bir şey olması mı gerekiyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.WRONGSTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBASE.WRONGSTAFF"
msgid "I don't think that works..."
msgstr "Bunun işe yaradığını sanmıyorum..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLY.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLY.GENERIC"
msgid "I've never seen a moth like this before!"
msgstr "Daha önce böyle bir güve görmemiştim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLY.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLY.HELD"
msgid "In my pocket you go!"
msgstr "Cebime giriyorsun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLYWINGS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLYWINGS"
msgid "They're very fragile."
msgstr "Çok kırılganlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLY_SAPLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONBUTTERFLY_SAPLING"
msgid "Poor moth."
msgstr "Zavallı güve."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.CAVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.CAVE"
msgid "I can't see through stone... or can I? ...Nope."
msgstr "Taşın içinden göremiyorum... yoksa görüyor muyum? ...Hayır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.GENERIC"
msgid "Huh? I can see the moon!"
msgstr "Hı? Ayı görebiliyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.GLASSED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.GLASSED"
msgid "Wait, this isn't ice... it's glass!"
msgstr "Dur, bu buz değil... cam!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_FULL"
msgid "The full moon, a.k.a. best time to spot a werewolf!"
msgstr "Dolunay, namı diğer kurt adam görmek için en iyi zaman!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_NEW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_NEW"
msgid "I know all the moon phases, this one's a new moon."
msgstr "Bütün ay evrelerini biliyorum, bu yeni ay."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_WANE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_WANE"
msgid "It's a waning moon."
msgstr "Küçülen ay."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_WAX
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONDIAL.NIGHT_WAX"
msgid "It's a waxing moon."
msgstr "Büyüyen ay."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS"
msgid "Wow... it's so light!"
msgstr "Vay... çok hafif!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASSAXE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASSAXE"
msgid "Hey... it just occurred to me that this might be dangerous."
msgstr "Hey... az önce bunun tehlikeli olabileceği aklıma geldi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS_CHARGED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS_CHARGED"
msgid "It's light and glowy."
msgstr "Hafif ve parıltılı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS_ROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS_ROCK"
msgid "I've never seen a rock like this before."
msgstr "Daha önce böyle bir kaya görmemiştim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS_WOBSTER_DEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONGLASS_WOBSTER_DEN"
msgid "That's where the Wobsters make camp."
msgstr "Wobster'ların kamp kurduğu yer."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKCRATER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKCRATER"
msgid "I feel like it's looking at me."
msgstr "Sanki bana bakıyormuş gibi hissediyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKIDOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKIDOL"
msgid "Usually these kind of things are locked in an ancient temple guarded by a monster."
msgstr "Genelde bunlar bir canavarın koruduğu kadim bir tapınakta kilitli olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKNUGGET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKNUGGET"
msgid "It came from outer space!"
msgstr "Uzaydan geldi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKSEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCKSEED"
msgid "Is the moon... haunted?"
msgstr "Ay... perili mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCK_PIECES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONROCK_PIECES"
msgid "Should we try to break it apart Woby?"
msgstr "Parçalamayı denemeli miyiz Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSPIDERDEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSPIDERDEN"
msgid "Look at that, Woby! It's a home for moon creatures!"
msgstr "Şuna bak, Woby! Ay yaratıkları için bir yuva!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_GLASS.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_GLASS.GENERIC"
msgid "I've never seen glass made by lightning before!"
msgstr "Daha önce şimşekle yapılmış cam görmemiştim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_GLASS.INFUSED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_GLASS.INFUSED"
msgid "Look at that, Woby! It's glowing!"
msgstr "Şuna bak, Woby! Parlıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_GOGGLESHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_GOGGLESHAT"
msgid "It's important to have the proper equipment in a storm."
msgstr "Fırtınada doğru ekipmana sahip olmak önemli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_SPARK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_SPARK"
msgid "It's literally spine-tingling!"
msgstr "Resmen tüyler ürpertici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC"
msgid "I wonder what he's working on?"
msgstr "Acaba ne üzerinde çalışıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC_CATCHER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC_CATCHER"
msgid "Looks empty, Wobes."
msgstr "Boş gibi, Wobes."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC_ITEM"
msgid "You'll be shocked to see what's inside! Get it? Because there's static inside?"
msgstr "İçinde ne olduğunu görünce şok olacaksın! Anladın mı? Çünkü içinde elektrik var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC_ROAMER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOONSTORM_STATIC_ROAMER"
msgid "Woby, should we name it Sparky?"
msgstr "Woby, ona Çıtırık adını koyalım mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR.GENERIC"
msgid "You're right, people SHOULD listen to me more often."
msgstr "Haklısın, insanlar beni daha sık dinleMELİ."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR.MOON_ALTAR_WIP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR.MOON_ALTAR_WIP"
msgid "Don't worry, a Pinetree Pioneer finishes what they start!"
msgstr "Merak etme, Çamağacı Öncüsü başladığı işi bitirir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ASTRAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ASTRAL"
msgid "I think it's ready."
msgstr "Sanırım hazır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_COSMIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_COSMIC"
msgid "\"It's almost time\"? Time for what?"
msgstr "\"Vakit yaklaştı\" mı? Ne vakti?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_CROWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_CROWN"
msgid "Don't worry, we'll get you home!"
msgstr "Merak etme, seni evine götüreceğiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_GLASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_GLASS"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll help you get where you need to go."
msgstr "Merak etme, gitmen gereken yere ulaşmana yardım edeceğim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ICON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ICON"
msgid "Woby and I will get you back together!"
msgstr "Woby ve ben seni eski hâline getireceğiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_IDOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_IDOL"
msgid "Do you need some assistance?"
msgstr "Yardıma ihtiyacın var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_LINK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_LINK"
msgid "What is it? Aaah, the suspense!"
msgstr "Ne bu? Aaaaa, gerilim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ROCK_GLASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ROCK_GLASS"
msgid "I think there's something in there..."
msgstr "Sanırım içinde bir şey var..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ROCK_IDOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ROCK_IDOL"
msgid "I think there's something in there..."
msgstr "Sanırım içinde bir şey var..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ROCK_SEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_ROCK_SEED"
msgid "I think there's something in there..."
msgstr "Sanırım içinde bir şey var..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_SEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_SEED"
msgid "We have to help it, Woby!"
msgstr "Ona yardım etmek zorundayız, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_WARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_ALTAR_WARD"
msgid "It's okay, we'll have you home in no time."
msgstr "Sorun yok, seni hemen evine döndüreceğiz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_CAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_CAP"
msgid "Another mushroom that isn't in my handbook..."
msgstr "El kitabımda olmayan başka bir mantar..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_CAP_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_CAP_COOKED"
msgid "This doesn't seem like the smartest idea."
msgstr "Bu en akıllıca fikir gibi görünmüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_DEVICE.CONSTRUCTION1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_DEVICE.CONSTRUCTION1"
msgid "We've still got a ways to go."
msgstr "Daha gidecek yolumuz var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_DEVICE.CONSTRUCTION2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_DEVICE.CONSTRUCTION2"
msgid "It's almost set up!"
msgstr "Neredeyse kuruldu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_DEVICE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_DEVICE.GENERIC"
msgid "Wow! I wonder what it's for?"
msgstr "Vay! Ne işe yarıyor acaba?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_FISSURE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_FISSURE.GENERIC"
msgid "Do you hear that whispering, Woby?"
msgstr "O fısıltıları duyuyor musun, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_FISSURE.NOLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_FISSURE.NOLIGHT"
msgid "Any monsters down there?"
msgstr "Aşağıda canavar var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_FISSURE_PLUGGED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_FISSURE_PLUGGED"
msgid "She trapped all the moon ghosts in their holes."
msgstr "Bütün ay hayaletlerini deliklerine hapsetti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.BURNING"
msgid "This is why we should always practice fire safety!"
msgstr "İşte bu yüzden her zaman ateş güvenliğine dikkat etmeliyiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.BURNT"
msgid "I guess it could've been worse."
msgstr "Sanırım daha kötü olabilirdi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.CHOPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.CHOPPED"
msgid "This one's already been chopped down."
msgstr "Bu çoktan kesilmiş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE.GENERIC"
msgid "That one definitely isn't in my handbook."
msgstr "Bu kesinlikle el kitabımda yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE_BLOSSOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE_BLOSSOM"
msgid "Who knew there were flowers on the moon?"
msgstr "Ayda çiçek olduğunu kim bilirdi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE_BLOSSOM_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOON_TREE_BLOSSOM_DRIED"
msgid "Dried perfectly!"
msgstr "Mükemmel kuruyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOOSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOOSE"
msgid "Woah! Now THAT should be Canada's national animal!"
msgstr "Vaay! İşte BU Kanada'nın ulusal hayvanı olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOOSEEGG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOOSEEGG"
msgid "I can't wait for them to hatch!"
msgstr "Yumurtadan çıkmaları için sabırsızlanıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOOSE_NESTING_GROUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOOSE_NESTING_GROUND"
msgid "Looks like we found its nest."
msgstr "Sanırım yuvasını bulduk."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOQUECA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOQUECA"
msgid "Wow, having a real chef around when you're camping is great!"
msgstr "Vay, kamp yaparken etrafta gerçek bir aşçı olması harika!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITO.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITO.GENERIC"
msgid "Tiny vampires of the insect world."
msgstr "Böcek dünyasının minik vampirleri."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITO.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITO.HELD"
msgid "Now I'm all itchy, I hope you're happy."
msgstr "Şimdi her yerim kaşınıyor, umarım mutlusundur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOBOMB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOBOMB"
msgid "Watch out, Woby! We don't wanna get caught up in the buzz!"
msgstr "Dikkat et, Woby! Vızıltıya yakalanmak istemeyiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOFERTILIZER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOFERTILIZER"
msgid "Plants love this stuff."
msgstr "Bitkiler bu şeye bayılır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOMERMSALVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOMERMSALVE"
msgid "That poor mosquito..."
msgstr "Zavallı sivrisinek..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOMUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOMUSK"
msgid "That's not a chew toy, Woby!"
msgstr "Bu çiğneme oyuncağı değil, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOSACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSQUITOSACK"
msgid "Good thing I'm not... squeamish..."
msgstr "İyi ki... mide bulantım yok..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSSLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOSSLING"
msgid "Aw, they're kind of cute!"
msgstr "Aaa, biraz şirinler!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOUND.DUG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOUND.DUG"
msgid "Well, my curiosity is satisfied."
msgstr "Eh, merakım giderildi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOUND.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MOUND.GENERIC"
msgid "I wonder if I'll find a skeleton down there..."
msgstr "Acaba aşağıda iskelet bulur muyum..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULLEDDRINK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULLEDDRINK"
msgid "I like to use the cinnamon stick as a straw."
msgstr "Tarçın çubuğunu pipet olarak kullanmayı seviyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULTIPLAYER_PORTAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULTIPLAYER_PORTAL"
msgid "Too bad it can't get us home."
msgstr "Eve götüremiyor olması üzücü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULTIPLAYER_PORTAL_MOONROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULTIPLAYER_PORTAL_MOONROCK"
msgid "This one looks way fancier... but still can't get us home."
msgstr "Bu çok daha şık görünüyor... ama yine de bizi evimize götüremiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULTITOOL_AXE_PICKAXE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MULTITOOL_AXE_PICKAXE"
msgid "It's two tools in one!"
msgstr "İki alet bir arada!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHGNOME
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHGNOME"
msgid "A living mushroom! Well, I guess all mushrooms are technically living..."
msgstr "Canlı bir mantar! Eh, sanırım bütün mantarlar teknik olarak canlı..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMBOMB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMBOMB"
msgid "My handbook says not to pick mushrooms you don't recognize."
msgstr "El kitabım tanımadığın mantarları toplama diyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMHAT"
msgid "It's not made of the poisonous kind, right?"
msgstr "Zehirli türden yapılmamıştır, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMSPROUT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMSPROUT.BURNT"
msgid "What a waste."
msgstr "Ne yazık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMSPROUT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOMSPROUT.GENERIC"
msgid "Woah! A giant mushroom!"
msgstr "Vaay! Devasa bir mantar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.BURNT"
msgid "That wasn't firewood!"
msgstr "O odun değildi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.EMPTY"
msgid "It needs something to get started."
msgstr "Başlamak için bir şeye ihtiyacı var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.LOTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.LOTS"
msgid "The mushrooms must love it there!"
msgstr "Mantarlar oraya bayılıyor olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.ROTTEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.ROTTEN"
msgid "Not much left of this log for the mushrooms to feed on."
msgstr "Mantarların beslenebileceği fazla kütük kalmamış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.SNOWCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.SNOWCOVERED"
msgid "My handbook says mushrooms need warmer weather to grow."
msgstr "El kitabım mantarların büyümesi için daha sıcak hava gerektiğini söylüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.SOME
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.SOME"
msgid "There's a few mushrooms now, but there'll probably be more soon."
msgstr "Şimdi birkaç mantar var ama yakında daha fazla olacaktır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.STUFFED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_FARM.STUFFED"
msgid "Mushrooms are kind of creepy when you think about them."
msgstr "Mantarlar düşününce biraz ürkütücü oluyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.BURNT"
msgid "Not mush we can do now."
msgstr "Mantar... pek bir şey yapamayız artık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.OFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.OFF"
msgid "It's easy to spot! You see, because it has spots! Heh..."
msgstr "Nokta atışı bulduk! Çünkü üstünde noktalar var! Heh..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.ON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT.ON"
msgid "My mom loves collecting odd lamps... I hope she's doing alright."
msgstr "Annem garip lambalar toplamayı sever... Umarım iyidir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT2.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT2.BURNT"
msgid "Not mush we can do now."
msgstr "Mantar... pek bir şey yapamayız artık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT2.OFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT2.OFF"
msgid "It's pretty... but I can't roast marshmallows over it."
msgstr "Güzel... ama üzerinde lokum kızartamam."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT2.ON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHROOM_LIGHT2.ON"
msgid "Nature is full of surprises."
msgstr "Doğa sürprizlerle dolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MEDIUM.ACIDCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MEDIUM.ACIDCOVERED"
msgid "Smells weird. Right, Woby?"
msgstr "Garip kokuyor. Değil mi, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MEDIUM.BLOOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MEDIUM.BLOOM"
msgid "Looks like this one's in bloom."
msgstr "Bu çiçek açmış gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MEDIUM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MEDIUM.GENERIC"
msgid "The mushrooms sure grow big down here..."
msgstr "Mantarlar burada cidden büyük büyüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_MOON"
msgid "It's actually kind of pretty!"
msgstr "Aslında bayağı güzel!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_SMALL.ACIDCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_SMALL.ACIDCOVERED"
msgid "Smells weird. Right, Woby?"
msgstr "Garip kokuyor. Değil mi, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_SMALL.BLOOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_SMALL.BLOOM"
msgid "It's making more mushrooms."
msgstr "Daha çok mantar yapıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_SMALL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_SMALL.GENERIC"
msgid "This one's kind of puny."
msgstr "Bu epey ufak tefek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL.ACIDCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL.ACIDCOVERED"
msgid "Smells weird. Right, Woby?"
msgstr "Garip kokuyor. Değil mi, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL.BLOOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL.BLOOM"
msgid "They only bloom spore-adically. Heh... nice one, Walter."
msgstr "Sadece spor-adik olarak çiçek açıyorlar. Heh... güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL.GENERIC"
msgid "That one's not in my handbook..."
msgstr "Bu el kitabımda yok..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL_WEBBED.ACIDCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL_WEBBED.ACIDCOVERED"
msgid "Smells weird. Right, Woby?"
msgstr "Garip kokuyor. Değil mi, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL_WEBBED.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUSHTREE_TALL_WEBBED.GENERIC"
msgid "There must be spiders around here somewhere!"
msgstr "Buralarda bir yerde örümcek olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBEARGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBEARGER"
msgid "A zombie Bearger? Neat!"
msgstr "Zombi Ayıger? Havalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBIRD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBIRD"
msgid "Look at that bird, Woby!"
msgstr "Şu kuşa bak, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBUZZARD_GESTALT.EATING_CORPSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBUZZARD_GESTALT.EATING_CORPSE"
msgid "It's really feasting, Woby!"
msgstr "Cidden ziyafet çekiyor, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBUZZARD_GESTALT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDBUZZARD_GESTALT.GENERIC"
msgid "I think it's a very bad sign."
msgstr "Sanırım bu çok kötü bir işaret."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDDEERCLOPS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDDEERCLOPS"
msgid "Aww, I think that poor Deerclops is sick!"
msgstr "Aaa, sanırım zavallı Geyikgöz hasta!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDHOUND.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDHOUND.DEAD"
msgid "Oh no... don't look, Woby."
msgstr "Ah hayır... bakma, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDHOUND.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDHOUND.GENERIC"
msgid "Is that an undead dog?"
msgstr "Bu yarı ölü bir köpek mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDHOUND.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDHOUND.SLEEPING"
msgid "See, they're harmless!"
msgstr "Bak, zararsızlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDWARG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATEDWARG"
msgid "That Varg doesn't look so good..."
msgstr "O Varg pek iyi görünmüyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATED_PENGUIN.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATED_PENGUIN.DEAD"
msgid "I guess it's properly dead now."
msgstr "Sanırım artık tamamen ölü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATED_PENGUIN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATED_PENGUIN.GENERIC"
msgid "It's a penguin, risen from the grave!"
msgstr "Mezardan kalkan bir penguen!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATED_PENGUIN.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATED_PENGUIN.SLEEPING"
msgid "I think it's sleeping, but it's hard to tell."
msgstr "Sanırım uyuyor ama anlamak zor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_DROPPER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_DROPPER"
msgid "Neat! There aren't any actual spider bits in these though, right?"
msgstr "Havalı! Ama bunlarda gerçek örümcek parçası yok, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_HEALER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_HEALER"
msgid "Neat! There aren't any actual spider bits in these though, right?"
msgstr "Havalı! Ama bunlarda gerçek örümcek parçası yok, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_HIDER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_HIDER"
msgid "Hey, cookies! Um... what are these made of, exactly?"
msgstr "Hey, kurabiye! Şey... bunlar tam olarak neden yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_MOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_MOON"
msgid "Hey, cookies! Um... what are these made of, exactly?"
msgstr "Hey, kurabiye! Şey... bunlar tam olarak neden yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_SPITTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_SPITTER"
msgid "Neat! There aren't any actual spider bits in these though, right?"
msgstr "Havalı! Ama bunlarda gerçek örümcek parçası yok, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_WARRIOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_WARRIOR"
msgid "Hey, cookies! Um... what are these made of, exactly?"
msgstr "Hey, kurabiye! Şey... bunlar tam olarak neden yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_WATER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.MUTATOR_WATER"
msgid "Hey, cookies! Um... what are these made of, exactly?"
msgstr "Hey, kurabiye! Şey... bunlar tam olarak neden yapılmış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NATURE_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NATURE_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "I hope it doesn't attract too many bees."
msgstr "Umarım çok fazla arı çekmez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTCAPHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTCAPHAT"
msgid "It's a little sleeping bag for your head."
msgstr "Kafan için küçük bir uyku tulumu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTLIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTLIGHT"
msgid "It really adds to the atmosphere."
msgstr "Atmosfere bayağı katkı sağlıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREFUEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREFUEL"
msgid "People always say my campfire stories are nightmare fuel."
msgstr "İnsanlar hep kamp ateşi hikâyelerimin karabasan yakıtı olduğunu söyler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREGROWTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREGROWTH"
msgid "We should probably stay away from those, Woby."
msgstr "Galiba bunlardan uzak durmalıyız, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARELIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARELIGHT"
msgid "But can you roast marshmallows over it?"
msgstr "Ama üzerinde lokum kızartabilir misin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREPIE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMAREPIE"
msgid "Looks good!"
msgstr "İyi görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.CALM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.CALM"
msgid "Nothing's really happening."
msgstr "Aslında hiçbir şey olmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.DAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.DAWN"
msgid "They're going away!"
msgstr "Gidiyorlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.NOMAGIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.NOMAGIC"
msgid "Aw, is it over?"
msgstr "Aaa, bitti mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.STEADY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.STEADY"
msgid "Just a steady stream of monsters!"
msgstr "Sürekli akan bir canavar dizisi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.WANING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.WANING"
msgid "I think they're running out of energy..."
msgstr "Sanırım enerjileri tükeniyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.WARN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.WARN"
msgid "Things are starting to get exciting!"
msgstr "İşler heyecanlanmaya başlıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.WAXING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTMARE_TIMEPIECE.WAXING"
msgid "I think the monsters are coming!"
msgstr "Sanırım canavarlar geliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTSTICK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTSTICK"
msgid "Whose bright idea was this? Get it? Because it's bright? Never mind."
msgstr "Bu kimin parlak fikriydi? Anladın mı? Çünkü parlak? Boş ver."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTSWORD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NIGHTSWORD"
msgid "That deeeefinitely has a curse on it."
msgstr "Bunda kesinlikleeeee bir lanet var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NITRE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NITRE"
msgid "Nitre here nor there. Heh..."
msgstr "Ne güherçile burada, ne orada. Heh..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NITRE_FORMATION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NITRE_FORMATION"
msgid "Huh. Looks like a big clump of rocks."
msgstr "Hı. Büyük bir kaya yığını gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NONSLIPGRIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NONSLIPGRIT"
msgid "Heh. My tools won't give me the slip with this!"
msgstr "Heh. Aletlerim artık bununla kayıp gitmeyecek!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NONSLIPGRITBOOSTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NONSLIPGRITBOOSTED"
msgid "No licking it off the ground, Woby!"
msgstr "Onu yerden yalama, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NUTRIENTSGOGGLESHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.NUTRIENTSGOGGLESHAT"
msgid "Woah, I can see right through the dirt!"
msgstr "Vay, toprağın içinden bakıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OAR"
msgid "I used to go canoing with my Pinetree Pioneer troop."
msgstr "Çamağacı Öncü grubumla kano yapardım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OAR_DRIFTWOOD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OAR_DRIFTWOOD"
msgid "I used to go canoing with my Pinetree Pioneer troop."
msgstr "Çamağacı Öncü grubumla kano yapardım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OAR_MONKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OAR_MONKEY"
msgid "Why is that paddle so sharp? Someone might get hurt!"
msgstr "Niye o kürek bu kadar keskin? Biri yaralanabilir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OASISLAKE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OASISLAKE.EMPTY"
msgid "An invisible lake?"
msgstr "Görünmez bir göl mü?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OASISLAKE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OASISLAKE.GENERIC"
msgid "We're saved, Woby!"
msgstr "Kurtulduk, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHABLEFLOTSAM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHABLEFLOTSAM"
msgid "Now that HAS to be a sea mons-- (sigh) no, just a muddy clump."
msgstr "İşte BU bir deniz canava-- (iç çekme) hayır, sadece çamur yığını."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_BALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_BALL"
msgid "Just a simple bobber."
msgstr "Sadece basit bir şamandıra."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_CANARY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_CANARY"
msgid "I followed the instructions perfectly."
msgstr "Talimatları kusursuzca takip ettim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_CROW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_CROW"
msgid "I followed the instructions perfectly."
msgstr "Talimatları kusursuzca takip ettim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_GOOSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_GOOSE"
msgid "It floats... like a feather, in fact."
msgstr "Yüzüyor... aslında, bir tüy gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_MALBATROSS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_MALBATROSS"
msgid "Thanks Malbatross!"
msgstr "Sağ ol Malbatross!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_NONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_NONE"
msgid "The diagram in my handbook shows a bobber, that might help."
msgstr "El kitabımdaki şemada şamandıra var, işe yarayabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_OVAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_OVAL"
msgid "A slightly less simple bobber."
msgstr "Biraz daha az basit bir şamandıra."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_ROBIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_ROBIN"
msgid "I followed the instructions perfectly."
msgstr "Talimatları kusursuzca takip ettim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_ROBIN_WINTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGBOBBER_ROBIN_WINTER"
msgid "I followed the instructions perfectly."
msgstr "Talimatları kusursuzca takip ettim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_DROWSY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_DROWSY"
msgid "Okay... just hold it carefully..."
msgstr "Tamam... sadece dikkatlice tut..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_HEAVY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_HEAVY"
msgid "Just watch Woby, I'll catch the biggest fish you've ever seen!"
msgstr "Sadece izle Woby, gördüğün en büyük balığı yakalayacağım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_RAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_RAIN"
msgid "I wonder how that works."
msgstr "Acaba nasıl çalışıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_SNOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_HERMIT_SNOW"
msgid "Snow fishing? Hmm, a new technique to master..."
msgstr "Kar avcılığı mı? Hım, ustalaşılacak yeni bir teknik..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPINNER_BLUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPINNER_BLUE"
msgid "Careful Woby, these aren't real food!"
msgstr "Dikkat et Woby, bunlar gerçek yemek değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPINNER_GREEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPINNER_GREEN"
msgid "Careful Woby, these aren't real food!"
msgstr "Dikkat et Woby, bunlar gerçek yemek değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPINNER_RED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPINNER_RED"
msgid "Careful Woby, these aren't real food!"
msgstr "Dikkat et Woby, bunlar gerçek yemek değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPOON_BLUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPOON_BLUE"
msgid "Careful Woby, these aren't real food!"
msgstr "Dikkat et Woby, bunlar gerçek yemek değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPOON_GREEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPOON_GREEN"
msgid "Careful Woby, these aren't real food!"
msgstr "Dikkat et Woby, bunlar gerçek yemek değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPOON_RED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGLURE_SPOON_RED"
msgid "Careful Woby, these aren't real food!"
msgstr "Dikkat et Woby, bunlar gerçek yemek değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGROD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISHINGROD"
msgid "This fishing rod's really sturdy!"
msgstr "Bu olta cidden sağlam!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_1"
msgid "SEA MONST-- oh wait, it's just a really ugly fish."
msgstr "DENİZ CANAVA-- ah dur, sadece çok çirkin bir balık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_2"
msgid "It's like it's staring into my soul..."
msgstr "Sanki ruhuma bakıyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_3"
msgid "None of these fish look anything like the ones in my handbook..."
msgstr "Bu balıkların hiçbiri el kitabımdakilere benzemiyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_4"
msgid "You're the unlucky fish who'll be my dinner."
msgstr "Akşam yemeğim olacak şanssız balık sensin."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_5"
msgid "Is it corn that mutated into a fish, or a fish that mutated into corn?"
msgstr "Bu balığa dönüşmüş mısır mı, yoksa mısıra dönüşmüş balık mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_6"
msgid "Don't you usually live in ponds?"
msgstr "Genelde göletlerde yaşamaz mısın?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_7
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_7"
msgid "Don't you usually live in ponds?"
msgstr "Genelde göletlerde yaşamaz mısın?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_8
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_8"
msgid "Will it melt if I try to cook it?"
msgstr "Pişirmeye çalışsam erir mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_9
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_MEDIUM_9"
msgid "Aww, it's got cute little ear fins!"
msgstr "Aaa, sevimli minik kulak yüzgeçleri var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_1"
msgid "It's barely big enough to call a guppy."
msgstr "Lebistesik diyecek kadar bile büyük değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_2"
msgid "I caught it on purpose. For practice."
msgstr "Bilerek yakaladım. Pratik için."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_3"
msgid "I usually catch much bigger fish, you know."
msgstr "Genelde çok daha büyük balık yakalarım, biliyor musun."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_4"
msgid "You know, sometimes catching smaller fish is the real challenge."
msgstr "Biliyor musun, bazen küçük balık yakalamak gerçek zorluktur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_5"
msgid "Careful the fins don't get stuck in your teeth."
msgstr "Yüzgeçler dişlerine takılmasın dikkat et."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_6"
msgid "It smells like dead leaves."
msgstr "Ölü yapraklar gibi kokuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_7
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_7"
msgid "Hey little buddy! Get it, because it's got a bud on its head?"
msgstr "Hey küçük filiz! Anladın mı, çünkü kafasında bir filiz var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_8
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_8"
msgid "Keep it away from anything flammable!"
msgstr "Tutuşabilecek hiçbir şeyden uzak tut!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_9
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANFISH_SMALL_9"
msgid "Hey! It's rude to spit at people!"
msgstr "Hey! İnsanlara tükürmek kabalık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANTREE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANTREE"
msgid "I guess they don't have to worry about getting enough water."
msgstr "Sanırım yeterli su bulmaktan endişelenmiyorlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANTREENUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANTREENUT"
msgid "That's one big seed!"
msgstr "İşte bu büyük bir tohum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANTREE_PILLAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANTREE_PILLAR"
msgid "It's a pretty swell shade tree!"
msgstr "Cidden havalı bir gölge ağacı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANVINE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANVINE"
msgid "Maybe one of them will turn out to be a snake!"
msgstr "Belki içinden biri yılan çıkar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANVINE_COCOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANVINE_COCOON"
msgid "That must be their nest! If I could just get a closer look..."
msgstr "Yuvaları olmalı! Sadece biraz daha yakından bakabilsem..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANVINE_COCOON_BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANVINE_COCOON_BURNT"
msgid "The poor spiders..."
msgstr "Zavallı örümcekler..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANWHIRLBIGPORTALEXIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANWHIRLBIGPORTALEXIT"
msgid "You smell anything in there, Woby?"
msgstr "Orada bir şey kokluyor musun, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANWHIRLPORTAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEANWHIRLPORTAL"
msgid "I don't think my water safety badge prepared me for that."
msgstr "Su güvenliği rozetim beni buna hazırlamadı sanırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.CAUGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.CAUGHT"
msgid "Look at all those fish!"
msgstr "Şu balıklara bak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.ESCAPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.ESCAPED"
msgid "Darnit, they got away!"
msgstr "Hay aksi, kaçtılar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.FIXED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.FIXED"
msgid "That wasn't so hard to fix."
msgstr "Tamir etmek o kadar zor değildi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.GENERIC"
msgid "Nets sure do make fishing easier."
msgstr "Ağlar balık tutmayı epey kolaylaştırıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.LOWERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER.LOWERED"
msgid "Soon I'll be roasting fish over a campfire."
msgstr "Yakında kamp ateşinde balık kızartıyor olacağım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OCEAN_TRAWLER_KIT"
msgid "I'd better build it if I want to catch any fish."
msgstr "Balık yakalamak istiyorsam onu yapsam iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT.GENERIC"
msgid "Need a little kelp? Heh. Good one, Walter."
msgstr "Biraz yosun-yardım gerekiyor mu? Heh. Güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT.LOTS_OF_KELP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT.LOTS_OF_KELP"
msgid "This is kelpful. Hah! Where are you getting this stuff, Walter?"
msgstr "Bu yosunca yararlı. Hah! Bu pun'ları nereden buluyorsun, Walter?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT.SOME_KELP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT.SOME_KELP"
msgid "More kelp is on the way! Get it, Woby?"
msgstr "Daha çok yosun-yardım yolda! Anladın mı, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT_UPGRADED.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT_UPGRADED.GENERIC"
msgid "Need a little kelp? Heh. Good one, Walter."
msgstr "Biraz yosun-yardım gerekiyor mu? Heh. Güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT_UPGRADED.LOTS_OF_KELP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT_UPGRADED.LOTS_OF_KELP"
msgid "This is kelpful. Hah! Where are you getting this stuff, Walter?"
msgstr "Bu yosunca yararlı. Hah! Bu pun'ları nereden buluyorsun, Walter?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT_UPGRADED.SOME_KELP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OFFERING_POT_UPGRADED.SOME_KELP"
msgid "More kelp is on the way! Get it, Woby?"
msgstr "Daha çok yosun-yardım yolda! Anladın mı, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONEMANBAND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONEMANBAND"
msgid "I've never played any of these instruments, but I'm sure I'll do great!"
msgstr "Bu enstrümanlardan hiçbirini çalmadım ama eminim harika olurum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION"
msgid "I hate chopping them."
msgstr "Onları doğramaktan nefret ediyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION_COOKED"
msgid "A juicy cooked onion."
msgstr "Sulu pişmiş soğan."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION_OVERSIZED"
msgid "I don't want to be the one who has to chop it."
msgstr "Onu doğramak zorunda kalan kişi olmak istemiyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ONION_SEEDS"
msgid "Where should we plant them, Woby?"
msgstr "Nereye ekelim, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OPALPRECIOUSGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OPALPRECIOUSGEM"
msgid "So many colours!"
msgstr "Bu kadar renk!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OPALSTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OPALSTAFF"
msgid "No Woby, this stick isn't for fetching!"
msgstr "Hayır Woby, bu sopa getir-götür için değil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGEAMULET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGEAMULET"
msgid "Getting there is half the fun!"
msgstr "Oraya varmak eğlencenin yarısı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGEGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGEGEM"
msgid "Orange you glad I found this orange gem? Ha ha, nice one Walter."
msgstr "Tur-uncu mu olmadın bu turuncu cevheri bulduğum için? Ha ha, güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGEMOONEYE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGEMOONEYE"
msgid "It's a pretty good landmark, you can't miss it!"
msgstr "Epey iyi bir nirengi noktası, gözden kaçıramazsın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGESTAFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ORANGESTAFF"
msgid "I bet I could race you now, Woby!"
msgstr "Bahse girerim seninle şimdi yarışabilirim, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTER"
msgid "Watch out, Woby. I think it wants our stuff."
msgstr "Dikkat et, Woby. Sanırım eşyalarımızı istiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTERDEN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTERDEN.GENERIC"
msgid "Looks like nothing. Oh well!"
msgstr "Hiçbir şeye benzemiyor. Eh işte!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTERDEN.HAS_LOOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTERDEN.HAS_LOOT"
msgid "I think we have a winner, Woby!"
msgstr "Sanırım kazanan belli, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTERDEN_DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.OTTERDEN_DEAD"
msgid "Woby, prepare to abandon ship."
msgstr "Woby, gemiyi terk etmeye hazırlan."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONETREE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONETREE"
msgid "Here it- nope, wait, this one isn't in my handbook either."
msgstr "İşte- hayır, dur, bu da el kitabımda yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONE_SAPLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONE_SAPLING"
msgid "It's still growing."
msgstr "Hâlâ büyüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONE_SCALE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONE_SCALE"
msgid "My handbook doesn't say anything about trees having scales..."
msgstr "El kitabımda ağaçların pulu olduğuna dair bir şey yok..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONE_SEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PALMCONE_SEED"
msgid "I should plant it, you can never have enough trees!"
msgstr "Onu ekmeliyim, ağaçtan asla bıkılmaz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PANDORASCHEST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PANDORASCHEST"
msgid "There's got to be something good inside!"
msgstr "İçinde mutlaka iyi bir şey olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PANETTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PANETTONE"
msgid "I could eat this forever."
msgstr "Bunu sonsuza kadar yiyebilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PANFLUTE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PANFLUTE"
msgid "It can't be too hard to play."
msgstr "Çalmak çok zor olamaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PAPYRUS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PAPYRUS"
msgid "Just some paper with nothing on it."
msgstr "Üzerinde hiçbir şey olmayan bir kâğıt sadece."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PAVLOVA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PAVLOVA"
msgid "Mmmm, it almost reminds me of a perfectly roasted marshmallow."
msgstr "Mmmm, neredeyse mükemmel kızartılmış lokumu hatırlatıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEGHOOK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEGHOOK"
msgid "That spit is corrosive!"
msgstr "O salya aşındırıcı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUIN"
msgid "I've never seen one up close before!"
msgstr "Daha önce yakından görmemiştim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUINCORPSE.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUINCORPSE.BURNING"
msgid "Smells kinda yummy."
msgstr "Bayağı leziz kokuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUINCORPSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUINCORPSE.GENERIC"
msgid "Stay away from it, Woby!"
msgstr "Ondan uzak dur, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUINCORPSE.REVIVING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PENGUINCORPSE.REVIVING"
msgid "Yes! I knew it!"
msgstr "Evet! Biliyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER"
msgid "Nice and red and ripe!"
msgstr "Güzel, kırmızı ve olgun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPERPOPPER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPERPOPPER"
msgid "Why does this taste minty...?"
msgstr "Niye nane gibi bir tadı var...?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER_COOKED"
msgid "It's hot!"
msgstr "Acı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Fire! Oh wait, it's just a hot pepper."
msgstr "Yangın! Ah dur, sadece acı biber."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEPPER_SEEDS"
msgid "Where should we plant them, Woby?"
msgstr "Nereye ekelim, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERD"
msgid "Hey, come back! We just want to eat you!"
msgstr "Hey, geri gel! Sadece seni yemek istiyoruz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDFAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDFAN"
msgid "Hey Woby, it's our biggest fan! Heh... good one, Walter."
msgstr "Hey Woby, en büyük hayranımız! Heh... güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDSHRINE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDSHRINE.BURNT"
msgid "Now nobody can use it."
msgstr "Artık kimse kullanamaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDSHRINE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDSHRINE.EMPTY"
msgid "It looks like something should go there."
msgstr "Oraya bir şey girmeli gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDSHRINE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PERDSHRINE.GENERIC"
msgid "This gobbler likes gold."
msgstr "Bu Perd altın seviyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEROGIES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PEROGIES"
msgid "The perfect size to pop in your mouth!"
msgstr "Ağzına atmak için kusursuz boyutta!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS"
msgid "Hope the bees aren't too mad at me."
msgstr "Umarım arılar bana çok kızgın değildir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS_DRIED"
msgid "Dried perfectly!"
msgstr "Mükemmel kuruyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS_EVIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS_EVIL"
msgid "I feel funny... did I accidentally pick some poison oak?"
msgstr "Tuhaf hissediyorum... yanlışlıkla zehirli meşe mi topladım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS_EVIL_DRIED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETALS_EVIL_DRIED"
msgid "Dried perfectly!"
msgstr "Mükemmel kuruyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETRIFIED_TREE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PETRIFIED_TREE"
msgid "What could've turned it to stone?"
msgstr "Onu ne taşa çevirmiş olabilir?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PHLEGM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PHLEGM"
msgid "Looks like a big booger."
msgstr "Büyük bir sümük gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PHONOGRAPH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PHONOGRAPH"
msgid "It's almost as good as a radio. Almost."
msgstr "Neredeyse radyo kadar iyi. Neredeyse."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PICKAXE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PICKAXE"
msgid "It's all mine!"
msgstr "Maden buldum, hepsi benim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PICKAXE_LUNARPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PICKAXE_LUNARPLANT"
msgid "Those are some really tough leaves!"
msgstr "Bunlar epey sert yapraklar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PICKLEDHERRING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PICKLEDHERRING"
msgid "Pickling is a really practical way to store food supplies."
msgstr "Salamura yapmak, yiyecek depolamanın gerçekten pratik bir yolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE1"
msgid "He's looking blue... because he's got blue tattoos, get it?"
msgstr "Mavi görünüyor... çünkü mavi dövmeleri var, anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE2"
msgid "Are you reddy? Heh, good one Walter."
msgstr "Kırmı-Hazır mısın? Heh, güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE3"
msgid "He's not afraid to get his hands... or anything else dirty."
msgstr "Ellerini... ya da başka bir yerini kirletmekten korkmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITE4"
msgid "He's probably really nice once you get to know him."
msgstr "Tanıyınca muhtemelen çok hoştur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER1"
msgid "He's looking blue... because he's got blue tattoos, get it?"
msgstr "Mavi görünüyor... çünkü mavi dövmeleri var, anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER2"
msgid "Are you reddy? Heh, good one Walter."
msgstr "Kırmı-Hazır mısın? Heh, güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER3"
msgid "He's not afraid to get his hands... or anything else dirty."
msgstr "Ellerini... ya da başka bir yerini kirletmekten korkmuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGELITEFIGHTER4"
msgid "He's probably really nice once you get to know him."
msgstr "Tanıyınca muhtemelen çok hoştur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGGUARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGGUARD"
msgid "I think we're already hitting it off!"
msgstr "Sanırım çoktan kafa dengi olduk!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGGYBACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGGYBACK"
msgid "This is giving me inspiration for a new campfire story..."
msgstr "Yeni bir kamp ateşi hikâyesi için bana ilham veriyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHEAD.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHEAD.BURNT"
msgid "Smells like burnt bacon."
msgstr "Yanmış pastırma gibi kokuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHEAD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHEAD.GENERIC"
msgid "Don't eat it Woby!"
msgstr "Onu yeme Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.BURNT"
msgid "That's why you don't play with fire."
msgstr "İşte bu yüzden ateşle oynamazsın."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.FULL"
msgid "I can hear oinking coming from inside..."
msgstr "İçeriden hor hor sesleri geliyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.GENERIC"
msgid "Why have a house when you could just camp all the time?"
msgstr "Hep kamp yapabilecekken ne diye ev olur ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.LIGHTSOUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGHOUSE.LIGHTSOUT"
msgid "Did they go to sleep?"
msgstr "Uyumaya mı gittiler?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGKING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGKING"
msgid "He looks like the Pioneer Leader of this troop."
msgstr "Bu grubun Öncü Lideri'ne benziyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.DEAD"
msgid "His bacon couldn't be saved."
msgstr "Pastırması kurtarılamadı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.FOLLOWER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.FOLLOWER"
msgid "See? We can all get along just fine."
msgstr "Gördün mü? Hepimiz iyi geçinebiliriz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.GENERIC"
msgid "It's a walking, talking pig!"
msgstr "Yürüyen, konuşan bir domuz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.GUARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.GUARD"
msgid "He looks pretty serious."
msgstr "Epey ciddi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.WEREPIG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGMAN.WEREPIG"
msgid "Double monster!"
msgstr "Çift canavar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSHRINE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSHRINE.BURNT"
msgid "This little piggy burnt down."
msgstr "Bu küçük domuzcuk yandı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSHRINE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSHRINE.EMPTY"
msgid "I think we're supposed to offer it meat."
msgstr "Sanırım ona et sunmamız gerekiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSHRINE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSHRINE.GENERIC"
msgid "What should we make, Woby?"
msgstr "Ne yapalım, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSKIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGSKIN"
msgid "Is this what people are always tossing around?"
msgstr "İnsanların etrafa fırlattıkları bu mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGTENT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGTENT"
msgid "It's a pretty decent tent."
msgstr "Epey iyi bir çadır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGTORCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIGTORCH"
msgid "Handy for finding your way in the dark."
msgstr "Karanlıkta yolunu bulmak için kullanışlı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIG_COIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIG_COIN"
msgid "It looks like a pig's snout! I wonder if that's on purpose."
msgstr "Domuz burnuna benziyor! Kasıtlı mı acaba?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIG_TOKEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIG_TOKEN"
msgid "I've already got a belt."
msgstr "Zaten kemerim var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PINECONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PINECONE"
msgid "I should find a good spot to plant this."
msgstr "Bunu ekecek iyi bir yer bulmalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PINECONE_SAPLING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PINECONE_SAPLING"
msgid "One day you'll be a nice big tree."
msgstr "Bir gün güzel kocaman bir ağaç olacaksın."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIRATE_FLAG_POLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIRATE_FLAG_POLE"
msgid "It's pretty good, but the Pinetree Pioneer flag looks better."
msgstr "Epey iyi ama Çamağacı Öncüleri bayrağı daha iyi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIRATE_STASH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PIRATE_STASH"
msgid "That has to be where the treasure is!"
msgstr "Hazinenin olduğu yer burası olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PITCHFORK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PITCHFORK"
msgid "I'm more of a forager than a farmer."
msgstr "Çiftçilikten çok toplayıcılık yaparım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANTMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANTMEAT"
msgid "Does this count as eating my vegetables?"
msgstr "Bu sebze yemiş olmaktan sayılır mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANTMEAT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANTMEAT_COOKED"
msgid "It has the weirdest flavour..."
msgstr "En tuhaf tadı var..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANTREGISTRYHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANTREGISTRYHAT"
msgid "It's like a handbook you wear on your head! A headbook?"
msgstr "Kafana taktığın bir el kitabı gibi! Kafa kitabı mı desem?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.GENERIC"
msgid "Guessing what it's going to be is half the fun."
msgstr "Ne olacağını tahmin etmek eğlencenin yarısı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.GROWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.GROWING"
msgid "I wish plants could grow as fast as you do Woby."
msgstr "Keşke bitkiler de senin kadar hızlı büyüyebilseydi Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.READY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.READY"
msgid "Fresh supplies!"
msgstr "Taze erzak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLANT_NORMAL.WITHERED"
msgid "Maybe it needs some water?"
msgstr "Belki suya ihtiyacı vardır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLAYBILL_THE_DOLL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLAYBILL_THE_DOLL"
msgid "It's like a radio play you can watch!"
msgstr "İzleyebileceğin bir radyo tiyatrosu gibi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLAYBILL_THE_PRINCESS_YOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PLAYBILL_THE_PRINCESS_YOTH"
