msgstr "Vaay, bu dişliler biraz ürkütücü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_PORTAL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_PORTAL.GENERIC"
