msgstr "Hadi Woby, çok eğlenceli olacak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_PORTAL_ENTRANCE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_PORTAL_ENTRANCE.GENERIC"
