#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_REVIVE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_REVIVE.GENERIC"
msgid "Ms. Wanda sure has a lot of clocks!"
msgstr "Bayan Wanda'nın gerçekten çok saati var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_REVIVE.RECHARGING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_REVIVE.RECHARGING"
msgid "Is that clock ticking backwards?"
msgstr "O saat geri mi tıklıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_WARP.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_WARP.GENERIC"
msgid "Ms. Wanda sure has a lot of clocks!"
msgstr "Bayan Wanda'nın gerçekten çok saati var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_WARP.RECHARGING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_WARP.RECHARGING"
msgid "Is that clock ticking backwards?"
msgstr "O saat geri mi tıklıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_WEAPON.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKETWATCH_WEAPON.GENERIC"
msgid "Um, Ms. Wanda... do you make all these clocks out in the woods?"
msgstr "Şey, Bayan Wanda... bu saatlerin hepsini ormanda mı yapıyorsunuz?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKET_SCALE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POCKET_SCALE"
msgid "Do you think there's a badge for catching the biggest fish?"
msgstr "Sence en büyük balığı tutmak için bir rozet var mıdır?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POLISHCOOKIE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POLISHCOOKIE"
msgid "There's fruit inside, it has to be at least a little healthy."
msgstr "İçinde meyve var, en azından biraz sağlıklı olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POLLY_ROGERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POLLY_ROGERS"
msgid "Thanks for the help, Polly! You'd make a great Pinetree Pioneer."
msgstr "Yardımın için sağ ol, Polly! Harika bir Çamağacı Öncüsü olurdun."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POLLY_ROGERSHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POLLY_ROGERSHAT"
msgid "I have to be careful putting it on, Polly likes to sleep in it."
msgstr "Takarken dikkatli olmam gerek, Polly içinde uyumayı seviyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE"
msgid "Fruit guts!"
msgstr "Meyve bağırsakları!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE_COOKED"
msgid "I thought it would taste better."
msgstr "Daha güzel olur sanmıştım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE_OVERSIZED"
msgid "Do pomegranates usually get that big?"
msgstr "Narlar genelde bu kadar büyük olur mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POMEGRANATE_SEEDS"
msgid "Where's a good spot to plant this?"
msgstr "Bunu ekecek iyi bir yer var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POND"
msgid "That'll make a swell swimming hole!"
msgstr "Harika bir yüzme havuzu olur!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PONDEEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PONDEEL"
msgid "It has sharp little teeth."
msgstr "Keskin küçük dişleri var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PONDFISH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PONDFISH"
msgid "Sorry, but someone has to be dinner."
msgstr "Üzgünüm ama birinin akşam yemeği olması lazım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POND_ALGAE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POND_ALGAE"
msgid "Pond monsters love algae!"
msgstr "Gölet canavarları alglere bayılır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POOP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POOP"
msgid "It's a natural part of nature!"
msgstr "Doğanın doğal bir parçası!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLEBLENDER_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLEBLENDER_ITEM"
msgid "It mixes all the food together."
msgstr "Bütün yemeği birlikte karıştırıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.COOKING_LONG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.COOKING_LONG"
msgid "Maybe I'll organize my bug collection while I'm waiting."
msgstr "Belki beklerken böcek koleksiyonumu düzenlerim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.COOKING_SHORT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.COOKING_SHORT"
msgid "It's almost done!"
msgstr "Neredeyse bitti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.DONE"
msgid "Mmmm, meal time!"
msgstr "Mmmm, yemek zamanı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.EMPTY"
msgid "I'll have to gather some food to start cooking."
msgstr "Pişirmeye başlamak için biraz yemek toplamam gerek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLECOOKPOT_ITEM.GENERIC"
msgid "It still doesn't beat roasting things over a campfire."
msgstr "Yine de kamp ateşinde kızartma yapmaya bedel değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLEFIREPIT_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLEFIREPIT_ITEM"
msgid "Woby, we're geniuses!"
msgstr "Woby, biz dahiyiz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLESPICER_ITEM.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLESPICER_ITEM.DONE"
msgid "Mmm, looks good!"
msgstr "Mmm, güzel görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLESPICER_ITEM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLESPICER_ITEM.GENERIC"
msgid "A little extra flavour never hurt anyone."
msgstr "Biraz ekstra lezzet kimseye zarar vermez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLETENT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLETENT"
msgid "Nice and sturdy!"
msgstr "Güzel ve sağlam!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLETENT_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PORTABLETENT_ITEM"
msgid "I'll have this set up lickety-split!"
msgstr "Bunu çabucak kuruyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO"
msgid "Should we mash them?"
msgstr "Onları ezelim mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATOSACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATOSACK"
msgid "Do you think I'd get muscles if I ate more potatoes, Woby?"
msgstr "Sence daha fazla patates yersem kaslı olur muyum, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATOSOUFFLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATOSOUFFLE"
msgid "This is really good, Mr. Warly!"
msgstr "Bu çok güzel, Bay Warly!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATOTORNADO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATOTORNADO"
msgid "I usually mash my potatoes."
msgstr "Genelde patatesleri ezerim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO_COOKED"
msgid "I love a campfire-roasted potato."
msgstr "Kamp ateşinde kızartılmış patates severim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO_OVERSIZED"
msgid "That's going to need a lot of mashing."
msgstr "Çok ezilmesi gerekecek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTATO_SEEDS"
msgid "Where should we plant them, Woby?"
msgstr "Nereye ekelim, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTTEDFERN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POTTEDFERN"
msgid "It's so... purple!"
msgstr "Çok... mor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POWCAKE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POWCAKE"
msgid "This could go badly."
msgstr "Bu kötü gidebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POWDER_MONKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.POWDER_MONKEY"
msgid "Maybe they're pirates cursed to be monkeys! Or monkeys cursed to be pirates..."
msgstr "Belki bunlar maymun olmaya lanetli korsanlardır! Ya da korsan olmaya lanetli maymunlar..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PREMIUMWATERINGCAN.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PREMIUMWATERINGCAN.EMPTY"
msgid "Whoops, looks like I'll have to find some water."
msgstr "Tüh, sanırım biraz su bulmam gerekecek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PREMIUMWATERINGCAN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PREMIUMWATERINGCAN.GENERIC"
msgid "Wow, fancy!"
msgstr "Vay, şık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PRIME_MATE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PRIME_MATE"
msgid "Arr, matey! Did I say that right?"
msgstr "Aaarr, dostum! Doğru söyledim mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUFFIN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUFFIN.GENERIC"
msgid "Hey, that one IS in my handbook!"
msgstr "Hey, bu el kitabımda VAR!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUFFIN.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUFFIN.HELD"
msgid "I hope it doesn't eat the bugs in my pocket."
msgstr "Umarım cebimdeki böcekleri yemez."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUFFIN.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUFFIN.SLEEPING"
msgid "Don't wake them up, Woby."
msgstr "Onları uyandırma, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN"
msgid "Is it Fall already?"
msgstr "Sonbahar mı geldi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINCARVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINCARVER"
msgid "Safety first, Woby!"
msgstr "Önce güvenlik, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINCOOKIE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINCOOKIE"
msgid "It's made from a vegetable, so it's healthy."
msgstr "Sebzeden yapılmış, yani sağlıklı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINHAT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINHAT.GENERIC"
msgid "I can't wait to scare someone!"
msgstr "Birini korkutmak için sabırsızlanıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINHAT.UNCARVED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINHAT.UNCARVED"
msgid "Let's face it, Woby... This pumpkin doesn't have one! Get it?"
msgstr "Yüzleşelim, Woby... Bu kabağın yüzü yok! Anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINPIE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKINPIE"
msgid "Mmmm, cut me a big slice!"
msgstr "Mmmm, bana büyük bir dilim kes!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_COOKED"
msgid "Hot, mushy pumpkin guts."
msgstr "Sıcak, lapa kabak bağırsakları."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_LANTERN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_LANTERN"
msgid "I heard a radio show once about a horseman with a pumpkin for a head!"
msgstr "Bir keresinde başında kabakla bir atlının radyo programını dinlemiştim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_OVERSIZED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_OVERSIZED"
msgid "It's the great pumpkin!"
msgstr "Yüce kabak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUMPKIN_SEEDS"
msgid "Woby, do you see a good spot to plant these?"
msgstr "Woby, bunları ekecek iyi bir yer görüyor musun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUNCHINGBAG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUNCHINGBAG"
msgid "Don't worry Woby, it's just for practice!"
msgstr "Merak etme Woby, sadece antrenman için!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUREBRILLIANCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PUREBRILLIANCE"
msgid "That's gotta be the shiniest rock I've ever seen."
msgstr "Bu gördüğüm en parlak taş olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PURPLEAMULET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PURPLEAMULET"
msgid "Do you hear the whispering too, Woby?"
msgstr "Sen de fısıltıları duyuyor musun, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PURPLEGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PURPLEGEM"
msgid "Purple's usually a friendly colour."
msgstr "Mor genelde dostça bir renktir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PURPLEMOONEYE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.PURPLEMOONEYE"
msgid "Purple! The friendliest colour!."
msgstr "Mor! En dostça renk!."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR.FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR.FULL"
msgid "It's in the process of digestinating."
msgstr "Sindirleme sürecinde."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR.GENERIC"
msgid "We'd better start cooking some offerings."
msgstr "Sunu pişirmeye başlasak iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_BOLLARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_BOLLARD"
msgid "As far as posts go, this one is adequate."
msgstr "Direkler arasında bu yeterince iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_IVY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_IVY"
msgid "Kind of clingy."
msgstr "Biraz yapışkan."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_QUEEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_QUEEN"
msgid "A monumental monument."
msgstr "Anıtsı bir anıt."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_STATUE1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_STATUE1"
msgid "It's an old statue."
msgstr "Eski bir heykel."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_STATUE2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_ALTAR_STATUE2"
msgid "What are you looking at?"
msgstr "Neye bakıyorsun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_BEEFALO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_BEEFALO"
msgid "Science says it should have died by now."
msgstr "Bilim şu ana kadar ölmesi gerektiğini söylüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_BERRYBUSH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_BERRYBUSH"
msgid "Those berries are all gone."
msgstr "O meyveler bitmiş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_BOWL_SILVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_BOWL_SILVER"
msgid "A bright bowl."
msgstr "Parlak bir kase."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CARROT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CARROT_SEEDS"
msgid "A handful of odd seeds."
msgstr "Bir avuç tuhaf tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CASSEROLEDISH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CASSEROLEDISH"
msgid "A dish for all seasonings."
msgstr "Her baharata-mevsime uygun bir tabak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CASSEROLEDISH_SMALL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CASSEROLEDISH_SMALL"
msgid "For making minuscule motleys."
msgstr "Minicik melezler yapmak için."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN1"
msgid "I'd like more than a penny for my thoughts."
msgstr "Düşüncelerim için bir kuruştan fazlası gerekir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN2"
msgid "A decent amount of coin."
msgstr "Hatırı sayılır bir miktar para."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN3"
msgid "Seems valuable."
msgstr "Değerli görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_COIN4"
msgid "We can use these to reopen the Gateway."
msgstr "Bunları Geçidi yeniden açmak için kullanabiliriz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRABMEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRABMEAT"
msgid "No imitations here."
msgstr "Burada taklit yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRABMEAT_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRABMEAT_COOKED"
msgid "I can put a meal together in a pinch."
msgstr "Kıskaç-anda bir yemek hazırlayabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRABTRAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRABTRAP"
msgid "A crabby trap."
msgstr "Huysuz bir yengeç tuzağı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRATE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_CRATE"
msgid "Kitchen stuff."
msgstr "Mutfak eşyası."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FERN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FERN"
msgid "Probably chock full of vitamins."
msgstr "Muhtemelen vitamin dolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FLOUR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FLOUR"
msgid "Ready for baking."
msgstr "Pişirmeye hazır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOLIAGE_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOLIAGE_COOKED"
msgid "We cooked the foliage."
msgstr "Yaprakları pişirdik."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.GENERIC"
msgid "I should offer it on the Altar of Gnaw."
msgstr "Onu Kemirme Sunağı'na sunmalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.MATCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.MATCH"
msgid "Science says this will appease the sky God."
msgstr "Bilim bunun gök Tanrı'yı yatıştıracağını söylüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.MATCH_BUT_SNACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.MATCH_BUT_SNACK"
msgid "It's more of a light snack, really."
msgstr "Aslında daha çok hafif bir atıştırmalık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.MISMATCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD.MISMATCH"
msgid "That's not what it wants."
msgstr "İstediği bu değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD_BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_FOOD_BURNT"
msgid "That one was an experiment."
msgstr "Bu bir deneydi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_GARLIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_GARLIC"
msgid "The number one breath enhancer."
