msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIG"
msgid "It's a super hairy pig."
msgstr "Süper tüylü bir domuz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIGELDER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIGELDER.GENERIC"
msgid "I guess you're in charge around here?"
msgstr "Sanırım buranın sorumlusu sensin?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIGELDER.SLEEPING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIGELDER.SLEEPING"
msgid "It's sleeping, for now."
msgstr "Şimdilik uyuyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIG_HOUSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIG_HOUSE"
msgid "It's seen better days."
msgstr "Daha iyi günler görmüş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIG_HOUSE_RUBBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SWAMPIG_HOUSE_RUBBLE"
msgid "Some pig's house was ruined."
msgstr "Bir domuzun evi yıkılmış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SYRUP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_SYRUP"
msgid "Adds sweetness to the mixture."
msgstr "Karışıma tatlılık katar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TOMATO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TOMATO"
msgid "It's red because it's full of science."
msgstr "Kırmızı çünkü içi bilim dolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TOMATO_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TOMATO_COOKED"
msgid "Cooking's easy if you understand chemistry."
msgstr "Kimyayı anlıyorsan yemek pişirmek kolay."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TOMATO_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TOMATO_SEEDS"
msgid "A handful of odd seeds."
msgstr "Bir avuç tuhaf tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TRADER_MERM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TRADER_MERM"
msgid "Maybe they'd be willing to trade."
msgstr "Belki takas etmek isterler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TRADER_MERM2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TRADER_MERM2"
msgid "Maybe they'd be willing to trade."
msgstr "Belki takas etmek isterler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TURNIP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TURNIP"
msgid "It's a raw turnip."
msgstr "Çiğ bir şalgam."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TURNIP_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TURNIP_COOKED"
msgid "Cooking is science in practice."
msgstr "Pişirmek pratikteki bilimdir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TURNIP_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_TURNIP_SEEDS"
msgid "A handful of odd seeds."
msgstr "Bir avuç tuhaf tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_WHEAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_WHEAT"
msgid "It looks a bit grainy."
msgstr "Biraz tane-li görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_WHEAT_SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.QUAGMIRE_WHEAT_SEEDS"
msgid "A handful of odd seeds."
msgstr "Bir avuç tuhaf tohum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBIT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBIT.GENERIC"
msgid "A real jackalope! Come here little guy!"
msgstr "Gerçek bir jackalope! Buraya gel ufaklık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBIT.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBIT.HELD"
msgid "Look, the antlers aren't held on with paste or anything!"
msgstr "Bak, boynuzlar yapıştırıcıyla falan tutturulmamış!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHAT"
msgid "Whoever wears that is a real hare-brain! Oh, Walter!"
msgstr "Bunu giyen gerçek bir tavşan-akıllı! Of, Walter!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOLE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOLE.GENERIC"
msgid "We found its den!"
msgstr "İnini bulduk!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOLE.SPRING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOLE.SPRING"
msgid "Looks like a cave-in."
msgstr "Çökme gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOUSE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOUSE.BURNT"
msgid "That's what happens when you're irresponsible with fire."
msgstr "Ateşle dikkatsiz olunca böyle olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOUSE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITHOUSE.GENERIC"
msgid "Do they ever dream of eating carrots and wake up with their house missing?"
msgstr "Hiç havuç yediklerini rüyalarında görüp evleri kaybolmuş bir şekilde uyandıkları olur mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGHORN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGHORN"
msgid "I can't carrot a tune! Heh. Nice, Walter."
msgstr "Havuçla bir nağme tutturamam! Heh. Güzeldi, Walter."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGHORN_CHEST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGHORN_CHEST"
msgid "Woby, now you don't have to carry everything!"
msgstr "Woby, artık her şeyi taşımak zorunda değilsin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGMINION_BUNNYMAN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGMINION_BUNNYMAN"
msgid "Who's a cranky pants?"
msgstr "Kim huysuzun teki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGSPEAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKINGSPEAR"
msgid "The most striking part of the rabbit. Heh."
msgstr "Tavşanın en vurucu kısmı. Heh."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKING_AGGRESSIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKING_AGGRESSIVE"
msgid "Someone's in a bad mood!"
msgstr "Birinin keyfi yok!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKING_LUCKY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKING_LUCKY"
msgid "Let's catch it, Woby!"
msgstr "Hadi yakalayalım, Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKING_PASSIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RABBITKING_PASSIVE"
msgid "It looks friendly!"
msgstr "Dostça görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINCOAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINCOAT"
msgid "Gotta be prepared for the elements!"
msgstr "Doğa olaylarına hazırlıklı olmak gerek!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINHAT"
msgid "I wonder if I could make one for Woby too."
msgstr "Woby için de bir tane yapabilir miyim acaba."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINOMETER.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINOMETER.BURNT"
msgid "It wasn't really that useful anyway."
msgstr "Zaten o kadar da kullanışlı değildi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINOMETER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAINOMETER.GENERIC"
msgid "A Pinetree Pioneer can smell rain coming a mile away."
msgstr "Bir Çamağacı Öncüsü kilometrelerce uzaktan yağmurun kokusunu alabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RATATOUILLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RATATOUILLE"
msgid "Apparently there's no actual rats in it."
msgstr "Görünüşe göre içinde gerçek fare yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAZOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RAZOR"
msgid "I found a whisker on my chin, I'm sure my beard will come in any day now."
msgstr "Çenemde bir tüy buldum, eminim sakalım her an gelecek."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD"
msgid "I could listen to this forever!"
msgstr "Bunu sonsuza kadar dinleyebilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_BALATRO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_BALATRO"
msgid "That's right, Woby! It's a real doozy!"
msgstr "Doğru, Woby! Bu gerçek bir ezici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_CREEPYFOREST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_CREEPYFOREST"
msgid "It's no Midnight Broadcast, but it's still pretty good."
msgstr "Gece Yarısı Yayını değil ama yine de epey iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DANGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DANGER"
msgid "Woby likes to howl along, don't you girl?"
msgstr "Woby buna eşlik etmeyi seviyor, değil mi kızım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DAWN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DAWN"
msgid "It's no Midnight Broadcast, but it's still pretty good."
msgstr "Gece Yarısı Yayını değil ama yine de epey iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DRSTYLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DRSTYLE"
msgid "Woby likes to howl along, don't you girl?"
msgstr "Woby buna eşlik etmeyi seviyor, değil mi kızım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_DUSK"
msgid "Woby likes to howl along, don't you girl?"
msgstr "Woby buna eşlik etmeyi seviyor, değil mi kızım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_EFS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_EFS"
msgid "It's no Midnight Broadcast, but it's still pretty good."
msgstr "Gece Yarısı Yayını değil ama yine de epey iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_END
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_END"
msgid "Oh, that's a good one!"
msgstr "Ah, bu bir güzel!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_HALLOWEDNIGHTS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_HALLOWEDNIGHTS"
msgid "Instant classic!"
msgstr "Anında klasik!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_MAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_MAIN"
msgid "Woby likes to howl along, don't you girl?"
msgstr "Woby buna eşlik etmeyi seviyor, değil mi kızım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_WORKTOBEDONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RECORD_WORKTOBEDONE"
msgid "It's no Midnight Broadcast, but it's still pretty good."
msgstr "Gece Yarısı Yayını değil ama yine de epey iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDGEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDGEM"
msgid "I think this gem might be magic."
msgstr "Sanırım bu cevher sihirli olabilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDLANTERN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDLANTERN"
msgid "I like this dramatic lighting!"
msgstr "Bu dramatik ışıklandırmayı sevdim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDMOONEYE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDMOONEYE"
msgid "This eye looks bloodshot!"
msgstr "Bu göz kanlanmış görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDPOUCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REDPOUCH"
msgid "It's jingling."
msgstr "Şıngırdıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_CAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_CAP"
msgid "That definitely looks poisonous."
msgstr "Bu kesinlikle zehirli görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_CAP_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_CAP_COOKED"
msgid "Did cooking it make it less poisonous?"
msgstr "Pişirmek onu daha az mı zehirli yaptı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_MUSHROOM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_MUSHROOM.GENERIC"
msgid "Probably shouldn't pick that one."
msgstr "Muhtemelen bunu toplamamalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_MUSHROOM.INGROUND
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_MUSHROOM.INGROUND"
msgid "There's a mushroom hiding down there."
msgstr "Aşağıda saklanan bir mantar var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_MUSHROOM.PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RED_MUSHROOM.PICKED"
msgid "Maybe it will grow back?"
msgstr "Belki geri büyür?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REEDS.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REEDS.BURNING"
msgid "Uh oh, who wasn't practicing fire safety?"
msgstr "Eyvah, kim ateş güvenliğine uymamış?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REEDS.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REEDS.GENERIC"
msgid "A pretty normal thing to see in a swamp."
msgstr "Bataklıkta görmek için epey normal bir şey."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REEDS.PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REEDS.PICKED"
msgid "Nothing left to gather here."
msgstr "Burada toplanacak bir şey kalmamış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REFINED_DUST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REFINED_DUST"
msgid "It took a long time to collect all that dust."
msgstr "Bütün o tozu toplamak çok uzun sürdü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REFLECTIVEVEST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REFLECTIVEVEST"
msgid "Do I look as cool as I feel?"
msgstr "Hissettiğim kadar havalı görünüyor muyum?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RELIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RELIC"
msgid "It's even older than the knick-knacks at my grandpa's house."
msgstr "Dedemin evindeki ıvır zıvırlardan bile daha eski."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB.BURNT"
msgid "Did that look like a campfire?!"
msgstr "Bu kamp ateşine mi benziyordu?!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB.GENERIC"
msgid "I never knew science was such an important part of survival."
msgstr "Bilimin hayatta kalmanın bu kadar önemli bir parçası olduğunu hiç bilmezdim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB2.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB2.BURNT"
msgid "I wish things would stop catching fire."
msgstr "Keşke eşyalar tutuşmayı bıraksa."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB2.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB2.GENERIC"
msgid "They never taught us about alchemy in school."
msgstr "Okulda bize simyayı hiç öğretmediler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB3.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB3.BURNT"
msgid "I guess the magic wasn't fireproof."
msgstr "Sanırım sihir ateşe dayanıklı değilmiş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB3.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB3.GENERIC"
msgid "Is it really magic?"
msgstr "Bu gerçekten sihir mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB4.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB4.BURNT"
msgid "I guess that's one way of putting an end to the mystery."
msgstr "Sanırım bu da gizemi sona erdirmenin bir yolu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB4.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESEARCHLAB4.GENERIC"
msgid "I don't really understand how it's supposed to work."
msgstr "Nasıl çalışması gerektiğini pek anlamıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESKIN_TOOL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESKIN_TOOL"
msgid "It changes how things look, but they're still the same deep down."
msgstr "Eşyaların görünümünü değiştiriyor ama derinlerde hâlâ aynılar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESURRECTIONSTATUE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESURRECTIONSTATUE.BURNT"
msgid "What a waste of supplies..."
msgstr "Ne malzeme israfı..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESURRECTIONSTATUE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESURRECTIONSTATUE.GENERIC"
msgid "I thought bringing back the dead involved more levers and electricity."
msgstr "Ölüleri geri getirmenin daha çok kol ve elektrik içereceğini sanırdım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESURRECTIONSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RESURRECTIONSTONE"
msgid "It must've been used by an ancient civilization!"
msgstr "Kadim bir medeniyet kullanmış olmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REVIVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.REVIVER"
msgid "Did you ever hear the story about the beating heart hidden under the floorboards?"
msgstr "Hiç döşeme tahtaları altında saklı çarpan kalp hikâyesini duydun mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RHINODRILL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RHINODRILL"
msgid "He's got a nose for this kind of work."
msgstr "Bu tür işler için iyi bir burnu var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROASTTURKEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROASTTURKEY"
msgid "Woby wants some too!"
msgstr "Woby da istiyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN.GENERIC"
msgid "Wonder how they got here?"
msgstr "Buraya nasıl gelmişler acaba?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN.HELD"
msgid "Are you happy in my pocket?"
msgstr "Cebimde mutlu musun?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN_WINTER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN_WINTER.GENERIC"
msgid "My handbook doesn't show them in this colour..."
msgstr "El kitabım onları bu renkte göstermiyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN_WINTER.HELD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBIN_WINTER.HELD"
msgid "They're extra downy."
msgstr "Ekstra tüylüler."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBOT_BLUEPRINT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBOT_BLUEPRINT"
msgid "Is this really for sewing?"
msgstr "Bu cidden dikiş için mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBOT_PUPPET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROBOT_PUPPET"
msgid "Don't worry, a Pinetree Pioneer always helps those in need!"
msgstr "Merak etme, bir Çamağacı Öncüsü her zaman ihtiyaç sahiplerine yardım eder!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK"
msgid "It would be more useful in smaller pieces."
msgstr "Daha küçük parçalar hâlinde daha kullanışlı olurdu."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCKS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCKS"
msgid "Maybe I could make a fire pit."
msgstr "Belki ateş çukuru yaparım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCKY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCKY"
msgid "Wow! Look at you!"
msgstr "Vay! Şu hâline bak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.BARREN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.BARREN"
msgid "I don't think it'll be making fruit anytime soon."
msgstr "Yakında meyve vereceğini sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.BURNING"
msgid "It's on fire!"
msgstr "Yanıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.DISEASED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.DISEASED"
msgid "Maybe that's how a moon bush is supposed to look?"
msgstr "Belki ay çalısı böyle görünmesi gerekiyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.DISEASING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.DISEASING"
msgid "Is something wrong with it?"
msgstr "Bir şey mi var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.GENERIC"
msgid "Is that tree growing... rocks?"
msgstr "Bu ağaç... kaya mı yetiştiriyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.PICKED"
msgid "We already gathered all the fruit."
msgstr "Bütün meyveleri çoktan topladık."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_BUSH.WITHERED"
msgid "I don't think it likes the heat."
msgstr "Sıcağı sevmiyor sanırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT"
msgid "It's hard as a rock!"
msgstr "Kaya kadar sert!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT_RIPE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT_RIPE"
msgid "It's finally ripe! ...I think."
msgstr "Sonunda olgunlaştı! ...Sanırım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT_RIPE_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT_RIPE_COOKED"
msgid "That's better."
msgstr "Bu daha iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT_SPROUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_AVOCADO_FRUIT_SPROUT"
msgid "Oh, it's growing!"
msgstr "Aaa, büyüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_ICE.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_ICE.GENERIC"
msgid "This will really give you the chills."
msgstr "Bu seni gerçekten üşütür."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_ICE.MELTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_ICE.MELTED"
msgid "Ice sometimes does that."
msgstr "Buz bazen öyle yapar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_ICE_MELTED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_ICE_MELTED"
msgid "Ice sometimes does that."
msgstr "Buz bazen öyle yapar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.GENERIC"
msgid "A crusted over lava pit."
msgstr "Kabuk bağlamış bir lav çukuru."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.LOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.LOW"
msgid "The lava's crusting over."
msgstr "Lav kabuk bağlıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.NORMAL"
msgid "Nice and comfy."
msgstr "Güzel ve rahat."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_LIGHT.OUT"
msgid "Looks fragile."
msgstr "Kırılgan görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_MOON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_MOON"
msgid "I wonder how it affects were-people. I should ask Mr. Woodie."
msgstr "Acaba kurt-insanları nasıl etkiliyor. Bay Woodie'ye sormalıyım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_PETRIFIED_TREE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_PETRIFIED_TREE"
msgid "What could've turned it to stone?"
msgstr "Onu ne taşa çevirmiş olabilir?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_PETRIFIED_TREE_OLD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROCK_PETRIFIED_TREE_OLD"
msgid "What could've turned it to stone?"
msgstr "Onu ne taşa çevirmiş olabilir?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROOK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROOK"
msgid "I wonder how it works?"
msgstr "Acaba nasıl çalışıyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROOK_NIGHTMARE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROOK_NIGHTMARE"
msgid "Wow! It looks even more dangerous than the usual ones!"
msgstr "Vay! Normallerinden daha tehlikeli görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROPE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROPE"
msgid "An essential part of any adventuring kit."
msgstr "Her macera setinin temel bir parçası."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROPE_BRIDGE_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROPE_BRIDGE_KIT"
msgid "This is basic Pinetree Pioneer stuff... now, where are those instructions?"
msgstr "Bu temel Çamağacı Öncüsü işi... şimdi, talimatlar nerede?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROSEGLASSESHAT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROSEGLASSESHAT.GENERIC"
msgid "Winona's been wearing those a lot lately."
msgstr "Winona son zamanlarda bunları çok takıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROSEGLASSESHAT.MISSINGSKILL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROSEGLASSESHAT.MISSINGSKILL"
msgid "only_used_by_winona"
msgstr "only_used_by_winona"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROTTENEGG.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROTTENEGG.GENERIC"
msgid "That's definitely gone off."
msgstr "Bu kesinlikle bozulmuş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROYAL_JELLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.ROYAL_JELLY"
msgid "It was a royal pain to get."
msgstr "Bunu almak kraliyet derdiydi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUBBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUBBLE"
msgid "A bunch of really old rocks. I guess all rocks are old..."
msgstr "Çok eski kayalar. Sanırım bütün kayalar eskidir..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUINSHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUINSHAT"
msgid "I'm the king! You have to listen to what I say!"
msgstr "Ben kralım! Söylediğimi dinlemek zorundasınız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUINS_BAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUINS_BAT"
msgid "I was never great at baseball... but maybe I would be with a bat like this!"
msgstr "Beyzbolda hiç iyi değildim... ama belki böyle bir sopayla iyi olurum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUINS_RUBBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.RUINS_RUBBLE"
msgid "We can fix it up with some Pinetree Pioneer determination!"
msgstr "Biraz Çamağacı Öncüsü kararlılığıyla onarabiliriz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SACRED_CHEST.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SACRED_CHEST.GENERIC"
msgid "There HAS to be something good in there, just look at it!"
msgstr "İçinde MUTLAKA iyi bir şey olmalı, şuna baksana!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SACRED_CHEST.LOCKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SACRED_CHEST.LOCKED"
msgid "How do we get it open? Any ideas, Woby?"
msgstr "Nasıl açacağız? Fikrin var mı, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLEHORN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLEHORN"
msgid "It can't be comfortable wearing a saddle all the time."
msgstr "Sürekli eyer takmak rahat olamaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_BASIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_BASIC"
msgid "Guess you need a saddle to ride some animals."
msgstr "Sanırım bazı hayvanlara binmek için eyer gerekiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_RACE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_RACE"
msgid "See? Bugs are helpful in lots of ways!"
msgstr "Gördün mü? Böcekler birçok şekilde faydalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_SHADOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_SHADOW"
msgid "Neat seat!"
msgstr "Havalı koltuk!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_WAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_WAR"
msgid "It's almost as comfy as sitting in Woby's fur."
msgstr "Neredeyse Woby'nin tüylerinde oturmak kadar rahat."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_WATHGRITHR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SADDLE_WATHGRITHR"
msgid "Wanna try it on, Woby? Don't worry, I was just kidding!"
msgstr "Denemek ister misin, Woby? Merak etme, şaka yapıyordum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALSA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALSA"
msgid "It only comes with one chip?!"
msgstr "Sadece bir cipsle mi geliyor?!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTBOX
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTBOX"
msgid "Salt is great for preserving your supplies."
msgstr "Tuz erzakını korumak için harikadır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTLICK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTLICK"
msgid "Don't eat that Woby, it's for the beefalo!"
msgstr "Onu yeme Woby, bızonsığırlar için!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTLICK_IMPROVED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTLICK_IMPROVED"
msgid "You're not a beefalo, Woby."
msgstr "Sen bızonsığır değilsin, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTROCK"
msgid "Hey, I think that's salt!"
msgstr "Hey, sanırım bu tuz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTSTACK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTSTACK.GENERIC"
msgid "Maybe there's a Medusa nearby... a salt Medusa..."
msgstr "Belki yakınlarda bir Medusa vardır... bir tuz Medusası..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTSTACK.GROWING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTSTACK.GROWING"
msgid "I'm glad they grow back!"
msgstr "Geri büyümelerine sevindim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTSTACK.MINED_OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTSTACK.MINED_OUT"
msgid "Nothing left to gather."
msgstr "Toplanacak bir şey kalmamış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTY_DOG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTY_DOG"
msgid "He's not technically a dog, but he's still a good boy!"
msgstr "Teknik olarak bir köpek değil ama yine de iyi bir oğlan!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTY_DOGHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SALTY_DOGHAT"
msgid "It looks so official!"
msgstr "Çok resmi görünüyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANDBLOCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANDBLOCK"
msgid "Woah! How do you do that?"
msgstr "Vaay! Nasıl yapıyorsun bunu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANDSPIKE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANDSPIKE"
msgid "Hey, careful! You almost hit me with that!"
msgstr "Hey, dikkat! Az kalsın bana çarpıyordun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANITYROCK.ACTIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANITYROCK.ACTIVE"
msgid "Hey, where did that come from?"
msgstr "Hey, bu nereden çıktı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANITYROCK.INACTIVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SANITYROCK.INACTIVE"
msgid "I swear there was something here a second ago."
msgstr "Yemin ederim bir saniye önce burada bir şey vardı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.BURNING"
msgid "Someone grab some water!"
msgstr "Birisi su getirsin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.DISEASED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.DISEASED"
msgid "That doesn't look healthy."
msgstr "Sağlıklı görünmüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.DISEASING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.DISEASING"
msgid "Is it supposed to look like that?"
msgstr "Böyle mi görünmesi gerekiyor?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.GENERIC"
msgid "It's a baby tree."
msgstr "Bebek bir ağaç."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.PICKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.PICKED"
msgid "Now it'll never grow into a tree."
msgstr "Artık asla ağaç olamayacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.WITHERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SAPLING.WITHERED"
msgid "I guess it's too hot out."
msgstr "Sanırım dışarısı çok sıcak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCANDATA
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCANDATA"
msgid "Neat! Wanna scan me next?"
msgstr "Havalı! Sıradaki olarak beni tarar mısın?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCARECROW.BURNING
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCARECROW.BURNING"
msgid "I guess that makes it look a little scarier."
msgstr "Sanırım bu onu biraz daha korkutucu kılıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCARECROW.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCARECROW.BURNT"
msgid "Not much use to us now."
msgstr "Artık bizim için pek faydası yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCARECROW.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCARECROW.GENERIC"
msgid "Who'd be scared of that?"
msgstr "Bundan kim korkar ki?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCORCHED_SKELETON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCORCHED_SKELETON"
msgid "I think the time for first aid has long passed."
msgstr "Sanırım ilk yardım zamanı çoktan geçti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCRAPBOOK_PAGE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCRAPBOOK_PAGE"
msgid "I should add it to my scrapbook!"
msgstr "Bunu karalama defterime eklemeliyim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCRAPHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCRAPHAT"
msgid "That werepig was so big, I can wear his shoulder pad as a hat!"
msgstr "O kurt domuz o kadar büyüktü ki, omuz kemerini şapka olarak takabilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCRAP_MONOCLEHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCRAP_MONOCLEHAT"
msgid "Woah! It's like binoculars, but... well, the opposite of that!"
msgstr "Vaay! Dürbün gibi ama... şey, tam tersi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.BLOCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.BLOCK"
msgid "This doesn't look too hard! Or does it..."
msgstr "Bu o kadar zor görünmüyor! Yoksa öyle mi..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.BURNT"
msgid "Don't we have a perfectly good fire pit?"
msgstr "Mükemmel bir ateş çukurumuz yok mu zaten?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.EMPTY"
msgid "Time for some arts and crafts."
msgstr "Sanat ve el işi zamanı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.SCULPTURE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTINGTABLE.SCULPTURE"
msgid "Hey Woby, look! I'm getting good at this!"
msgstr "Hey Woby, bak! Bunda iyileşiyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.COVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.COVERED"
msgid "One part of this statue looks older than the other."
msgstr "Bu heykelin bir kısmı diğerinden daha eski görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.FINISHED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.FINISHED"
msgid "Finished!"
msgstr "Bitti!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.READY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.READY"
msgid "Huh? I think I hear something moving in there."
msgstr "Hı? İçeride bir şey hareket ediyor gibi geliyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.UNCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPBODY.UNCOVERED"
msgid "Can you sniff out the missing piece Woby?"
msgstr "Eksik parçayı koklayarak bulabilir misin Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPHEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_BISHOPHEAD"
msgid "What's that doing here?"
msgstr "Bunun burada ne işi var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.COVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.COVERED"
msgid "There's something weird about it."
msgstr "Onda tuhaf bir şey var."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.FINISHED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.FINISHED"
msgid "That looks better."
msgstr "Bu daha iyi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.READY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.READY"
msgid "Huh? I think I hear something moving in there."
msgstr "Hı? İçeride bir şey hareket ediyor gibi geliyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.UNCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTBODY.UNCOVERED"
msgid "It's all broken up."
msgstr "Tamamen kırılmış."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTHEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_KNIGHTHEAD"
msgid "That's one way to get a head. Get it?"
msgstr "Kafa edinmenin bir yolu. Anladın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.COVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.COVERED"
msgid "I think there's something else hiding in that marble."
msgstr "Sanırım o mermerde başka bir şey saklı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.FINISHED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.FINISHED"
msgid "That was easy enough."
msgstr "Yeterince kolaydı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.READY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.READY"
msgid "Huh? I think I hear something moving in there."
msgstr "Hı? İçeride bir şey hareket ediyor gibi geliyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.UNCOVERED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKBODY.UNCOVERED"
msgid "There's something missing..."
msgstr "Eksik bir şey var..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKNOSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SCULPTURE_ROOKNOSE"
msgid "How did it get there?"
msgstr "Oraya nasıl gitmiş?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEAFARING_PROTOTYPER.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEAFARING_PROTOTYPER.BURNT"
msgid "We should really be more careful with our resources."
msgstr "Cidden kaynaklarımızla daha dikkatli olmalıyız."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEAFARING_PROTOTYPER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEAFARING_PROTOTYPER.GENERIC"
msgid "We're going to need a better boat."
msgstr "Daha iyi bir tekneye ihtiyacımız olacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEAFOODGUMBO
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEAFOODGUMBO"
msgid "Packed full of flavour!"
msgstr "Lezzetle dolu!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEASTACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEASTACK"
msgid "Rocks off the port bow!"
msgstr "İskele tarafında kayalar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SECURITY_PULSE_CAGE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SECURITY_PULSE_CAGE"
msgid "It's empty, Woby. Let's find something to put in there."
msgstr "Boş, Woby. İçine koyacak bir şey bulalım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SECURITY_PULSE_CAGE_FULL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SECURITY_PULSE_CAGE_FULL"
msgid "I wonder if there is a glowing ball trapping badge."
msgstr "Acaba parlayan top yakalama rozeti var mı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEEDPOUCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEEDPOUCH"
msgid "You can never have too many pockets!"
msgstr "Çok cep çok olmaz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEEDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEEDS"
msgid "It's nice of the birds to share."
msgstr "Kuşların paylaşması ne hoş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEEDS_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEEDS_COOKED"
msgid "You make do with what you have when you're out in the wilderness."
msgstr "Doğada elinde olanla idare edersin."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SENTRYWARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SENTRYWARD"
msgid "Map making is so much more interesting here!"
msgstr "Burada harita yapımı çok daha ilginç!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_KIT"
msgid "Better make sure all my badges are secure!"
msgstr "Bütün rozetlerimin sağlam olduğundan emin olsam iyi olur!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_MANNEQUIN.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_MANNEQUIN.BURNT"
msgid "Oh no, I thought I smelled a campfire burning around here!"
msgstr "Ah hayır, buralarda kamp ateşi kokusu aldığımı sanmıştım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_MANNEQUIN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_MANNEQUIN.GENERIC"
msgid "I don't know why some people think mannequins are scary."
msgstr "Bazı insanların mankenleri neden korkutucu bulduğunu bilmiyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_TAPE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SEWING_TAPE"
msgid "It's so handy!"
msgstr "Çok kullanışlı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWDANCER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWDANCER"
msgid "Mr. Maxwell's actually kind of fun when you get to know him."
msgstr "Bay Maxwell aslında tanıyınca biraz eğlenceli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWDIGGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWDIGGER"
msgid "I wish my shadow could help me with my chores."
msgstr "Keşke gölgem ev işlerimde bana yardım edebilseydi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWHEART
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWHEART"
msgid "Look at that! I wonder what's keeping it alive?"
msgstr "Şuna bak! Onu canlı tutan ne acaba?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWRIFT_PORTAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWRIFT_PORTAL"
msgid "I wish I could get a better look inside..."
msgstr "Keşke içine daha iyi bakabilseydim..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_CENTIPEDE.BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_CENTIPEDE.BODY"
msgid "Beware of de-feet! Get it, Wobes? De-feet!"
msgstr "Yenilgi-yenil ayaklara dikkat! Anladın mı, Wobes? Yenilgi-yenil!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_CENTIPEDE.FLIPPED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_CENTIPEDE.FLIPPED"
msgid "No, Woby. I don't think it wants its belly scratched."
msgstr "Hayır, Woby. Karnının kaşınmasını istediğini sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_CENTIPEDE.HEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_CENTIPEDE.HEAD"
msgid "Are two heads better than one?"
msgstr "İki kafa bir kafadan iyi midir?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_HANDS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_HANDS"
msgid "They seem fun!"
msgstr "Eğlenceli görünüyorlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_HORNS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_HORNS"
msgid "I bet they're friendly!"
msgstr "Eminim dostçadırlar!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_MOUTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_MOUTH"
msgid "It's a silly one!"
msgstr "Bu komik bir tanesi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_PARASITE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_PARASITE"
msgid "I think it just wants a friend."
msgstr "Sanırım sadece arkadaş istiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_WINGS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOWTHRALL_WINGS"
msgid "Oooh, neat! That one can fly!"
msgstr "Oooo, havalı! Bu uçabiliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_BATTLEAXE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_BATTLEAXE"
msgid "Woby, I think it winked at me!"
msgstr "Woby, sanırım bana göz kırptı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_BEEF_BELL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_BEEF_BELL"
msgid "Like first aid but magic."
msgstr "İlk yardım gibi ama sihirli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_FORGE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_FORGE"
msgid "It's really handy! Get it? Because it has hands?"
msgstr "Cidden el verişli! Anladın mı? Çünkü elleri var?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_FORGE_KIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_FORGE_KIT"
msgid "Don't worry, I'm great at setting things up!"
msgstr "Merak etme, kurmakta çok iyiyim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_HEART_VEIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHADOW_HEART_VEIN"
msgid "Aw, it's so helpful!"
msgstr "Aaa, çok yardımsever!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHALLOW_GRAVE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHALLOW_GRAVE"
msgid "Don't sniff around there, Woby."
msgstr "Oraları koklama, Woby."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHARK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHARK"
msgid "Just look at the size of those teeth!"
msgstr "Şu dişlerin boyuna bir bak!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHARKBOI
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHARKBOI"
msgid "Better watch out for frostbite!"
msgstr "Soğuk ısırığına dikkat etsem iyi olur!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHELLWEAVER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHELLWEAVER"
msgid "You can make a lot of stuff out of salt!"
msgstr "Tuzdan bir sürü şey yapabilirsin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHELL_CLUSTER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHELL_CLUSTER"
msgid "Let's break it apart and see what's inside."
msgstr "Hadi parçalayıp içinde ne olduğuna bakalım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHIELDOFTERROR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHIELDOFTERROR"
msgid "I like to think it's smiling."
msgstr "Gülümsediğini düşünmek hoşuma gidiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHOVEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHOVEL"
msgid "You never know what you'll find if you do a little digging."
msgstr "Biraz kazınca ne bulacağın hiç belli olmaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHOVEL_LUNARPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHOVEL_LUNARPLANT"
msgid "I came up with the name!"
msgstr "Adını ben buldum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHROOMBAIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHROOMBAIT"
msgid "Don't eat that Woby! It'll knock you right out."
msgstr "Onu yeme Woby! Seni resmen bayıltır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHROOMCAKE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHROOMCAKE"
msgid "Is that really a cake?"
msgstr "Bu cidden bir pasta mı?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHROOM_SKIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SHROOM_SKIN"
msgid "It's so weird! Can I keep it?"
msgstr "Çok garip! Bunu saklayabilir miyim?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SIESTAHUT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SIESTAHUT.BURNT"
msgid "What a waste of supplies..."
msgstr "Ne malzeme israfı..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SIESTAHUT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SIESTAHUT.GENERIC"
msgid "A shady spot for a quick nap."
msgstr "Hızlı bir şekerleme için gölgeli bir yer."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SILK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SILK"
msgid "Spiders are pretty useful."
msgstr "Örümcekler epey faydalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SINGINGSHELL_OCTAVE3.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SINGINGSHELL_OCTAVE3.GENERIC"
msgid "There's something inside it!"
msgstr "İçinde bir şey var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SINGINGSHELL_OCTAVE4.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SINGINGSHELL_OCTAVE4.GENERIC"
msgid "Maybe I could teach it to play some songs I learned in the Pioneers."
msgstr "Belki ona Öncülerde öğrendiğim şarkıları çalmayı öğretebilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SINGINGSHELL_OCTAVE5.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SINGINGSHELL_OCTAVE5.GENERIC"
msgid "Is that hard on your ears, Woby?"
msgstr "Bu kulağına ağır geliyor mu, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.GENERIC"
msgid "Yeah, that looks haunted."
msgstr "Evet, perili görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.LOTS_OF_FLOWERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.LOTS_OF_FLOWERS"
msgid "That looks pretty nice."
msgstr "Epey güzel görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.LOTS_OF_FLOWERS_BLOSSOM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.LOTS_OF_FLOWERS_BLOSSOM"
msgid "Do you hear that, Woby?"
msgstr "Bunu duyuyor musun, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.LOTS_OF_FLOWERS_EVIL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.LOTS_OF_FLOWERS_EVIL"
msgid "They make me feel weird."
msgstr "Bana garip hissettiriyorlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.SOME_FLOWERS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SISTURN.SOME_FLOWERS"
msgid "If I find some flowers I'll bring them back here."
msgstr "Çiçek bulursam onları buraya getiririm."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON"
msgid "Is it a real skeleton?"
msgstr "Bu gerçek bir iskelet mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETONHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETONHAT"
msgid "Good thing they had such a thick skull, this makes a great helmet!"
msgstr "İyi ki kalın bir kafatasları varmış, harika bir miğfer oluyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_NOTPLAYER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_NOTPLAYER"
msgid "Think it's a monster skeleton, Woby?"
msgstr "Sence bu canavar iskeleti mi, Woby?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.DEFAULT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.DEFAULT"
msgid "Poor %s. I guess %s might be more dangerous than I thought..."
msgstr "Zavallı %s. Sanırım %s düşündüğümden daha tehlikeli olabilir..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.FEMALE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.FEMALE"
msgid "Poor %s. I guess %s might be more dangerous than I thought..."
msgstr "Zavallı %s. Sanırım %s düşündüğümden daha tehlikeli olabilir..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.MALE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.MALE"
msgid "Poor %s. I guess %s might be more dangerous than I thought..."
msgstr "Zavallı %s. Sanırım %s düşündüğümden daha tehlikeli olabilir..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.ROBOT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKELETON_PLAYER.ROBOT"
msgid "Poor %s. I guess %s might be more dangerous than I thought..."
msgstr "Zavallı %s. Sanırım %s düşündüğümden daha tehlikeli olabilir..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKETCH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKETCH"
msgid "I think I could sculpt this! I'm pretty good at arts and crafts."
msgstr "Sanırım bunu yontabilirim! Sanat ve el işinde epey iyiyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKULLCHEST
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SKULLCHEST"
msgid "There's got to be something good in there."
msgstr "İçinde mutlaka iyi bir şey olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLEEPBOMB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLEEPBOMB"
msgid "It's more humane than a stink bomb."
msgstr "Kokuşmuş bombadan daha insancıl."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT.GENERIC"
msgid "You never know what you'll run into out in the wilderness."
msgstr "Doğada neyle karşılaşacağın hiç belli olmaz."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT.NOT_MINE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT.NOT_MINE"
msgid "I really shouldn't pick up things that don't belong to me."
msgstr "Bana ait olmayan şeyleri alıyor olmamalıyım gerçekten."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_CONTAINER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_CONTAINER"
msgid "A good Pinetree Pioneer always packs extra ammo!"
msgstr "İyi bir Çamağacı Öncüsü daima yedek mermi taşır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_DREADSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_DREADSTONE"
msgid "These will pack a real punch-a-roo!"
msgstr "Bunlar gerçek bir yumruk-omba indirir!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_FREEZE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_FREEZE"
msgid "Almost as chilling as my favourite radio shows!"
msgstr "Neredeyse en sevdiğim radyo programlarım kadar tüyler ürpertici!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_GELBLOB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_GELBLOB"
msgid "Icky. Just the way I like it!"
msgstr "İğrenç. Tam sevdiğim gibi!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_GOLD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_GOLD"
msgid "These rounds are golden! Literally!"
msgstr "Bu mermiler altın değerinde! Tam anlamıyla!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_GUNPOWDER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_GUNPOWDER"
msgid "Woby, we're going out with a BANG!"
msgstr "Woby, BÜYÜK bir patlamayla çıkıyoruz!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_HONEY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_HONEY"
msgid "Sweet!"
msgstr "Tatlı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_HORRORFUEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_HORRORFUEL"
msgid "Spooktacular! Heh."
msgstr "Korku-müthiş! Heh."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_LUNARPLANTHUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_LUNARPLANTHUSK"
msgid "Prrrickly-wickly!"
msgstr "Diiiken-miken!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_MARBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_MARBLE"
msgid "I wish they weren't so hard to find!"
msgstr "Keşke bulması bu kadar zor olmasaydı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_MOONGLASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_MOONGLASS"
msgid "Now I can hit'em with the moon!"
msgstr "Artık onlara ayla vurabilirim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_POOP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_POOP"
msgid "Gross... but a distraction is a distraction."
msgstr "İğrenç... ama dikkat dağıtmak dikkat dağıtmaktır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_PUREBRILLIANCE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_PUREBRILLIANCE"
msgid "Yes, Woby. We are brilliant!"
msgstr "Evet, Woby. Biz parlağız!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_ROCK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_ROCK"
msgid "They're not the best, but they'll work."
msgstr "En iyileri değil ama iş görür."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_SCRAPFEATHER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_SCRAPFEATHER"
msgid "They're in for a shock!"
msgstr "Onları bir şok bekliyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_SLOW
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_SLOW"
msgid "These should slow them down!"
msgstr "Bunlar onları yavaşlatmalı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_STINGER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_STINGER"
msgid "Better be careful with these."
msgstr "Bunlarla dikkatli olsam iyi olur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_THULECITE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTAMMO_THULECITE"
msgid "Shadow magic is pretty handy, I see why the Ancients liked it!"
msgstr "Gölge sihiri epey kullanışlı, Kadimler'in neden sevdiğini şimdi anlıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTMODKIT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOTMODKIT"
msgid "Time to mod my trusty slingshot?"
msgstr "Sadık sapanımı modlama vakti mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_BAND_MIMIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_BAND_MIMIC"
msgid "Creepy! I love it."
msgstr "Ürkütücü! Bayıldım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_BAND_PIGSKIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_BAND_PIGSKIN"
msgid "Mmm. Smells like bacon! But don't eat it Woby!"
msgstr "Mmm. Pastırma gibi kokuyor! Ama yeme Woby!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_BAND_TENTACLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_BAND_TENTACLE"
msgid "It's a little twitchy!"
msgstr "Biraz seğiriyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_FRAME_BONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_FRAME_BONE"
msgid "Bad to the bone!"
msgstr "İliklerine kadar kötü!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_FRAME_GEMS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WALTER.DESCRIBE.SLINGSHOT_FRAME_GEMS"
msgid "Now we're getting fancy!"
