#. STRINGS.SKIN_DESCRIPTIONS.wateringcan_rustic
msgctxt "STRINGS.SKIN_DESCRIPTIONS.wateringcan_rustic"
msgid "With a little care and attention, it could be good as new."
msgstr "Biraz özen ve dikkatle yeni gibi olabilir."

#. STRINGS.SKIN_DESCRIPTIONS.watermelonhat_banana
msgctxt "STRINGS.SKIN_DESCRIPTIONS.watermelonhat_banana"
msgid "Headwear so a-peeling, it's bananas."
